Text0_0_loc9='What\'s a young $C like you out visiting an old farmer like me?'
Text0_0_loc9='Naralex sleeps again!$B$BLong ago, Naralex journeyed to this cavern with the honorable goal of entering the Emerald Dream and regrowing the Barrens into a lush forest. His focus waned and his thoughts became tainted by serpentine visions.$B$BNow, reptilian beasts seep from his dreams to the land. He must be awoken from the nightmare or he will be forever lost, and a great evil unleashed.$B$BOnly after his corrupted servants, the Fanglords, have been slain can I perform the awakening ritual.$B$B'
Text0_0_loc9='The Fanglords are dead! All hope is not lost!$B$BThe awakening ritual is quite complex, however. It cannot be done alone.$B$BI will handle all of the necessary preparations but I will need you to protect me. The nightmares summoned from Naralex\'s journey through the Emerald Dream prove to be quite formidable. Without your help, this mission is doomed.$B$BWhen you are ready to defend me, say the word, and I shall lead the way to Naralex\'s chamber.'
Text0_0_loc9='The machine adjusts to face you.$B$BOn the back of the machine is an empty, oddly misshapen slot with an engraving that reads: "Propirtee o\' Cap\'n Gelkak Gyromast"'
Text0_0_loc9='Hey!  Are you on an errand for Tirth?  If I were you I\'d get as far away from him as I could!  His mind\'s been pickled from too much drink but his magic\'s as strong as ever!'
Text0_0_loc9='Sure, I\'ll tell you the phrase.  As long as I don\'t have to go anywhere near Tirth!'
Text0_0_loc9='Gelkak\'s key slides into the vacant slot.'
Text0_0_loc9='Do you mock me while I am unable to defend myself, bound to this ball of iron?'
Text0_0_loc9='One of the humans has the key to this infernal contraption. Eston I think they said his name was.'
Text0_0_loc9='Get away from here, $C, or they\'ll put you in chains as well.'
Text0_0_loc9='Marlgen... One of the jailors. He has the key to my bonds.'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The Bank of Stormwind is located in the Trade District just northwest of the city gates. Here, let me show you on your map.',Text0_1_loc9='The Bank of Stormwind is located in the Trade District just northwest of the city gates. Here, let me show you on your map.',Text1_0_loc9='Stormwind Counting House is located by the front gates in the Trade District of Stormwind. And when you get tired of counting your money, be sure to stop by the Gilded Rose for a drink.',Text1_1_loc9='Stormwind Counting House is located by the front gates in the Trade District of Stormwind. And when you get tired of counting your money, be sure to stop by the Gilded Rose for a drink.' WHERE entry=764;
Text0_0_loc9='I wish the snow would just all melt away. It\'s always getting my robe wet and messing up everything!'
Text0_0_loc9='Stupid snow... Hey, you\'re, $N, aren\'t you? I\'ve just received a message asking for you.'
Text0_0_loc9='You\'ve been summoned by Lago Blackwrench, warlock master of Ironforge. You\'d do yourself well to report to him immediately. You\'ll find him in the Forlorn Cavern district of the city.'
Text0_0_loc9='Greetings $R, I am Tharnariun Treetender.'
