UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Therum Deepforge is the dwarf you want to talk to. One of the finest blacksmiths around if you ask me. You can find him in the heart of the Dwarven District.',Text0_1_loc9='Therum Deepforge is the dwarf you want to talk to. One of the finest blacksmiths around if you ask me. You can find him in the heart of the Dwarven District.',Text1_0_loc9='You mean you can\'t smell the smoke of the Dwarven forges from here?  Well, you will be looking for Therum Deepforge if you want to learn blacksmithing.  He\'s over in the Dwarven District which is just north of the Cathedral Square.',Text1_1_loc9='You mean you can\'t smell the smoke of the Dwarven forges from here?  Well, you will be looking for Therum Deepforge if you want to learn blacksmithing.  He\'s over in the Dwarven District which is just north of the Cathedral Square.' WHERE entry=920;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='If you are looking to become a great cook, venture over to the Pig and Whistle Tavern in Old Town and talk to Stephen Ryback. That man knows how to cook up a rack of ribs like no other.$B$BMan... now you got me hungry for some of his famous ribs. Don\'t count on him teaching you that recipe though!',Text0_1_loc9='If you are looking to become a great cook, venture over to the Pig and Whistle Tavern in Old Town and talk to Stephen Ryback. That man knows how to cook up a rack of ribs like no other.$B$BMan... now you got me hungry for some of his famous ribs. Don\'t count on him teaching you that recipe though!',Text1_0_loc9='There\'s a great cook who works at the Pig and Whistle Tavern in Old Town.  I\'ve watched him use a knife when he cooks and just between you and me, I don\'t think he\'s always been a cook.  Don\'t get me wrong... if you still want to learn, he\'s the best we have.',Text1_1_loc9='There\'s a great cook who works at the Pig and Whistle Tavern in Old Town.  I\'ve watched him use a knife when he cooks and just between you and me, I don\'t think he\'s always been a cook.  Don\'t get me wrong... if you still want to learn, he\'s the best we have.' WHERE entry=921;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Stormwind\'s resident engineer trainer is an ingenious gnome by the name of Lilliam Sparkspindle. He can be found in the back of the Dwarven District.',Text0_1_loc9='Stormwind\'s resident engineer trainer is an ingenious gnome by the name of Lilliam Sparkspindle. He can be found in the back of the Dwarven District.',Text1_0_loc9='Hey, that reminds me, I need to have my rocket boots repaired.  Word to the wise my friend, rocket boots and gryphons don\'t mix.  $B$BOh, but you need directions...  just head on over to the Dwarven District, you\'ll find Lilliam Sparkspindle towards the back.',Text1_1_loc9='Hey, that reminds me, I need to have my rocket boots repaired.  Word to the wise my friend, rocket boots and gryphons don\'t mix.  $B$BOh, but you need directions...  just head on over to the Dwarven District, you\'ll find Lilliam Sparkspindle towards the back.' WHERE entry=922;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The Cathedral of Light is the center of all the healing practices of Stormwind. There you can find Shaina Fuller to help you learn this craft.',Text0_1_loc9='The Cathedral of Light is the center of all the healing practices of Stormwind. There you can find Shaina Fuller to help you learn this craft.',Text1_0_loc9='No better place to learn First Aid than under the watchful eye of Shaina Fuller at the Cathedral of Light.  $B$BTo get there, just look for the yellow rooftops, or the towering spire of the Cathedral itself which you can see from almost anywhere in the city.',Text1_1_loc9='No better place to learn First Aid than under the watchful eye of Shaina Fuller at the Cathedral of Light.  $B$BTo get there, just look for the yellow rooftops, or the towering spire of the Cathedral itself which you can see from almost anywhere in the city.' WHERE entry=923;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You can find Tannysa standing outside Alchemy Needs in the Mage Quarter.',Text0_1_loc9='You can find Tannysa standing outside Alchemy Needs in the Mage Quarter.',Text1_0_loc9='There\'s nothing quite like communing with nature... or at least that\'s what the night elves tell me.  I\'m not much for talking to flowers and trees, but I\'m sure Tannysa could help you out.  She\'s over in the Mage Quarter outside of Alchemy Needs.',Text1_1_loc9='There\'s nothing quite like communing with nature... or at least that\'s what the night elves tell me.  I\'m not much for talking to flowers and trees, but I\'m sure Tannysa could help you out.  She\'s over in the Mage Quarter outside of Alchemy Needs.' WHERE entry=924;
