UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The Inn?  Ah, ye looking to toss back some of the best ales Ironforge has to offer?  The Stonefire Tavern is where ye\'ll want to go. $B$BYe\'ll find it just to the left of the entrance to Ironforge if ye be coming, or to the right if ye be going.',Text0_1_loc9='The Inn?  Ah, ye looking to toss back some of the best ales Ironforge has to offer?  The Stonefire Tavern is where ye\'ll want to go. $B$BYe\'ll find it just to the left of the entrance to Ironforge if ye be coming, or to the right if ye be going.',Text1_0_loc9='If yer of need of an Inn, The Stonefire Inn is where ye should be.  Ye\'ll find it just to the left of the entrance to Ironforge if ye be coming, or to the right if ye be going.  $B$BOh, and if yer going that way, then tell them to have a tankard ready for me.',Text1_1_loc9='If yer of need of an Inn, The Stonefire Inn is where ye should be.  Ye\'ll find it just to the left of the entrance to Ironforge if ye be coming, or to the right if ye be going.  $B$BOh, and if yer going that way, then tell them to have a tankard ready for me.' WHERE entry=2768;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You can find a mailbox right o\'er by The Stonefire Tavern.  It\'s just north of the gates of Ironforge.',Text0_1_loc9='You can find a mailbox right o\'er by The Stonefire Tavern.  It\'s just north of the gates of Ironforge.',Text1_0_loc9='Bah!  Mailboxes...  all I get is junk mail lately!  $B$BIncrease the size of this... decrease the size of that... act now for your free Sword of Dragonslaying.  I have to change my mailbox number every other month!  $B$BWell, ye can\'t say I didn\'t warn ye.  If you\'re looking for the mailbox it\'s just outside the Stonefire Tavern.',Text1_1_loc9='Bah!  Mailboxes...  all I get is junk mail lately!  $B$BIncrease the size of this... decrease the size of that... act now for your free Sword of Dragonslaying.  I have to change my mailbox number every other month!  $B$BWell, ye can\'t say I didn\'t warn ye.  If you\'re looking for the mailbox it\'s just outside the Stonefire Tavern.' WHERE entry=2769;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I overheard Regnus Thundergranite in the Hall of Arms bragging about a new trophy for his den the other day.  If yer looking for training from a skilled hunter, Regnus is the one to see.',Text0_1_loc9='I overheard Regnus Thundergranite in the Hall of Arms bragging about a new trophy for his den the other day.  If yer looking for training from a skilled hunter, Regnus is the one to see.',Text1_0_loc9='Do ye have the potential to be a skilled hunter?  Well $Gladdie : lassie;, only time will tell.  Just don\'t ye go shooting at apples atop peoples\' heads till ye\'ve spoken with Regnus o\'er in the Hall of Arms.',Text1_1_loc9='Do ye have the potential to be a skilled hunter?  Well $Gladdie : lassie;, only time will tell.  Just don\'t ye go shooting at apples atop peoples\' heads till ye\'ve spoken with Regnus o\'er in the Hall of Arms.' WHERE entry=2770;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='That wee wizardly lass, Bink, over in the Hall of Mysteries would probably be able to help ye out with any magical needs you have.$B$BThe Hall of Mysteries is just north of the gates of Ironforge.',Text0_1_loc9='That wee wizardly lass, Bink, over in the Hall of Mysteries would probably be able to help ye out with any magical needs you have.$B$BThe Hall of Mysteries is just north of the gates of Ironforge.',Text1_0_loc9='Well ye\'d be sure to find some training in the magical arts over in the Hall of Mysteries, north of the gates of Ironforge.  Juli Stormkettle can always be found there with her nose in a book.',Text1_1_loc9='Well ye\'d be sure to find some training in the magical arts over in the Hall of Mysteries, north of the gates of Ironforge.  Juli Stormkettle can always be found there with her nose in a book.' WHERE entry=2771;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Ah, Braenna Flintcrag.  She has magic hands, that one.  Braenna is the one to see about Priestly matters.  $B$BYe\'ll want to travel north from the gates of Ironforge to the Hall of Mysteries.  That\'s where ye\'ll find her.',Text0_1_loc9='Ah, Braenna Flintcrag.  She has magic hands, that one.  Braenna is the one to see about Priestly matters.  $B$BYe\'ll want to travel north from the gates of Ironforge to the Hall of Mysteries.  That\'s where ye\'ll find her.',Text1_0_loc9='Ah, nothing better than a priest to cure what ails ye.  Of course a nice tall pint cures a lot of what ails ye too, but I don\'t think Braenna Flintcrag teaches brewing.  I guess ye\'ll have to settle for some priest training over in the Hall of Mysteries instead.',Text1_1_loc9='Ah, nothing better than a priest to cure what ails ye.  Of course a nice tall pint cures a lot of what ails ye too, but I don\'t think Braenna Flintcrag teaches brewing.  I guess ye\'ll have to settle for some priest training over in the Hall of Mysteries instead.' WHERE entry=2772;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Brandur Ironhammer would be the one ye\'d want to see.  Ye can find him in the Hall of Mysteries north of the gates of Ironforge.',Text0_1_loc9='Brandur Ironhammer would be the one ye\'d want to see.  Ye can find him in the Hall of Mysteries north of the gates of Ironforge.',Text1_0_loc9='Ah, good ol\' Brandur Ironhammer.  There\'s no doubt he\'ll provide ye with the guidance ye seek, $Glad : lass;.  Ye\'ll find him in the Hall of Mysteries north of the gates of Ironforge.',Text1_1_loc9='Ah, good ol\' Brandur Ironhammer.  There\'s no doubt he\'ll provide ye with the guidance ye seek, $Glad : lass;.  Ye\'ll find him in the Hall of Mysteries north of the gates of Ironforge.' WHERE entry=2773;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Now why would ye be needing the services of one of those types?  We get enough trouble out of that rogue, Hulfdan Blackbeard, over in The Forlorn Cavern, do I need to be turning my eye to you as well?',Text0_1_loc9='Now why would ye be needing the services of one of those types?  We get enough trouble out of that rogue, Hulfdan Blackbeard, over in The Forlorn Cavern, do I need to be turning my eye to you as well?',Text1_0_loc9='All the roguish types hang out in The Forlorn Cavern, north of the gates of Ironforge.  I\'d wager ye\'ll find Fenthwick there, no doubt counting the coin of another cut purse.  I\'ll catch him one of these days!  $B$BIn the meantime I\'ll have my eye on you as well, $Glad : lass;.',Text1_1_loc9='All the roguish types hang out in The Forlorn Cavern, north of the gates of Ironforge.  I\'d wager ye\'ll find Fenthwick there, no doubt counting the coin of another cut purse.  I\'ll catch him one of these days!  $B$BIn the meantime I\'ll have my eye on you as well, $Glad : lass;.' WHERE entry=2774;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Where better to look for a dark and brooding lot, than the dark section of Ironforge, aptly named The Forlorn Cavern.  Thistleheart is sure to be found there, likely summoning some manner of vile creature to do his bidding.',Text0_1_loc9='Where better to look for a dark and brooding lot, than the dark section of Ironforge, aptly named The Forlorn Cavern.  Thistleheart is sure to be found there, likely summoning some manner of vile creature to do his bidding.',Text1_0_loc9='A warlock, eh...  Well, if you\'ve got a mind to be doing that sort of thing around here then ye best keep yer demons on a leash $Gboyo : girlie;.  I don\'t like demons, but I love putting mah axe to them.  Ye get me?  $B$BNow you just leave me be and go get lost in The Forlorn Cavern.  That\'s where you\'ll find that warlock, Thistleheart.',Text1_1_loc9='A warlock, eh...  Well, if you\'ve got a mind to be doing that sort of thing around here then ye best keep yer demons on a leash $Gboyo : girlie;.  I don\'t like demons, but I love putting mah axe to them.  Ye get me?  $B$BNow you just leave me be and go get lost in The Forlorn Cavern.  That\'s where you\'ll find that warlock, Thistleheart.' WHERE entry=2775;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Och! Ye seek training in the way of the warrior, do ye?  Kelstrum Stonebreaker will put ye through yer paces!  Just march yerself over to the Hall of Arms east of the gates of Ironforge.',Text0_1_loc9='Och! Ye seek training in the way of the warrior, do ye?  Kelstrum Stonebreaker will put ye through yer paces!  Just march yerself over to the Hall of Arms east of the gates of Ironforge.',Text1_0_loc9='Kelstrum is a loudmouth and a braggart... and if that weren\'t enough he\'s also one of the most skilled warriors ye\'ll ever meet!  $B$BI tell ye, if ye\'re looking to be trained in the ways of a warrior, that\'s who ye should be talking to.  I\'m sure he can be found over in the Hall of Arms east of the Gates of Ironforge.',Text1_1_loc9='Kelstrum is a loudmouth and a braggart... and if that weren\'t enough he\'s also one of the most skilled warriors ye\'ll ever meet!  $B$BI tell ye, if ye\'re looking to be trained in the ways of a warrior, that\'s who ye should be talking to.  I\'m sure he can be found over in the Hall of Arms east of the Gates of Ironforge.' WHERE entry=2776;
