UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='An Alchemy trainer is what you need?  Well, I just came from there, I did.  Ye\'ll find Ms. Berryfizz over in Tinker Town where the gnomes gather.',Text0_1_loc9='An Alchemy trainer is what you need?  Well, I just came from there, I did.  Ye\'ll find Ms. Berryfizz over in Tinker Town where the gnomes gather.',Text1_0_loc9='Yer looking for an Alchemy trainer are ye?  Just came from there, I did.  Ye\'ll find Ms. Berryfizz over in Tinker Town where the gnomes gather.  $B$B::sigh:: ...why o\' why didn\'t I take the blue potion.',Text1_1_loc9='Yer looking for an Alchemy trainer are ye?  Just came from there, I did.  Ye\'ll find Ms. Berryfizz over in Tinker Town where the gnomes gather.  $B$B::sigh:: ...why o\' why didn\'t I take the blue potion.' WHERE entry=2794;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Ye\'ve come to the right place $Glad : lass;!  People come here from all o\'er the world to train to be a blacksmith.  Ye\'ll find Bengus Deepforge hammering away at an anvil in the middle of our fine city by The Great Forge itself.',Text0_1_loc9='Ye\'ve come to the right place $Glad : lass;!  People come here from all o\'er the world to train to be a blacksmith.  Ye\'ll find Bengus Deepforge hammering away at an anvil in the middle of our fine city by The Great Forge itself.',Text1_0_loc9='Are ye really askin\' me where the Blacksmith is?  Have ye not heard of The Great Forge!?  All our best blacksmiths gather there to craft their weapons and armor!  $B$BIt\'s dead smack in the middle of Ironforge, and that\'s where you\'ll find one of our most brilliant blacksmiths, Bengus Deepforge.',Text1_1_loc9='Are ye really askin\' me where the Blacksmith is?  Have ye not heard of The Great Forge!?  All our best blacksmiths gather there to craft their weapons and armor!  $B$BIt\'s dead smack in the middle of Ironforge, and that\'s where you\'ll find one of our most brilliant blacksmiths, Bengus Deepforge.' WHERE entry=2795;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='A Cooking trainer is it?  Well then, get yerself over to the Bronze Kettle on the northeastern side of The Great Forge.  Daryl Riknussun will teach ye to make a mighty fine dish that\'s sure to put the life back in ye!',Text0_1_loc9='A Cooking trainer is it?  Well then, get yerself over to the Bronze Kettle on the northeastern side of The Great Forge.  Daryl Riknussun will teach ye to make a mighty fine dish that\'s sure to put the life back in ye!',Text1_0_loc9='Och!  That Daryl Riknussun is a brilliant cook!  He makes a chilli so hot ye could temper steel with it!  I don\'t think he\'ll teach ye the recipe, but he\'ll certainly help ye to become a good cook.  Ye\'ll find him at the Bronze Kettle o\'er on the northeastern side of The Great Forge.',Text1_1_loc9='Och!  That Daryl Riknussun is a brilliant cook!  He makes a chilli so hot ye could temper steel with it!  I don\'t think he\'ll teach ye the recipe, but he\'ll certainly help ye to become a good cook.  Ye\'ll find him at the Bronze Kettle o\'er on the northeastern side of The Great Forge.' WHERE entry=2796;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Ah, I believe Gimble Thistlefuzz is who ye\'ll be needing if yer looking to learn the Enchanter\'s profession.  Ye\'ll find Gimble in his shop, Thistlefuzz Arcanery, right by the Gryphon Master at The Great Forge.',Text0_1_loc9='Ah, I believe Gimble Thistlefuzz is who ye\'ll be needing if yer looking to learn the Enchanter\'s profession.  Ye\'ll find Gimble in his shop, Thistlefuzz Arcanery, right by the Gryphon Master at The Great Forge.',Text1_0_loc9='Och!  Ye should be careful what ye get enchanted $Glad : lass;.  I had me mug enchanted so it wouldn\'t spill a drop, but now I can\'t drink from it!  Such a tragedy.  $B$BYou be sure to heed me advice when ye see Gimble.  He\'ll be in his shop right by the Gryphon Master at The Great Forge.',Text1_1_loc9='Och!  Ye should be careful what ye get enchanted $Glad : lass;.  I had me mug enchanted so it wouldn\'t spill a drop, but now I can\'t drink from it!  Such a tragedy.  $B$BYou be sure to heed me advice when ye see Gimble.  He\'ll be in his shop right by the Gryphon Master at The Great Forge.' WHERE entry=2797;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The tinkerer\'s craft for you is it?  No doubt ye\'ll want to go see Springspindle Fizzlegear in Tinker Town.  $B$BJust head east from the gates of Ironforge, or follow the sound of the explosions.',Text0_1_loc9='The tinkerer\'s craft for you is it?  No doubt ye\'ll want to go see Springspindle Fizzlegear in Tinker Town.  $B$BJust head east from the gates of Ironforge, or follow the sound of the explosions.',Text1_0_loc9='Oh, you\'re looking for Springspindle Fizzlegear then.  Why that little gnome and his gadgets...  Let me tell you, if you\'re going to his shop in Tinker Town, keep your hands to yourself and don\'t pet any of his mechanical sheep!  $B$BExploding sheep... now why would you even make such a thing!?',Text1_1_loc9='Oh, you\'re looking for Springspindle Fizzlegear then.  Why that little gnome and his gadgets...  Let me tell you, if you\'re going to his shop in Tinker Town, keep your hands to yourself and don\'t pet any of his mechanical sheep!  $B$BExploding sheep... now why would you even make such a thing!?' WHERE entry=2798;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='A valuable skill First Aid is.  Our resident trainer, Nissa Firestone, can show ye how it\'s done.  Look for her on the southern side of The Great Forge at the Ironforge Physician.',Text0_1_loc9='A valuable skill First Aid is.  Our resident trainer, Nissa Firestone, can show ye how it\'s done.  Look for her on the southern side of The Great Forge at the Ironforge Physician.' WHERE entry=2799;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='A valuable skill First Aid is.  Our resident trainer, Nissa Firestone, can show ye how it\'s done.  Look for her on the southern side of The Great Forge at the Ironforge Physician.', Text1_0_loc9='First Aid?  Well ye don\'t look hurt to me.  If yer really interested in learning First Aid, then Nissa Firestone is the one to learn from.  Go see her over by The Great Forge in her shop, The Ironforge Physician.',, Text1_1_loc9='First Aid?  Well ye don\'t look hurt to me.  If yer really interested in learning First Aid, then Nissa Firestone is the one to learn from.  Go see her over by The Great Forge in her shop, The Ironforge Physician.' WHERE entry=2799;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Grimnur Stonebrand will tell ye some whoppers about the one that got away, but he\'s still one o\' the best fishermen around.  He\'s got a shop set up in The Forlorn Cavern called the Traveling Fisherman.',Text0_1_loc9='Grimnur Stonebrand will tell ye some whoppers about the one that got away, but he\'s still one o\' the best fishermen around.  He\'s got a shop set up in The Forlorn Cavern called the Traveling Fisherman.',Text1_0_loc9='I once heard ol\' Grimnur say he fished up a sword.  Or was it a swordfish?  Damn that Grimnur, he\'s told so many fish tales I can\'t remember which is which.  Well, why don\'t you go see him over in The Forlorn Cavern and have him tell you what it was.',Text1_1_loc9='I once heard ol\' Grimnur say he fished up a sword.  Or was it a swordfish?  Damn that Grimnur, he\'s told so many fish tales I can\'t remember which is which.  Well, why don\'t you go see him over in The Forlorn Cavern and have him tell you what it was.' WHERE entry=2800;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Flowers and seeds and such?  That would be Reyna Stonebranch\'s area of expertise.  Ye can find her tending to her plants over at the Ironforge Physician on the southern side of The Great Forge.',Text0_1_loc9='Flowers and seeds and such?  That would be Reyna Stonebranch\'s area of expertise.  Ye can find her tending to her plants over at the Ironforge Physician on the southern side of The Great Forge.',Text1_0_loc9='Oh, ye want to learn to pick some daisies do ye?  Ha!  I\'m just teasing ye $Gladdie : lass;.  $B$BA fine profession it is, and Reyna Stonebranch can show ye how it\'s done.  She works at the Ironforge Physician on the southern side of The Great Forge.',Text1_1_loc9='Oh, ye want to learn to pick some daisies do ye?  Ha!  I\'m just teasing ye $Gladdie : lass;.  $B$BA fine profession it is, and Reyna Stonebranch can show ye how it\'s done.  She works at the Ironforge Physician on the southern side of The Great Forge.' WHERE entry=2801;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Fimble Finespindle has a shop set up on the northwest side of The Great Forge.  I wager he could show ye how to make some fine armor.',Text0_1_loc9='Fimble Finespindle has a shop set up on the northwest side of The Great Forge.  I wager he could show ye how to make some fine armor.',Text1_0_loc9='Sure ye don\'t want to be a Blacksmith?  Well, if yer heart is set on Leatherworking, then you best talk to Fimble Finespindle over at his shop on the northwest side of The Great Forge.',Text1_1_loc9='Sure ye don\'t want to be a Blacksmith?  Well, if yer heart is set on Leatherworking, then you best talk to Fimble Finespindle over at his shop on the northwest side of The Great Forge.' WHERE entry=2802;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Do we have Mining trainers here?  Where do ye think ye are!?  $B$BWhy you\'ll find one o\' the best miners in all Dun Morogh at the Deepmountain Mining Guild on the northern side of The Great Forge.  There, Geofram Bouldertoe will show ye the true art of mining.',Text0_1_loc9='Do we have Mining trainers here?  Where do ye think ye are!?  $B$BWhy you\'ll find one o\' the best miners in all Dun Morogh at the Deepmountain Mining Guild on the northern side of The Great Forge.  There, Geofram Bouldertoe will show ye the true art of mining.',Text1_0_loc9='Well well!  You\'ve come to the right place to learn Mining, $Gboyo : girlie;!  Geofram Bouldertoe himself resides at the Deepmountain Mining Guild.  Ye couldn\'t ask for a better instructor than him.',Text1_1_loc9='Well well!  You\'ve come to the right place to learn Mining, $Gboyo : girlie;!  Geofram Bouldertoe himself resides at the Deepmountain Mining Guild.  Ye couldn\'t ask for a better instructor than him.' WHERE entry=2804;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Balthus Stoneflayer is the one to see about Skinning.  If it can be skinned, he can teach ye how.  Just walk yerself over to Finespindle\'s Leather Goods on the northern side of The Great Forge.',Text0_1_loc9='Balthus Stoneflayer is the one to see about Skinning.  If it can be skinned, he can teach ye how.  Just walk yerself over to Finespindle\'s Leather Goods on the northern side of The Great Forge.',Text1_0_loc9='Skinning?  The only thing ye look like ye could skin is yer own knee!  Ha!  Now why don\'t you go see Balthus Stoneflayer so he can teach you how to properly skin some animals.  You\'ll find him in Finespindle\'s Leather Goods on the northern side of The Great Forge.',Text1_1_loc9='Skinning?  The only thing ye look like ye could skin is yer own knee!  Ha!  Now why don\'t you go see Balthus Stoneflayer so he can teach you how to properly skin some animals.  You\'ll find him in Finespindle\'s Leather Goods on the northern side of The Great Forge.' WHERE entry=2805;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='That Jormund Stonebrow has a knack for the needle, he does.  Should you be needing some training, then you\'ll find him at Stonebrow\'s Clothier on the northern side of The Great Forge.',Text0_1_loc9='That Jormund Stonebrow has a knack for the needle, he does.  Should you be needing some training, then you\'ll find him at Stonebrow\'s Clothier on the northern side of The Great Forge.',Text1_0_loc9='Ye might not know it, but in addition to being a skilled tailor, Jormund is also a slayer of giants!  Why he must have overheard a few of us sharing stories when he shouted that he\'d killed seven with one blow!  $B$BYe should pay him a visit at his store on the north side of The Great Forge an\' see if he\'ll tell ye the tale!',Text1_1_loc9='Ye might not know it, but in addition to being a skilled tailor, Jormund is also a slayer of giants!  Why he must have overheard a few of us sharing stories when he shouted that he\'d killed seven with one blow!  $B$BYe should pay him a visit at his store on the north side of The Great Forge an\' see if he\'ll tell ye the tale!' WHERE entry=2807;
Text0_0_loc9='I have suffered, but now I can feel it slowly fading from me. I feel... free.'
Text0_0_loc9='The Crystal Pylons of Un\'Goro are a mystery to all. To the few inhabitants here, they are a source of legend, with much speculation as to their purpose.'
Text0_0_loc9='A closer inspection of the pylon leads you to find a small table containing blue, yellow, and green crystals arranged in what seems like a specific formation.$B$BA large blue circle of crystals is flanked on either side by a smaller circle of yellow crystals and another of green crystals.$B$BYou carefully take note of the colors of the crystals, knowing that J.D. would be very interested in hearing about what you have found.'
