UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Of all the wondrous places within Darnassus, which would you have me direct you to?',Text0_1_loc9='Of all the wondrous places within Darnassus, which would you have me direct you to?',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=3016;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You may find storage for your worldly goods at the bank of Darnassus, which lies in the center of our wondrous city.',Text0_1_loc9='You may find storage for your worldly goods at the bank of Darnassus, which lies in the center of our wondrous city.',Text1_0_loc9='Another material $Gboy : girl; are we?  Well, if you are obsessed with your precious items then you will probably want to store them at the Darnassus Bank in the center of our city.',Text1_1_loc9='Another material $Gboy : girl; are we?  Well, if you are obsessed with your precious items then you will probably want to store them at the Darnassus Bank in the center of our city.' WHERE entry=3017;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Vesprystus\' hippogryphs will bear you swiftly to your destination.  Seek him out in Rut\'theran Village, through the portal which lies in the western section of Darnassus.',Text0_1_loc9='Vesprystus\' hippogryphs will bear you swiftly to your destination.  Seek him out in Rut\'theran Village, through the portal which lies in the western section of Darnassus.',Text1_0_loc9='It is Vesprystus that you seek.  He watches over the hippogryphs that come and go from the base of Teldrassil.  You will find him through the portal in western Darnassus that will take you to Rut\'theran Village.',Text1_1_loc9='It is Vesprystus that you seek.  He watches over the hippogryphs that come and go from the base of Teldrassil.  You will find him through the portal in western Darnassus that will take you to Rut\'theran Village.' WHERE entry=3018;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='If you desire to form a fellowship then it is the guild master, Lysheana, that you must see.  You will find her in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace in the northeastern section of Darnassus.',Text0_1_loc9='If you desire to form a fellowship then it is the guild master, Lysheana, that you must see.  You will find her in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace in the northeastern section of Darnassus.',Text1_0_loc9='Lysheana can offer you the proper documents, she resides in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace in northeasten Darnassus.  May your fellowship bring glory to the Night Elves!',Text1_1_loc9='Lysheana can offer you the proper documents, she resides in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace in northeasten Darnassus.  May your fellowship bring glory to the Night Elves!' WHERE entry=3019;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Though I find the cool grass which covers Teldrassil as good a bed as any, the beds which Saelienne keeps at the Inn in Craftsman\'s Terrace are quite suitable for those with a taste for luxury.',Text0_1_loc9='Though I find the cool grass which covers Teldrassil as good a bed as any, the beds which Saelienne keeps at the Inn in Craftsman\'s Terrace are quite suitable for those with a taste for luxury.',Text1_0_loc9='Has the sun risen already?  There are just never enough hours in the night!  Well, Saelienne will take good care of you.  You can find her tending to her guests over in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace in northeastern Darnassus.',Text1_1_loc9='Has the sun risen already?  There are just never enough hours in the night!  Well, Saelienne will take good care of you.  You can find her tending to her guests over in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace in northeastern Darnassus.' WHERE entry=3020;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='There is a mailbox outside of the Bank which you\'ll find in the center of Darnassus.',Text0_1_loc9='There is a mailbox outside of the Bank which you\'ll find in the center of Darnassus.',Text1_0_loc9='A mailbox?  You have a letter to send, or perhaps have received one?  I hope it\'s something good!  There\'s a mailbox right outside of the Bank in the center of Darnassus.',Text1_1_loc9='A mailbox?  You have a letter to send, or perhaps have received one?  I hope it\'s something good!  There\'s a mailbox right outside of the Bank in the center of Darnassus.' WHERE entry=3021;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Here in Darnassus you will find skilled trainers who have perfected the skills of their chosen class through ages of training and dedication.  I will guide you to one who can become your mentor, you have but to name your chosen path.',Text0_1_loc9='Here in Darnassus you will find skilled trainers who have perfected the skills of their chosen class through ages of training and dedication.  I will guide you to one who can become your mentor, you have but to name your chosen path.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=3022;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You are fortunate to have come to Darnassus where you can find such an accomplished Hunter as Jocaste among our trainers.  I encourage you to visit her over in the Cenarion Enclave and seek her tutelage.',Text0_1_loc9='You are fortunate to have come to Darnassus where you can find such an accomplished Hunter as Jocaste among our trainers.  I encourage you to visit her over in the Cenarion Enclave and seek her tutelage.',Text1_0_loc9='Jocaste was the greatest of Hunters of her time.  These days you can find her over in the Cenarion Enclave where she teaches those who are just starting down the Hunter\'s path.',Text1_1_loc9='Jocaste was the greatest of Hunters of her time.  These days you can find her over in the Cenarion Enclave where she teaches those who are just starting down the Hunter\'s path.' WHERE entry=3023;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Ever vigilant in their protection of the natural world, the druids are guided by Arch Druid Fandral Staghelm who resides in the Cenarion Enclave.  You will find him and the other Druid trainers in the northern section of Darnassus.',Text0_1_loc9='Ever vigilant in their protection of the natural world, the druids are guided by Arch Druid Fandral Staghelm who resides in the Cenarion Enclave.  You will find him and the other Druid trainers in the northern section of Darnassus.',Text1_0_loc9='In grizzly times a druid can be a dear friend to those around them.  Ask any of the druids in the Cenarion Enclave and they will tell you the same.',Text1_1_loc9='In grizzly times a druid can be a dear friend to those around them.  Ask any of the druids in the Cenarion Enclave and they will tell you the same.' WHERE entry=3024;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The Temple of the Moon is home to the priests of Elune.  There you will find Jandria and Lariia, who will provide you with further guidance in the path of priesthood.',Text0_1_loc9='The Temple of the Moon is home to the priests of Elune.  There you will find Jandria and Lariia, who will provide you with further guidance in the path of priesthood.',Text1_0_loc9='The power of Elune compels you!  The power of Elune compels you!  $B$BGo now!  Seek out Jandria in the central hall of the Temple of the Moon in the southern section of Darnassus!',Text1_1_loc9='The power of Elune compels you!  The power of Elune compels you!  $B$BGo now!  Seek out Jandria in the central hall of the Temple of the Moon in the southern section of Darnassus!' WHERE entry=3025;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='It is Syurna that you seek if you are to follow the rogue\'s path.  She dwells in the Cenarion Enclave down the spiraling path within the western most tree.',Text0_1_loc9='It is Syurna that you seek if you are to follow the rogue\'s path.  She dwells in the Cenarion Enclave down the spiraling path within the western most tree.',Text1_0_loc9='There are those that attempt to follow the path of the Rogue, but only the night elves are truly embraced by the night.  If you seek to walk the shaded path then find Syurna in the Cenarion Enclave.',Text1_1_loc9='There are those that attempt to follow the path of the Rogue, but only the night elves are truly embraced by the night.  If you seek to walk the shaded path then find Syurna in the Cenarion Enclave.' WHERE entry=3026;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You will find Sildinair at the Warrior\'s Terrace among the guards, her keen eyes scanning the forest for enemies that might dare to enter our fair city.',Text0_1_loc9='You will find Sildinair at the Warrior\'s Terrace among the guards, her keen eyes scanning the forest for enemies that might dare to enter our fair city.',Text1_0_loc9='Sildinair has trained many of the Sentinels who guard our beloved city.  I am certain she can make a warrior out of the likes of you.  Seek her out at the Warrior\'s Terrace near the entrance to our city.',Text1_1_loc9='Sildinair has trained many of the Sentinels who guard our beloved city.  I am certain she can make a warrior out of the likes of you.  Seek her out at the Warrior\'s Terrace near the entrance to our city.' WHERE entry=3033;
