Text0_0_loc9='...pan fried, deep fried, and stir fried...'
Text0_0_loc9='The liquids and mixtures all bubble and spasm as you approach. Next to the equipment lies a large pair of tongs that look as though they would be adequate for dropping in samples of ooze.$B$BThere is safety gear present, but it appears to be dusty and well-ignored.$B$BYou don\'t think touching anything would be wise.'
