Text0_0_loc9='When the work of a blacksmith reaches your level of expert craftsmanship, I present them with a choice.$B$BWhile you are not required to make a choice, it is recommended that you do - after all, do you want to be a neophyte forever? It is the artisan armorsmiths and weaponsmiths that supply our armies, win our wars and garner acclaim!$B$BBe warned, $N. Once a choice is made and the tasks required completed - there is no going back. One can only walk down one path.'
