UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Certainly, $G sir:miss;. We were once servants of the house Barov: What is now known as the Scholomance.$B$BI was the head maid and Lucien was Master Barov\'s butler.$B$BWe had worked for the Barovs for decades, until...$B$B<Eva weeps.>',Text0_1_loc9='Certainly, $G sir:miss;. We were once servants of the house Barov: What is now known as the Scholomance.$B$BI was the head maid and Lucien was Master Barov\'s butler.$B$BWe had worked for the Barovs for decades, until...$B$B<Eva weeps.>',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=4042;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Oh it\'s just so horrible, $G sir:miss;. The house Barov was once full of life... full of splendor. The manor was the Barov\'s primary residence amidst their far reaching empire.$B$BLucien and I noticed that as the days progressed, the Barovs became depressed. Despondent. Paranoia and rage often overcame the master and misses. At night, we could hear the Barovs arguing in their chambers. From what we understood, their greed had \'broken the dam,\' so to speak.',Text0_1_loc9='Oh it\'s just so horrible, $G sir:miss;. The house Barov was once full of life... full of splendor. The manor was the Barov\'s primary residence amidst their far reaching empire.$B$BLucien and I noticed that as the days progressed, the Barovs became depressed. Despondent. Paranoia and rage often overcame the master and missus. At night, we could hear the Barovs arguing in their chambers. From what we understood, their greed had \'broken the dam,\' so to speak.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=4043;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='We suspect that in order to preserve their fortune and hold of the land - well past their lifespan - the Barovs made a deal with a powerful human mage named Kel\'Thuzad.$B$B<Eva shudders.>$B$BFrom this deal sprang the school of necromancy: A place which bore the Cult of the Damned and would become their capital.$B$BAs each week passed, the house Barov became more and more decrepit...$B$BDark beings began to take residence in the various wings of the house. Upkeep became impossible... and disgusting.',Text0_1_loc9='We suspect that in order to preserve their fortune and hold of the land - well past their lifespan - the Barovs made a deal with a powerful human mage named Kel\'Thuzad.$B$B<Eva shudders.>$B$BFrom this deal sprang the school of necromancy: A place which bore the Cult of the Damned and would become their capital.$B$BAs each week passed, the house Barov became more and more decrepit...$B$BDark beings began to take residence in the various wings of the house. Upkeep became impossible... and disgusting.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=4044;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='And go where? It was all that we knew; all that we had known and all that we would ever know.$B$BEventually, we lost contact with the Barovs and ultimately, were separated from the household. We knew not what happened to the other servants, only that there were screams. Tortured screams.$B$BKnowing that we had nowhere to go, Lucien and I were forced to hide in our quarters. During the day, when the school was relatively quiet, Lucien would sneak out to scrounge up food and drink.',Text0_1_loc9='And go where? It was all that we knew; all that we had known and all that we would ever know.$B$BEventually, we lost contact with the Barovs and ultimately, were separated from the household. We knew not what happened to the other servants, only that there were screams. Tortured screams.$B$BKnowing that we had nowhere to go, Lucien and I were forced to hide in our quarters. During the day, when the school was relatively quiet, Lucien would sneak out to scrounge up food and drink.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=4045;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='We did this for about six months and watched as the house went through horrifying changes. Foul monsters roamed through the manor at will. Dark cultists populated every inch with various paraphernalia relating to rituals and sacrifices. We knew that we could not hide much longer.$B$BAs expected, we were found and captured. They stripped us of all our clothes and laid us out inside a circle of blood. We sat there for days, naked and terrified.',Text0_1_loc9='We did this for about six months and watched as the house went through horrifying changes. Foul monsters roamed through the manor at will. Dark cultists populated every inch with various paraphernalia relating to rituals and sacrifices. We knew that we could not hide much longer.$B$BAs expected, we were found and captured. They stripped us of all our clothes and laid us out inside a circle of blood. We sat there for days, naked and terrified.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=4046;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Restraints? There are things in this world far more restraining than bars and shackles, young $G master:mistress;. The undead surrounded us, constantly tormenting us with horrifying acts of depravity.$B$BFinally, he came. He introduced himself as Doctor Theolen Krastinov. We came to know him as \'The Butcher.\'',Text0_1_loc9='Restraints? There are things in this world far more restraining than bars and shackles, young $G master:mistress;. The undead surrounded us, constantly tormenting us with horrifying acts of depravity.$B$BFinally, he came. He introduced himself as Doctor Theolen Krastinov. We came to know him as \'The Butcher.\'',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=4047;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='We finally understood what the screams were from. The Butcher exposed us to pain that we did not know existed. He used us in countless experiments, attempting to devise a plague.$B$BThe days turned to weeks. We would have died on the first day had it not been for that cruel bastard keeping us alive through magical means.',Text0_1_loc9='We finally understood what the screams were from. The Butcher exposed us to pain that we did not know existed. He used us in countless experiments, attempting to devise a plague.$B$BThe days turned to weeks. We would have died on the first day had it not been for that cruel monster keeping us alive through magical means.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=4048;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The Butcher would speak of \'the blood of innocents,\' and his dark master, \'Kirtonos.\' Of how he must appease his master.$B$BFinally, the beast was done with his experiments. We had been drained of all life. Our spirits shattered. The sweet embrace of death was upon us and we welcomed it with open arms. But in his infinite cruelty, the Butcher revived us from death\'s door.$B$BWe were to be kept alive and thrown to his ravenous ghouls. He laughed as he watched the fiends devour our flesh.',Text0_1_loc9='The Butcher would speak of \'the blood of innocents,\' and his dark master, \'Kirtonos.\' Of how he must appease his master.$B$BFinally, the beast was done with his experiments. We had been drained of all life. Our spirits shattered. The sweet embrace of death was upon us and we welcomed it with open arms. But in his infinite cruelty, the Butcher revived us from death\'s door.$B$BWe were to be kept alive and thrown to his ravenous ghouls. He laughed as he watched the fiends devour our flesh.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=4049;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='We feel nothing. Our souls remain here, in limbo. We are unable to leave until our remains are found and spirits laid to rest.',Text0_1_loc9='We feel nothing. Our souls remain here, in limbo. We are unable to leave until our remains are found and spirits laid to rest.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=4050;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Ah, you must go to the great heights of Thunder Bluff to visit one of those.  Follow the path north out of Bloodhoof Village.  At the base of the bluffs is an elevator that will take you to the top.  When you get there ask for further directions from one of the Bluffwatchers.',Text0_1_loc9='Ah, you must go to the great heights of Thunder Bluff to visit one of those.  Follow the path north out of Bloodhoof Village.  At the base of the bluffs is an elevator that will take you to the top.  When you get there ask for further directions from one of the Bluffwatchers.',Text1_0_loc9='We have no such place in the village.  The soaring heights of Thunder Bluff does though.  Head north up the road out of Bloodhoof Village until you come to the base of the bluffs.  There ride the elevator to the top and speak with a Bluffwatcher.  May your ancestors watch over you.',Text1_1_loc9='We have no such place in the village.  The soaring heights of Thunder Bluff does though.  Head north up the road out of Bloodhoof Village until you come to the base of the bluffs.  There ride the elevator to the top and speak with a Bluffwatcher.  May your ancestors watch over you.' WHERE entry=4051;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='There is a Wind Rider Master in the great city of Thunder Bluff to the north.  Ride the elevator from the base of Thunder Bluff to the top and ask one of the Bluffwatchers there for further instructions.',Text0_1_loc9='There is a Wind Rider Master in the great city of Thunder Bluff to the north.  Ride the elevator from the base of Thunder Bluff to the top and ask one of the Bluffwatchers there for further instructions.',Text1_0_loc9='Nothing frees the spirit like soaring through the sky.  There is such a place in our great tribal center Thunder Bluff.  The road north out of Bloodhoof Village will guide you there.  Once you ride the elevator to the top speak with one of the Bluffwatchers who can give you further directions.',Text1_1_loc9='Nothing frees the spirit like soaring through the sky.  There is such a place in our great tribal center Thunder Bluff.  The road north out of Bloodhoof Village will guide you there.  Once you ride the elevator to the top speak with one of the Bluffwatchers who can give you further directions.' WHERE entry=4052;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Innkeeper Kauth can see to your needs.  He can be found on the west side of the village in one of the long houses.',Text0_1_loc9='Innkeeper Kauth can see to your needs.  He can be found on the west side of the village in one of the long houses.',Text1_0_loc9='There is a time and a place for all things, including relaxation.  On the west side of Bloodhoof Village Innkeeper Kauth maintains a long house for those who seek to rest.  You will find him there.',Text1_1_loc9='There is a time and a place for all things, including relaxation.  On the west side of Bloodhoof Village Innkeeper Kauth maintains a long house for those who seek to rest.  You will find him there.' WHERE entry=4053;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='It is Gennia Runetotem\'s counsel that you seek.  You will find her in the large tent on the east side of the village.',Text0_1_loc9='It is Gennia Runetotem\'s counsel that you seek.  You will find her in the large tent on the east side of the village.',Text1_0_loc9='The way of the Druid is sibling to the Shaman.  Gennia Runetotem is steeped in such knowledge.  Seek her out in the large tent on the east side of Bloodhoof Village.',Text1_1_loc9='The way of the Druid is sibling to the Shaman.  Gennia Runetotem is steeped in such knowledge.  Seek her out in the large tent on the east side of Bloodhoof Village.' WHERE entry=4054;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Yaw Sharpmane awaits you on the north edge of the village.  He can teach you the ways of the Hunter.',Text0_1_loc9='Yaw Sharpmane awaits you on the north edge of the village.  He can teach you the ways of the Hunter.',Text1_0_loc9='To learn to be one with Nature in the eyes of the Earth Mother, this is a matter of pride.  If your will is to learn the ways of the Hunter you must seek out Yaw Sharpmane at the north end of Bloodhoof Village.',Text1_1_loc9='To learn to be one with Nature in the eyes of the Earth Mother, this is a matter of pride.  If your will is to learn the ways of the Hunter you must seek out Yaw Sharpmane at the north end of Bloodhoof Village.' WHERE entry=4055;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='There is a large tent on the east side of Bloodhoof Village.  You will find Narm Skychaser awaiting you there.',Text0_1_loc9='There is a large tent on the east side of Bloodhoof Village.  You will find Narm Skychaser awaiting you there.',Text1_0_loc9='There is a wise one in the village who goes by the name Narm Skychaser.  He can continue your learning along the path of the Shaman.',Text1_1_loc9='There is a wise one in the village who goes by the name Narm Skychaser.  He can continue your learning along the path of the Shaman.' WHERE entry=4056;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Krang Stonehoof stands astride his training circle at the southeast corner of the village.',Text0_1_loc9='Krang Stonehoof stands astride his training circle at the southeast corner of the village.',Text1_0_loc9='If it is the way of the Warrior that you crave then you must seek out Krang Stonehoof.  You will find him in the southeast corner of the village at his training circle, often instructing his other students.',Text1_1_loc9='If it is the way of the Warrior that you crave then you must seek out Krang Stonehoof.  You will find him in the southeast corner of the village at his training circle, often instructing his other students.' WHERE entry=4057;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='While we have no Alchemy Trainer here in Bloodhoof Village, there is one in Thunder Bluff to the north.  Follow the road there and ask one of the Bluffwatchers for directions when you get to the top.',Text0_1_loc9='While we have no Alchemy Trainer here in Bloodhoof Village, there is one in Thunder Bluff to the north.  Follow the road there and ask one of the Bluffwatchers for directions when you get to the top.',Text1_0_loc9='Using the fruits of the Earth Mother to create potions to aid us in our eternal struggle is an honorable endeavor.  To learn of this you must travel north to our great home of Thunder Bluff.  When you arrive at the top seek out the assistance of one of the Bluffwatchers for more specific directions.',Text1_1_loc9='Using the fruits of the Earth Mother to create potions to aid us in our eternal struggle is an honorable endeavor.  To learn of this you must travel north to our great home of Thunder Bluff.  When you arrive at the top seek out the assistance of one of the Bluffwatchers for more specific directions.' WHERE entry=4058;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='There is a Blacksmithing Trainer in our great home Thunder Bluff to the north.  If you seek such knowledge then head there and ask one of the Bluffwatchers for directions.',Text0_1_loc9='There is a Blacksmithing Trainer in our great home Thunder Bluff to the north.  If you seek such knowledge then head there and ask one of the Bluffwatchers for directions.',Text1_0_loc9='You desire to shape the bones of the Earth Mother into tools that will aid the Horde.  Good, good.  Follow the path north out of Bloodhoof Village until you come to the elevator leading to the top of Thunder Bluff.  A Bluffwatcher there can give you further assistance.',Text1_1_loc9='You desire to shape the bones of the Earth Mother into tools that will aid the Horde.  Good, good.  Follow the path north out of Bloodhoof Village until you come to the elevator leading to the top of Thunder Bluff.  A Bluffwatcher there can give you further assistance.' WHERE entry=4059;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You will find Pyall Silentstride inside the great tent in the northwest corner of the village.  He can teach you what you crave.',Text0_1_loc9='You will find Pyall Silentstride inside the great tent in the northwest corner of the village.  He can teach you what you crave.',Text1_0_loc9='My mouth waters just to think on it.  Pyall Silentstride is the finest cook in Bloodhoof Village.  You will find him in the great tent at the northwest corner of the village.',Text1_1_loc9='My mouth waters just to think on it.  Pyall Silentstride is the finest cook in Bloodhoof Village.  You will find him in the great tent at the northwest corner of the village.' WHERE entry=4060;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Away to Thunder Bluff to the north is where your journey takes you then friend.  Once there seek out the wisdom of one of the Bluffwatchers who can tell you directly where to find whom you seek.',Text0_1_loc9='Away to Thunder Bluff to the north is where your journey takes you then friend.  Once there seek out the wisdom of one of the Bluffwatchers who can tell you directly where to find whom you seek.',Text1_0_loc9='Such wisdom is steeped in a mystery that can only be found in great Thunder Bluff.  Follow the path north out of Bloodhoof Village until you come to an elevator at the base of the bluffs.  Ride it to the top and ask one of the Bluffwatchers for further assistance.',Text1_1_loc9='Such wisdom is steeped in a mystery that can only be found in great Thunder Bluff.  Follow the path north out of Bloodhoof Village until you come to an elevator at the base of the bluffs.  Ride it to the top and ask one of the Bluffwatchers for further assistance.' WHERE entry=4061;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Vira Younghoof keeps her practice inside the long house on the west side of the village.',Text0_1_loc9='Vira Younghoof keeps her practice inside the long house on the west side of the village.',Text1_0_loc9='Bandages, anti-venoms and such things, these are the inevitable necessities of life on the plains.  Vira Younghoof can teach you this knowledge.  You can find her in the long house on the west side of Bloodhoof Village.',Text1_1_loc9='Bandages, anti-venoms and such things, these are the inevitable necessities of life on the plains.  Vira Younghoof can teach you this knowledge.  You can find her in the long house on the west side of Bloodhoof Village.' WHERE entry=4062;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You are looking for Uthan Stillwater.  You will find him west of the village, fishing at Stonebull Lake.',Text0_1_loc9='You are looking for Uthan Stillwater.  You will find him west of the village, fishing at Stonebull Lake.',Text1_0_loc9='Give a bull a fish and feed him for a day.  Teach a bull to fish and feed him for life.  Uthan Stillwater can teach you how to fish.  Seek his wisdom west of Bloodhoof Village along the banks of Stonebull Lake.',Text1_1_loc9='Give a bull a fish and feed him for a day.  Teach a bull to fish and feed him for life.  Uthan Stillwater can teach you how to fish.  Seek his wisdom west of Bloodhoof Village along the banks of Stonebull Lake.' WHERE entry=4063;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='If you desire to learn the ways of Herbalism then it is to Thunder Bluff that you must go.  Follow the road north out of Bloodhoof Village and take the elevator to the top of the rise.  You can ask a Bluffwatcher there for further assistance.',Text0_1_loc9='If you desire to learn the ways of Herbalism then it is to Thunder Bluff that you must go.  Follow the road north out of Bloodhoof Village and take the elevator to the top of the rise.  You can ask a Bluffwatcher there for further assistance.',Text1_0_loc9='There are those that would teach you of Herbalism in the great home of Thunder Bluff away to the north.  Follow the road out of the village to get there and at the base of the bluff ride the elevator to the top of the rise.  There are many Bluffwatchers there who can direct you further.',Text1_1_loc9='There are those that would teach you of Herbalism in the great home of Thunder Bluff away to the north.  Follow the road out of the village to get there and at the base of the bluff ride the elevator to the top of the rise.  There are many Bluffwatchers there who can direct you further.' WHERE entry=4064;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Inside the great tent at the northwest corner of the village is where Chaw Stronghide resides.  He will teach you what you must know of Leatherworking for now.',Text0_1_loc9='Inside the great tent at the northwest corner of the village is where Chaw Stronghide resides.  He will teach you what you must know of Leatherworking for now.',Text1_0_loc9='When we use the hides of the animals we must fell for food or protection we give honor to the Earth Mother and respect to the animal.  Chaw Stronghide can teach you of such things.  You will find him in the great tent at the northwest corner of Bloodhoof Village.',Text1_1_loc9='When we use the hides of the animals we must fell for food or protection we give honor to the Earth Mother and respect to the animal.  Chaw Stronghide can teach you of such things.  You will find him in the great tent at the northwest corner of Bloodhoof Village.' WHERE entry=4065;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Hmmm, I think you will need to go up to Thunder Bluff to learn that.  Head north on the road out of Bloodhoof Village.  It will take you to the base of Thunder Bluff.  Ride the elevator to the top and you should be able to ask any of the Bluffwatchers there for further assistance.',Text0_1_loc9='Hmmm, I think you will need to go up to Thunder Bluff to learn that.  Head north on the road out of Bloodhoof Village.  It will take you to the base of Thunder Bluff.  Ride the elevator to the top and you should be able to ask any of the Bluffwatchers there for further assistance.',Text1_0_loc9='I hear that they have a Mining Trainer in Thunder Bluff to the north.  Take the road out of the village and when you get there ride the elevator to the top of the rise.  Any of the Bluffwatchers should be able to help you from there.',Text1_1_loc9='I hear that they have a Mining Trainer in Thunder Bluff to the north.  Take the road out of the village and when you get there ride the elevator to the top of the rise.  Any of the Bluffwatchers should be able to help you from there.' WHERE entry=4066;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Yonn Deepcut can be found inside the great tent at the northwest corner of Bloodhoof Village.',Text0_1_loc9='Yonn Deepcut can be found inside the great tent at the northwest corner of Bloodhoof Village.',Text1_0_loc9='Ah yes, Skinning.  There is no one finer in wielding a skinning knife than Yonn Deepcut.  You can find him in the great tent at the northwest corner of the village.',Text1_1_loc9='Ah yes, Skinning.  There is no one finer in wielding a skinning knife than Yonn Deepcut.  You can find him in the great tent at the northwest corner of the village.' WHERE entry=4067;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Unfortunately we do not have one who teaches Tailoring here in Bloodhoof Village, but you can find a trainer in Thunder Bluff.  Follow the path north out of the village until you come to a set of elevators.  Take one up to the top of the rise and ask one of the Bluffwatchers there for directions.',Text0_1_loc9='Unfortunately we do not have one who teaches Tailoring here in Bloodhoof Village, but you can find a trainer in Thunder Bluff.  Follow the path north out of the village until you come to a set of elevators.  Take one up to the top of the rise and ask one of the Bluffwatchers there for directions.',Text1_0_loc9='Tailoring you say?  Hmmm.  Ah yes, of course.  You\'ll need to head to Thunder Bluff, up north.  Take the path out of the village to get there.  When you arrive at the base of the bluffs ride the elevator to the top of the rise and speak with one of the Bluffwatchers.',Text1_1_loc9='Tailoring you say?  Hmmm.  Ah yes, of course.  You\'ll need to head to Thunder Bluff, up north.  Take the path out of the village to get there.  When you arrive at the base of the bluffs ride the elevator to the top of the rise and speak with one of the Bluffwatchers.' WHERE entry=4068;
