Text0_0_loc9='I\'ve heard that there\'s a dwarf in Stormwind who has achieved some fame for his hunting skill.  Maybe you should go see if he could help you.',Text0_1_loc9='I\'ve heard that there\'s a dwarf in Stormwind who has achieved some fame for his hunting skill.  Maybe you should go see if he could help you.'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Josetta has been a blessing to this town with her aid of the local guards.  If you seek her for training in the ways of a priest, you can find her in the Lion\'s Pride Inn.',Text0_1_loc9='Josetta has been a blessing to this town with her aid of the local guards.  If you seek her for training in the ways of a priest, you can find her in the Lion\'s Pride Inn.',Text1_0_loc9='I bet Josetta would be more than happy to teach you some new spells.  She is probably up in her room at the Lion\'s Pride Inn.',Text1_1_loc9='I bet Josetta would be more than happy to teach you some new spells.  She is probably up in her room at the Lion\'s Pride Inn.' WHERE entry=4267;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Zaldimar could probably teach you some new spells.  He has recently taken a liking to staying at the Lion\'s Pride Inn, you might want to check one of the rooms and see if he\'s in.',Text0_1_loc9='Zaldimar could probably teach you some new spells.  He has recently taken a liking to staying at the Lion\'s Pride Inn, you might want to check one of the rooms and see if he\'s in.',Text1_0_loc9='I don\'t know much about magic, but there\'s a mage named Zaldimar who is staying at the Lion\'s Pride Inn that could probably assist you.',Text1_1_loc9='I don\'t know much about magic, but there\'s a mage named Zaldimar who is staying at the Lion\'s Pride Inn that could probably assist you.' WHERE entry=4268;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You can usually find Brother Wilhelm in back of the smithy trading stories with Lyria.  He\'s always up for teaching fellow paladins new skills.',Text0_1_loc9='You can usually find Brother Wilhelm in back of the smithy trading stories with Lyria.  He\'s always up for teaching fellow paladins new skills.',Text1_0_loc9='Brother Wilhelm often trains with Lyria Du Lac out in back of the smithy in Goldshire.  You could probably learn a thing or two about being a paladin from him.',Text1_1_loc9='Brother Wilhelm often trains with Lyria Du Lac out in back of the smithy in Goldshire.  You could probably learn a thing or two about being a paladin from him.' WHERE entry=4269;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='A rogue?  Hmmm... well, I\'ve heard that Keryn Sylvius hangs around those shady types.  You might want to talk to her and see what you can learn.',Text0_1_loc9='A rogue?  Hmmm... well, I\'ve heard that Keryn Sylvius hangs around those shady types.  You might want to talk to her and see what you can learn.',Text1_0_loc9='I\'d wager Keryn Sylvius knows the type you\'re looking for. The company Keryn keeps is less than honorable. She usually hangs out in the Lion\'s Pride Inn.',Text1_1_loc9='I\'d wager Keryn Sylvius knows the type you\'re looking for. The company Keryn keeps is less than honorable. She usually hangs out in the Lion\'s Pride Inn.' WHERE entry=4270;
