UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='To reach the Rut\'theran Ferry, you will need to travel to Darnassus and take the portal to Rut\'theran Village at the base of Teldrassil.',Text0_1_loc9='To reach the Rut\'theran Ferry, you will need to travel to Darnassus and take the portal to Rut\'theran Village at the base of Teldrassil.',Text1_0_loc9='A Rut\'theran Ferry leaves for Auberdine from Rut\'theran Village at the base of Teldrassil.  The portal in Darnassus will allow you to reach Rut\'theran safely.',Text1_1_loc9='A Rut\'theran Ferry leaves for Auberdine from Rut\'theran Village at the base of Teldrassil.  The portal in Darnassus will allow you to reach Rut\'theran safely.' WHERE entry=4318;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Matters of such an official nature are only handled in Darnassus.  You must travel there to begin the process of your guild\'s creation.',Text0_1_loc9='Matters of such an official nature are only handled in Darnassus.  You must travel there to begin the process of your guild\'s creation.',Text1_0_loc9='Documents such as guild creation papers can be acquired from the Guild Master in the city of Darnassus.',Text1_1_loc9='Documents such as guild creation papers can be acquired from the Guild Master in the city of Darnassus.' WHERE entry=4319;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='A restful sleep is sure to be had in the beds which Innkeeper Keldamyr keeps at the Inn in Dolanaar.',Text0_1_loc9='A restful sleep is sure to be had in the beds which Innkeeper Keldamyr keeps at the Inn in Dolanaar.',Text1_0_loc9='If you require time to rest and regain your strength, you will find the best at the Inn in Dolanaar.  Innkeeper Keldamyr will see to it that you are taken care of.',Text1_1_loc9='If you require time to rest and regain your strength, you will find the best at the Inn in Dolanaar.  Innkeeper Keldamyr will see to it that you are taken care of.' WHERE entry=4320;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You seek the aid of a Druid?  Then you should go see Kal at the Moonwell just south of the Inn in Dolanaar.',Text0_1_loc9='You seek the aid of a Druid?  Then you should go see Kal at the Moonwell just south of the Inn in Dolanaar.',Text1_0_loc9='The druid, Kal, often spends his time at the moonwell in Dolanaar.  I am certain he would be able to provide you with the training you require.',Text1_1_loc9='The druid, Kal, often spends his time at the moonwell in Dolanaar.  I am certain he would be able to provide you with the training you require.' WHERE entry=4323;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='If a hunter is whom you seek, then it is Dazalar that you should visit.  He can usually be found just outside the Inn in Dolanaar.',Text0_1_loc9='If a hunter is whom you seek, then it is Dazalar that you should visit.  He can usually be found just outside the Inn in Dolanaar.',Text1_0_loc9='Dazalar is well known around Dolanaar for his hunting skill.  Why don\'t you talk to him and see what he can teach you?',Text1_1_loc9='Dazalar is well known around Dolanaar for his hunting skill.  Why don\'t you talk to him and see what he can teach you?' WHERE entry=4324;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='A priestess by the name of Laurna Morninglight calls Dolanaar home.  I believe she can be found just north of the Inn.',Text0_1_loc9='A priestess by the name of Laurna Morninglight calls Dolanaar home.  I believe she can be found just north of the Inn.',Text1_0_loc9='Laurna Morninglight offers healing to those that live around Dolanaar.  Perhaps she would be able to teach you in the ways of a priest.',Text1_1_loc9='Laurna Morninglight offers healing to those that live around Dolanaar.  Perhaps she would be able to teach you in the ways of a priest.' WHERE entry=4325;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='A rogue?  I\'m not in the habit of referring people to those types, but I believe Jannok would be the one you\'re looking for.  You will find him at the Inn in Dolanaar.',Text0_1_loc9='A rogue?  I\'m not in the habit of referring people to those types, but I believe Jannok would be the one you\'re looking for.  You will find him at the Inn in Dolanaar.',Text1_0_loc9='You seek a rogue?  I believe Jannok would fit that description.  Why don\'t you go talk to him over at the Inn in Dolanaar.',Text1_1_loc9='You seek a rogue?  I believe Jannok would fit that description.  Why don\'t you go talk to him over at the Inn in Dolanaar.' WHERE entry=4326;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Kyra Windblade wields her blade with great skill.  She should be able to provide you with some training.  You\'ll find her at the Inn in Dolanaar.',Text0_1_loc9='Kyra Windblade wields her blade with great skill.  She should be able to provide you with some training.  You\'ll find her at the Inn in Dolanaar.',Text1_0_loc9='I had the pleasure of seeing Kyra Windblade in combat once.  Considering what I witnessed, I am confident she will train you well.  Look for her at the Inn in Dolanaar.',Text1_1_loc9='I had the pleasure of seeing Kyra Windblade in combat once.  Considering what I witnessed, I am confident she will train you well.  Look for her at the Inn in Dolanaar.' WHERE entry=4327;
