Text0_0_loc9='I train and guide young hunters in the traditions passed down many generations.'
Text0_0_loc9='Remember, all things are connected. If the beasts were gone from the land, our kind would die from a great loneliness of spirit, for whatever happens to the beasts also happens to the Tauren. Whatever befalls Azeroth befalls all those that inhabit it. $B'
Text0_0_loc9='If you\'re here to be trained in the tactics and strategy of hunting, you\'ve come to the right place!'
Text0_0_loc9='Hey mon! You\'ve ever been diving deep in the ocean? I\'ll let you in on a little secret, eh. Deep in the ocean you can find bubbly fissures; they\'ll allow you to breathe air while underwater.  Let\'s keep this secret between you and me though, eh. I don\'t need no competition for me shellfish traps elsewhere... if you get my drift!
'
