Text0_0_loc9='Before the Scourge came, I had a great business.  I bought and sold everything.  Everything!$B$BAnd my prices were INSANE!$B$BJust ask anyone.  Anyone who\'s not dead.'
Text0_0_loc9='Hi $N!  Are you here to buy something?  Or maybe sell something?$B$BYou won\'t find better prices anywhere, or my name isn\'t Augustus the Touched!'
Text0_0_loc9='This is a dangerous place, $N. Be careful around here.'
