Text0_0_loc9='Where are you going?  Well if you\'re looking to get there quickly, then look no further!'
Text0_0_loc9='I try to keep Sentinel Hill stocked, and that\'s not easy with all the action we see.'
Text0_0_loc9='A mere three hundred years ago, a reckless dwarf named Thaurissan summoned the master from his fiery realm. His return to this paltry world devastated the surrounding lands and created this volcanic Core. Mighty Ragnaros has slept under this mountain ever since. $B$B',Text0_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text0:'
Text0_0_loc9='We, his sworn servants, do his bidding and enforce his iron-rule. Cut off from the energies of his fiery realm, Ragnaros is but a shadow of his true self. However, he has more than enough strength to be your end.      $B$B',Text0_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text0:'
Text0_0_loc9='Good day, $Gsir:ma\'am;. I\'d shake your hand, but as you see, I\'m in the middle of something. May I be of assistance?'
Text0_0_loc9='You\'ve made a good start, but you still have a great deal to learn, $N.'
Text0_0_loc9='You\'ve already learned everything I can teach you, $N. Talk to the night elf Lilyssia Nightbreeze in the Mage Quarter of Stormwind if you want to continue your studies. I hear she\'s a good teacher.'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Shut inside this little house, I dream of joining the battles that rage outside the city walls. Still, duty compels me to share my knowledge with others who fight in my stead... for now.',Text0_1_loc9='Shut inside this little house, I dream of joining the battles that rage outside the city walls. Still, duty compels me to share my knowledge with others who fight in my stead... for now.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5016;
Text0_0_loc9='Ishnu-alah, $Gbrother:sister;. Have you any tidings from abroad? My heart yearns for news of Teldrassil.'
Text0_0_loc9='I am honored to share my knowledge with you, $N. See that you use it well.'
Text0_0_loc9='You must choose a more experienced teacher, for you have surpassed my abilities. I advise you to speak with Lilyssia Nightbreeze here: she has much knowledge to offer.'
