Text0_0_loc9='I don\'t suppose you\'re here to talk about my lovely Kali. Fine, then. Potions it is. Anyone ever tell ye you\'ve got a one-track mind?'
Text0_0_loc9='Ye\'re beyond my skill to teach, $N. Go pester Tally Berryfizz; she\'s a gnome living in Tinker Town of Ironforge. Oh, and since you\'re headed up anyway, give Kali my love.'
Text0_0_loc9='Don\'t let those big, innocent eyes fool ye. Tally\'s an expert, all right: I learn something new every day. Why d\'you think I\'m here in Tinker Town? Do I look like an engineer to you? Aye, I didn\'t think so.'
Text0_0_loc9='Put your back into it, $Glad:lass;. Hard work and determination--that\'s the way! Don\'t let anyone tell you book learnin\' is all ye need.'
Text0_0_loc9='Och, there\'s nothing I can teach ye, $N. Have a word with Tally Berryfizz over there. She can hardly reach the tables, but when she starts brewing a potion, watch out!'
Text0_0_loc9='You got the look of someone wantin\' adventure. Me, I had enough of that by the time we trolls came here. Now I take each day as it comes, an\' I train other folks to handle adventures for me.'
Text0_0_loc9='Ready for another lesson? All right, then. First, relax. You gotta stay loose to stir a potion just right.'
Text0_0_loc9='You got questions, but they be too big for me to answer, $N. You be needin\' to have words with the orc Yelmak in the Drag of Orgrimmar. He\'ll help you out.'
Text0_0_loc9='All the bottles on this table are potions I brewed today. And they say a watched pot never boils. Ha!'
Text0_0_loc9='They called me stupid, but I\'ll show them. I\'m going to watch every pot I have and prove that they can all boil stuff anyway. Yeah, I\'m on a roll! Who\'s stupid now, huh? Huh!?'
Text0_0_loc9='Can\'t help you. You know more about potions than I do. Besides, I have pots to watch. Talk to Yelmak over there. He knows a lot about potions.'
Text0_0_loc9='Bena works like one possessed. Day and night I have seen her bent over these potions, often going without sleep or food. I know our undead allies need help, but I begin to fear she will do herself an injury.'
Text0_0_loc9='I must have broken hundreds of vials when I first began brewing potions. The glass was so fragile in my clumsy hands. I hope you are more cautious than I was.'
Text0_0_loc9='Your capacity for learning has outstripped mine. You will need to talk to Bena Winterhoof over there for further instruction. Please don\'t take too much of her time, though. She needs her rest.'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Nice to see a friendly face. I don\'t get much chitchat from Apothecary Johaan unless he wants something. He\'s been out of the grave too long. Someday I\'ll be like that, I hear. Creepy. Maybe by then I won\'t care.',Text0_1_loc9='Nice to see a friendly face. I don\'t get much chitchat from Apothecary Johaan unless he wants something. He\'s been out of the grave too long. Someday I\'ll be like that, I hear. Creepy. Maybe by then I won\'t care.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5043;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Here to learn about potions? I\'ve got plenty to teach you. I might be dead, but I haven\'t lost my brains. Yet.',Text0_1_loc9='Here to learn about potions? I\'ve got plenty to teach you. I might be dead, but I haven\'t lost my brains. Yet.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5044;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I appreciate the company, but let\'s face it: you have more experience with potions than I do. Talk to Doctor Marsh instead if you want training. He\'s a Forsaken in the Apothecarium of the Undercity.',Text0_1_loc9='I appreciate the company, but let\'s face it: you have more experience with potions than I do. Talk to Doctor Marsh instead if you want training. He\'s a Forsaken in the Apothecarium of the Undercity.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5045;
Text0_0_loc9='Once, it is true, I was human. What might otherwise be a shortcoming works to our advantage, $N, for I know human weaknesses intimately.'
Text0_0_loc9='Very well. Cut another lump of flesh from one of these specimens. Let us test what you\'ve learned so far, and we can progress from there.'
Text0_0_loc9='Your knowledge of potions has exceeded mine, but you still have much to learn. Go up the stairs to the southeast and see Doctor Marsh. He will teach you true sufferi--ahem. He is a Forsaken who will train you further.'
Text0_0_loc9='Stop giving me that look. I may not be an adventurer like you, but that doesn\'t mean I can\'t have a few muscles. All that stirring makes your arms strong.'
Text0_0_loc9='There\'s nothing more I can teach you. I\'ve heard of a night elf who might be able to, though. Her name is Ainethil, and she lives in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace of Darnassus.'
Text0_0_loc9='I\'m sorry, $N, but I have no time to spend on novices. You want someone closer to your own skill level. Try the night elf Milla Fairancora, in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace of Darnassus.'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='' WHERE entry=5053;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Don\'t let the beady eyes and bushy beard fool you. Vosur\'s a talented apprentice and a good friend, even if I do get a crick in my neck when I talk to him.',Text0_1_loc9='Don\'t let the beady eyes and bushy beard fool you. Vosur\'s a talented apprentice and a good friend, even if I do get a crick in my neck when I talk to him.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5054;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Um, you already know everything I could teach you. Maybe it\'s time for you to talk to someone else. Try the night elf Ainethil in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace of Darnassus. She\'s got some real talent!',Text0_1_loc9='Um, you already know everything I could teach you. Maybe it\'s time for you to talk to someone else. Try the night elf Ainethil in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace of Darnassus. She\'s got some real talent!',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5055;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='That\'s nice, $N. Go show whatever it is to Vosur over there. He\'ll answer any questions you have.',Text0_1_loc9='That\'s nice, $N. Go show whatever it is to Vosur over there. He\'ll answer any questions you have.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5057;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Who are you and why are you bothering me? Oh, right--potions student. Right. What can I do for you?',Text0_1_loc9='Who are you and why are you bothering me? Oh, right--potions student. Right. What can I do for you?',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5058;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Ishnu-dal-dieb, $N. Have you come here in search of knowledge?',Text0_1_loc9='Ishnu-dal-dieb, $N. Have you come here in search of knowledge?',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5059;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Teaching is not a one-sided trade, $N. As I teach you, I learn more myself, and my understanding grows.',Text0_1_loc9='Teaching is not a one-sided trade, $N. As I teach you, I learn more myself, and my understanding grows.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5060;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Although I am flattered by your confidence in my abilities, teaching you is beyond my skill. You must go to the Craftsmen\'s Terrace in Darnassus, and speak with the night elf Ainethil. She can help you.',Text0_1_loc9='Although I am flattered by your confidence in my abilities, teaching you is beyond my skill. You must go to the Craftsmen\'s Terrace in Darnassus, and speak with the night elf Ainethil. She can help you.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5063;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Even slight alterations to a potion\'s ingredients can change it fundamentally. Patience and precision, young one: they will serve you well in all walks of life.',Text0_1_loc9='Even slight alterations to a potion\'s ingredients can change it fundamentally. Patience and precision, young one: they will serve you well in all walks of life.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5064;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='My skill at creating potions is inferior to yours. You are ready to speak with Ainethil, just over there. She will understand that you are ready for further instruction.',Text0_1_loc9='My skill at creating potions is inferior to yours. You are ready to speak with Ainethil, just over there. She will understand that you are ready for further instruction.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5065;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Ah, to be young again, and to have discovered potions for the first time. Thank you for refreshing my memory, $N. Now go share that youthful enthusiasm with Milla Fairancora over there.',Text0_1_loc9='Ah, to be young again, and to have discovered potions for the first time. Thank you for refreshing my memory, $N. Now go share that youthful enthusiasm with Milla Fairancora over there.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5067;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I have learned much of potions over the long years, $N, and that knowledge is at your disposal. You have only to ask.',Text0_1_loc9='I have learned much of potions over the long years, $N, and that knowledge is at your disposal. You have only to ask.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5068;
Text0_0_loc9='I\'m busy, $N. Tell Whuut to handle whatever it is. That young pup has been stewing all day long. He spends much more time like that, and he\'s going to hurt something.'
Text0_0_loc9='I\'m honored to meet you, $N, but your skill at potions is greater than my own. Go see Doctor Herbert Halsey, an undead in the Apothecarium of the Undercity. He can help you from now on.'
Text0_0_loc9='You\'re talking to the wrong orc. I don\'t train novices. Talk to young Whuut over there... and use small words.'
Text0_0_loc9='Another student, eh? All right. I\'ll see what I can do to help you out.'
Text0_0_loc9='Glyx and I have an understanding: he keeps me supplied, and I keep him rich. Seriously! What that pirate charges me for a measly pouch of crumpled kingsblood... it\'s enough to make a grown goblin cry.'
Text0_0_loc9='I\'ve got plenty of great recipes for you to take a look at, and at discounted prices, too!'
Text0_0_loc9='You\'re better at this gig than I am! You want someone with even more experience than I\'ve got. That\'d be Ainethil, a night elf lady who lives in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace of Darnassus.'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='When I first saw the undead, I wept, for I could not imagine their horror and loneliness. The Earth Mother spoke to me then; she sang in my blood. And she told me, "Save them."',Text0_1_loc9='When I first saw the undead, I wept, for I could not imagine their horror and loneliness. The Earth Mother spoke to me then; she sang in my blood. And she told me, "Save them."',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5079;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Can you not sense the anguish of the Earth Mother for her lost children, the undead? Speak quickly, $N. Every second costs me dearly. We must help them find their way back to her!',Text0_1_loc9='Can you not sense the anguish of the Earth Mother for her lost children, the undead? Speak quickly, $N. Every second costs me dearly. We must help them find their way back to her!',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5080;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I cannot in good conscience spend time training novices while our allies, the undead, are suffering so terribly. Please speak with Kray over there instead; he can help you for now.',Text0_1_loc9='I cannot in good conscience spend time training novices while our allies, the undead, are suffering so terribly. Please speak with Kray over there instead; he can help you for now.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5081;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Your potion-making skills are beyond mine. Seek out the undead Doctor Herbert Halsey in the Apothecarium of the Undercity. He has the skill to train you further, and you can witness firsthand his people\'s plight.',Text0_1_loc9='Your potion-making skills are beyond mine. Seek out the undead Doctor Herbert Halsey in the Apothecarium of the Undercity. He has the skill to train you further, and you can witness firsthand his people\'s plight.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5083;
Text0_0_loc9='Another interruption. How am I supposed to get any work done like this? Don\'t answer that; do I look as if I care what you have to say? Why don\'t you go bother Mr. High-And-Mighty instead?'
Text0_0_loc9='Me, train you? Come on--we both know I can\'t. It\'s this teaching, you see. My own skills suffer. You want training, go to Doctor Herbert Halsey, a Forsaken in the Apothecarium of the Undercity.'
Text0_0_loc9='Don\'t waste my time. I have research projects older than you. Go talk to Doctor Martin Felben in the Apothecarium of the Undercity. He\'s a Forsaken who can probably manage to teach you the basics.'
Text0_0_loc9='Another student. Wonderful. This is why Lydon belongs to the Royal Society of Snobs and gets to do research, and I\'m stuck being an instructor. If I win another teaching award, I\'ll never live it down!'
Text0_0_loc9='With Algernon to keep me supplied, I can do all my work here without hunting for a single herb. If I never have to see the wonders of nature again, it won\'t be too soon.'
Text0_0_loc9='I have no more knowledge to bestow upon you. Go through the archway and down the ramp to the southeast, and talk to Doctor Herbert Halsey. He is a Forsaken who can teach you more advanced techniques.'
Text0_0_loc9='I\'m not amused by your audacity in coming to me for training. Go through the archway and down the ramp to the southeast, and talk to Doctor Martin Felben. He is a Forsaken who can teach you the basics.'
Text0_0_loc9='Here to learn? Very well. I suppose you can\'t cause our allies much harm if I teach you. Just as long as you actually do manage to harm our enemies.'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='This potion seems to heal less damage every time I brew it, though I use the same ingredients. There can be only one conclusion: the plants are changing. I cannot say why or into what.',Text0_1_loc9='This potion seems to heal less damage every time I brew it, though I use the same ingredients. There can be only one conclusion: the plants are changing. I cannot say why or into what.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5094;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='It is time you moved on to a more advanced teacher. In the Feathermoon Stronghold of Feralas dwells the night elf Kylanna Windwhisper. She has a brilliant mind; doubtless she can train you further.',Text0_1_loc9='It is time you moved on to a more advanced teacher. In the Feathermoon Stronghold of Feralas dwells the night elf Kylanna Windwhisper. She has a brilliant mind; doubtless she can train you further.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5095;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Your skill at brewing potions needs to be greater before you can become one of my students. In the meantime, perhaps Sylvanna Forestmoon or Milla Fairancora can help you, just over there.',Text0_1_loc9='Your skill at brewing potions needs to be greater before you can become one of my students. In the meantime, perhaps Sylvanna Forestmoon or Milla Fairancora can help you, just over there.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5097;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Your education is progressing well. You should be proud of your accomplishments.',Text0_1_loc9='Your education is progressing well. You should be proud of your accomplishments.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5098;
Text0_0_loc9='My colleagues and I are gathering the deadliest substances we know and testing their effects on our enemies. Once I have everything I need, I shall brew such plagues as this world has never seen.'
Text0_0_loc9='Incredible. Your potions display a knowledge that rivals my own. I cannot train you further, but talk to the orc Rogvar of Stonard in the Swamp of Sorrows. He\'s known for his cutting-edge experiments.'
Text0_0_loc9='You don\'t yet have the skill to study with me. Go talk to Doctor Martin Felben over there, or go up the ramp to the southeast and see Doctor Marsh. They are Forsaken who can give you the training you need.'
Text0_0_loc9='Ready for training? Then try to keep up, $N. We\'ve got a lot of ground to cover.'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Once I welcomed darkness, for it was the sister of night. Now it is dark all the time, even during the day, and the forests cry out for sustenance. Unless we act soon, this spreading blight will cover the world.',Text0_1_loc9='Once I welcomed darkness, for it was the sister of night. Now it is dark all the time, even during the day, and the forests cry out for sustenance. Unless we act soon, this spreading blight will cover the world.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5104;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Have you come here for instruction in the art of making potions? You were mistaken if you thought that I would offer such a privilege to you, unearned. Go, and do not return to me until you have greater skill.',Text0_1_loc9='Have you come here for instruction in the art of making potions? You were mistaken if you thought that I would offer such a privilege to you, unearned. Go, and do not return to me until you have greater skill.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5105;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Your skill displays an enduring affection for our art, but I would see further evidence of your commitment. I shall charge you with a task. Fulfill it, and I will be content.',Text0_1_loc9='Your skill displays an enduring affection for our art, but I would see further evidence of your commitment. I shall charge you with a task. Fulfill it, and I will be content.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5106;
Text0_0_loc9='Warchief Thrall himself asked me to come out here. I was honored to obey, and it\'s no hardship. I couldn\'t have asked for a better posting than Stonard. Just about any herb I might need grows in the muck here.'
Text0_0_loc9='Hmm, well, I can see that you have a little skill at making potions. Whether you\'re worthy to be my student remains to be seen, however. I have a job for you. Impress me.'
Text0_0_loc9='How dare you ask me for training, maggot? What were you hoping for, you slack-jawed yokel, a lecture on the proper uses of silverleaf? Out! You\'re lucky I don\'t thrash you senseless for wasting my time.'
Text0_0_loc9='Just a minor adjustment here... ah there we go!'
Text0_0_loc9='I would train ye if I could, but ye need the services of someone a bit more... what\'s the word? Brainy! Look for Trixie Quickswitch in Ironforge. Tell \'er Bronk sent ye!'
Text0_0_loc9='Lookin\' to be an engineer, eh? Well, by Muradin, ye\'ve come to the right place!'
Text0_0_loc9='Where\'s my spinner? I just had it here somewhere...'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='' WHERE entry=5116;
Text0_0_loc9='I would be delighted to aid you in the commencement of your pursuit! Let me grab my spinner and we\'ll get started...'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I heard the new Henweigh 6000 will be rolling off the assembly line soon. I can barely contain my excitement!',Text0_1_loc9='I heard the new Henweigh 6000 will be rolling off the assembly line soon. I can barely contain my excitement!',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5118;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Well... I hate to admit it, but my sister\'s the one you\'ll have to talk to if you want to continue training. I don\'t know as much as she does... yet! She\'s standing over by the rocket car.',Text0_1_loc9='Well... I hate to admit it, but my sister\'s the one you\'ll have to talk to if you want to continue training. I don\'t know as much as she does... yet! She\'s standing over by the rocket car.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5119;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I\'d love to teach you! Show my sister she\'s not the only one who knows a thing or two about engineering...',Text0_1_loc9='I\'d love to teach you! Show my sister she\'s not the only one who knows a thing or two about engineering...',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5120;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Hello there! My name\'s Jenna! And you?',Text0_1_loc9='Hello there! My name\'s Jenna! And you?',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5121;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Oh, you\'ve got oodles of things to learn still. I would teach you everything if I could, but I\'m still learning too! Why don\'t you talk to Trixie Quickswitch in Ironforge, she\'ll help you further your education!',Text0_1_loc9='Oh, you\'ve got oodles of things to learn still. I would teach you everything if I could, but I\'m still learning too! Why don\'t you talk to Trixie Quickswitch in Ironforge, she\'ll help you further your education!',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5122;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You want to train? With me? Fantastic! The only thing better than assembling bullets and explosive devices is to share that knowledge with someone else! Let\'s get started!',Text0_1_loc9='You want to train? With me? Fantastic! The only thing better than assembling bullets and explosive devices is to share that knowledge with someone else! Let\'s get started!',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5123;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Ah, what a beautiful day to blow something up!',Text0_1_loc9='Ah, what a beautiful day to blow something up!',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5124;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You need to start learning things that are beyond my expertise! Talk to Lilliam Sparkspindle in front of the tent there. He\'ll set you on the right course!',Text0_1_loc9='You need to start learning things that are beyond my expertise! Talk to Lilliam Sparkspindle in front of the tent there. He\'ll set you on the right course!',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5125;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='This kind of work isn\'t for the faint of heart. I have an uncle who lost a hand! Poor old Stumpy... anyway, if you\'re still interested I might be able to show you a few things.',Text0_1_loc9='This kind of work isn\'t for the faint of heart. I have an uncle who lost a hand! Poor old Stumpy... anyway, if you\'re still interested I might be able to show you a few things.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5126;
Text0_0_loc9='What? You want something?'
Text0_0_loc9='I can\'t help ya\'! You\'re ready to see someone who\'s been at it longer than I have! Let\'s see... you\'re an Alliance type, so you need to talk to Lilliam Sparkspindle in Stormwind.'
Text0_0_loc9='Yeah, I\'ll show you a few things. We\'ll see how you do, maybe you\'ll surprise me!'
Text0_0_loc9='(Sniff, sniff) You smell that? Don\'t you just LOVE the smell of grease?'
Text0_0_loc9='I\'m afraid you\'re out of my league, friend! You should go see Nogg in Orgrimmar, he\'ll take you to the next level!'
Text0_0_loc9='I like to build stuff. Of course, I like to blow stuff up even more!'
Text0_0_loc9='You know who can really show you some things? Nogg! You go find him in Orgrimmar.'
Text0_0_loc9='I know a few things. You want me to show you?'
Text0_0_loc9='Who says Orcs aren\'t smart? It takes a lot of brains to be an engineer!'
Text0_0_loc9='You know who\'s really smart? Nogg! Smarter than me, even. You go tell Nogg Thund sent you! You can find him by the control panel over there.'
Text0_0_loc9='You think you\'re smart enough? You think you got what it takes? Let\'s find out!'
Text0_0_loc9='The Dark Lady has said that knowledge will be our greatest weapon in this war.'
Text0_0_loc9='You are ready for greater things! See Franklin Lloyd, to my right. He will guide you from now on.'
Text0_0_loc9='Engineering will provide you with the skills and knowledge to dismantle your opponents! Let me show you how...'
Text0_0_loc9='I\'m never too busy to speak to a stranger! Almost never, anyway...'
Text0_0_loc9='You\'re working your way up??? higher than me, at this point! You should talk to Springspindle Fizzlegear in Ironforge! He\'ll show you more than I ever could!'
Text0_0_loc9='I can show you a few tricks... if you don\'t mind doing a little something first, that is.'
Text0_0_loc9='Hmm well, I can\'t help you quite yet! You have to learn the basics first. Why don\'t you go see Sprite Jumpsprocket in Stormwind!'
Text0_0_loc9='Fantastic! Aren\'t you the industrious one? Well, let\'s get started, shall we?'
Text0_0_loc9='Let\'s see... fourteen plus seven, carry the two... oh, yes?'
Text0_0_loc9='Well, you\'re just zooming right along! I can\'t teach you anything you don\'t already know, but Springspindle Fizzlegear sure can! You can find Sprinspindle in Ironforge. Good luck!'
Text0_0_loc9='Quid pro quo! I\'ll teach you what I know, but first I want you to perform a small task?'
Text0_0_loc9='You can learn from me in time, but not yet! Why don\'t you start out by talking to Sprite Jumpsprocket to my right here. You can check in with me after you\'ve gotten your feet wet!'
Text0_0_loc9='You certainly did not disappoint! Now that we\'ve gotten that out of the way, your instruction may begin!'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The plans for my twenty-foot tall turkey baster are nearly complete! Now all I need is a twenty-foot tall turkey...',Text0_1_loc9='The plans for my twenty-foot tall turkey baster are nearly complete! Now all I need is a twenty-foot tall turkey...',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5152;
