Text0_0_loc9='If there were just a few more hours in a day...'
Text0_0_loc9='You have earned the privilege of training with a higher instructor. Go see my pal Roxxik there.'
Text0_0_loc9='Every day is a test, and this day is no different. If you pass this test, I will share some of my knowledge...'
Text0_0_loc9='You have not yet earned the right to train with me. See Thund first, over by the table. Come back when he says you\'re ready!'
Text0_0_loc9='You have passed your test, well done! Your training may now continue.'
Text0_0_loc9='I don\'t have time for idle gossip, I\'m a professional!'
Text0_0_loc9='What do you think I could teach you? Roxxik would do a much better job. You can find him in Orgrimmar. Now be off!'
Text0_0_loc9='Let\'s see how competent you are, shall we? If you perform this task to my liking, I\'ll spend the time to teach you!'
Text0_0_loc9='This is a waste of time, mine and yours! Go see Graham Van Talen if you want to begin your instruction! He\'s standing to my left over there.'
