UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Too bad we can\'t skin the humans and their allies. All that skin is just going to waste. Still, who\'d want to wear the flimsy leather you could make out of it?',Text0_1_loc9='Too bad we can\'t skin the humans and their allies. All that skin is just going to waste. Still, who\'d want to wear the flimsy leather you could make out of it?',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5281;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Skin, glorious skin. It holds your insides... in. You might\'ve noticed my skin\'s not doing so well. To think I used to worry about my pores. Hardly any skin left to worry about these days. In a way, it\'s very freeing.',Text0_1_loc9='Skin, glorious skin. It holds your insides... in. You might\'ve noticed my skin\'s not doing so well. To think I used to worry about my pores. Hardly any skin left to worry about these days. In a way, it\'s very freeing.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5282;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You\'ve got the hang of it. I can\'t teach you any more, but talk to Arthur Moore, a Forsaken who works in the Rogues\' Quarter of the Undercity. Tell him I sent you.',Text0_1_loc9='You\'ve got the hang of it. I can\'t teach you any more, but talk to Arthur Moore, a Forsaken who works in the Rogues\' Quarter of the Undercity. Tell him I sent you.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5283;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Before the plague came, I knew nothing about leather. Now I know enough to teach others. Death\'s left me with a lot of time on my hands.',Text0_1_loc9='Before the plague came, I knew nothing about leather. Now I know enough to teach others. Death\'s left me with a lot of time on my hands.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5284;
Text0_0_loc9='Meat, skin, bones... a good hunter lets nothing go to waste. Every scrap of leather can be salvaged, perhaps to reinforce an ally\'s armor. Thus, each of us is strong alone, but together we become invincible.'
Text0_0_loc9='You have outgrown any teachings I could offer. Go with the blessing of the Earth Mother. Seek out the tauren Tarn in the northwestern shops of Thunder Bluff\'s central plateau. Be guided by his wisdom.'
Text0_0_loc9='We live and die, and the land remains, eternal, unmoved by our passage. Thus, land cannot belong to us, $N. Instead, we belong to it. Therefore we protect the land, for without it we cannot hope to survive.'
Text0_0_loc9='The caverns below us are a source of strange and wondrous hides, but you must take care if you venture into their depths, $N. Remember that your own skin is far more valuable.'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='' WHERE entry=5289;
Text0_0_loc9='Cairne himself lives here, they say. Once I have finished crafting a fitting gift, I will seek him out. Perhaps he will have words of wisdom for me.'
Text0_0_loc9='Your talent is beyond my own, friend. Speak with Tarn here; his knowledge of leather is much greater than mine. I\'m sure he would welcome another student.'
Text0_0_loc9='Cleanse your hands before you begin any project. Staining the leather with blood or dirt would take away from its natural beauty.'
Text0_0_loc9='When I clawed my way out of the grave, I thought my family would welcome me with open arms. Instead, they drove me from the village, screaming in a language I could no longer understand.'
Text0_0_loc9='I can\'t help you; your work is beyond my own. Talk to Arthur Moore, over there by the coffins. He\'ll be able to train you further.'
Text0_0_loc9='Take every word I say and commit it to memory. Until our enemies have been eradicated, we must never shirk a chance to further our knowledge. Reinforce your armor, and never relax your guard.'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You are beyond my limited abilities. Seek out the night elf Ainethil in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace of Darnassus. She can teach you more. I only wish that I could go with you.',Text0_1_loc9='You are beyond my limited abilities. Seek out the night elf Ainethil in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace of Darnassus. She can teach you more. I only wish that I could go with you.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5314;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='My teachings would be too advanced for you at this stage. If you wish to learn more of potions, speak with Tel\'Athir here instead.',Text0_1_loc9='My teachings would be too advanced for you at this stage. If you wish to learn more of potions, speak with Tel\'Athir here instead.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5316;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Listen carefully, $N, for I have much knowledge to impart.',Text0_1_loc9='Listen carefully, $N, for I have much knowledge to impart.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5317;
Text0_0_loc9='Even I have my limitations! Go talk to Lavinia Crowe in Undercity if you wish to further your training.'
Text0_0_loc9='Not bad... I suppose training you is not out of the question. Very well! Let\'s begin...'
Text0_0_loc9='Randal\'s a bit of a dandy, but he\'s dependable, which is more than I can say for a lot of the students I take on. Still, I guess I can\'t blame them for wanting a bit of adventure.'
Text0_0_loc9='Sorry, but you\'ve reached the limit of what I can teach. If you want to learn more, go see Telonis in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace of Darnassus. He\'s pretty talented, so I hear.'
Text0_0_loc9='Come back to me when you\'ve had more training. Randal Worth over there can help you with that.'
Text0_0_loc9='Hmm, I guess I can take on another student. Well, don\'t just stand there. Tell me what you\'re looking to learn.'
Text0_0_loc9='Darianna shows promise, but she is so full of energy that it is hard for her to stay still and listen. With her strength and agility, I fear it won\'t be long before she is called to fight. We must teach her quickly.'
Text0_0_loc9='If you are here for further training, you have overestimated my abilities. Have a word with Telonis over there; he can help you.'
Text0_0_loc9='In time you will be ready for what I have to teach, $N. Until then, please ask Darianna over there to help you with your training.'
Text0_0_loc9='Many animals lost their lives so that we could gain these materials. Do not take their sacrifice lightly, $N. Handle the leather with the respect it deserves.'
Text0_0_loc9='Lots to do! Haven\'t been this busy since my cousin accidentally vaporized all the cloth and leather in Gnomeregan. My, it was drafty for a while! Ah, $N, those were the days....'
Text0_0_loc9='Nope, can\'t help you, I\'m afraid. Your skills have mine beat! If you want to learn more, talk to the night elf Telonis in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace of Darnassus. He\'s amazing!'
Text0_0_loc9='Well, I declare! It\'s a new student! I\'ll gladly teach you everything I know once you have a little more skill. Go talk to Gretta Finespindle over there, would you? She\'ll have you up to speed in no time.'
Text0_0_loc9='Your skills are coming along nicely. Soon you\'ll be running a leather shop of your own. I\'ll be glad for the help, $N. My hands are only so fast, you know? There\'s so much work to do!'
Text0_0_loc9='The strongest hides come from those kodo that have laid themselves to rest in this wasteland.'
Text0_0_loc9='I cannot aid you with further lessons: your skills have surpassed mine. Go and see the tauren Una in the northwestern shops of Thunder Bluff\'s central plateau. She offers more advanced training.'
Text0_0_loc9='I do not offer apprentice training. Look for the tauren Waldor in the Wailing Caverns, here in the Barrens. He can assist you with whatever you need.'
Text0_0_loc9='Have you come for further training? Shake the dust of the road from your garments, then, and let us get to work.'
Text0_0_loc9='My axe has seen many battles, and I like to keep it handy. Enemy forces have fought their way into our capital several times now, but have no fear: we have always driven them back.'
Text0_0_loc9='I cannot help you with further training: your skill at working with leather rivals my own. You should speak with Una, over there. I will vouch for your skill if need be.'
Text0_0_loc9='Your skills are insufficient to learn what I teach. Try talking to Mak over there instead. He can help you out until you\'re ready for more advanced lessons.'
Text0_0_loc9='I am pleased with your progress so far. Surely the Earth Mother has inspired your hands.'
Text0_0_loc9='We have only a small foothold on this continent for now, but the humans can\'t fight us off forever. Then they\'ll pay for enslaving us. We\'ll cut their lying tongues out for their treachery.'
Text0_0_loc9='I\'d train you if I could, but you\'re too much for me. Tell you what: go talk to the tauren Una in the northwestern shops of Thunder Bluff\'s central plateau. She\'s got some real talent.'
Text0_0_loc9='You\'ve got more guts than brains, coming to me without the proper training. Go talk to somebody closer to your skill level, like the orc Kamari, who lives in the Drag of Orgrimmar.'
Text0_0_loc9='Am I busy? What\'s that supposed to mean? Do you think I just stand here all day, twiddling my thumbs? If you\'re here to buy something, talk to Handor.'
Text0_0_loc9='You won\'t learn anything new from me; you know too much already. If you want more training, talk to the tauren Una in the northwestern shops of Thunder Bluff\'s central plateau. Send her my regards, eh?'
Text0_0_loc9='You can\'t study my techniques until you\'ve learned the basics. Speak with Kamari if you are interested in training.'
Text0_0_loc9='The twists and turns of Orgrimmar are designed to thwart invaders. Can you imagine how quickly one of those puny gnomes would get lost in here? Ha! If it was lucky, I\'d track it down and keep it as a pet.'
Text0_0_loc9='Before my death, I was a librarian; I had nothing to do with wars and plagues. I never asked to become this. On the other hand, now that my mind is my own again, I\'m not about to surrender without a fight.'
Text0_0_loc9='I\'m pleased to say that your talents have outpaced my own. Go away now. Err, try the tauren Una in the northwestern shops of Thunder Bluff\'s central plateau. She\'s very skilled, I assure you.'
Text0_0_loc9='If I taught novices, there\'d be a lot more students visiting me, and things would get noisy. Go talk to Dan Golthas over there. He\'s a little intense, but he means well, and he\'s a decent teacher.'
Text0_0_loc9='I first set up shop in the Magic Quarter, but it was pretty noisy there. This is a definite improvement, barring a few persistent students who still track me down, despite the fact that I\'ve relocated.'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Elune has granted the night elves many gifts. In return, it is our responsibility to safeguard these forests from the demonic taint that the Horde always brings with it.',Text0_1_loc9='Elune has granted the night elves many gifts. In return, it is our responsibility to safeguard these forests from the demonic taint that the Horde always brings with it.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5360;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Training you further is beyond my abilities. Speak to Telonis in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace of Darnassus. He is always glad to help talented students.',Text0_1_loc9='Training you further is beyond my abilities. Speak to Telonis in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace of Darnassus. He is always glad to help talented students.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5361;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I only teach students who have already mastered the basics. You must seek out the night elf Darianna in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace of Darnassus. Her skills will be a perfect complement to yours.',Text0_1_loc9='I only teach students who have already mastered the basics. You must seek out the night elf Darianna in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace of Darnassus. Her skills will be a perfect complement to yours.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5363;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Always double-check your measurements before you begin to cut the leather. We cannot afford to waste materials.',Text0_1_loc9='Always double-check your measurements before you begin to cut the leather. We cannot afford to waste materials.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5364;
Text0_0_loc9='The waters of Westfall is where you must search, due west-northwest of where the Gold Coast Quarry meets with the shore.  An anchor shows where a boat has sunk beyond it, deep within the water.  The underwater pressure is fierce here; swimming too far will crush even the mightiest swimmer from fatigue.  $B$BLook for a natural formation to aid you, $N - a bubbly fissure is near here, offering deep-water swimmers a chance for renewed breath.$B'
Text0_0_loc9='In the Silverpine Forest along the edges of the North Tide\'s Run, a derelict boat rests on the shore.  Out to the west of this lies what you seek; swim too far and the ocean will crush you from fatigue.  It resides on the ocean floor in a lockbox, waiting for you to claim it.$B$BYou\'ll be hard pressed to survive a dive to such depths without aid, so take heart; a bubbly fissure offers renewed breath to divers seeking this half of the pendant.  Use it wisely.'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='In the northern part of Darkshore runs the Cliffspring River, flowing down from the lands now known as Felwood.  As the river flows out and empties out into the Mist\'s Edge, travel north to where deepest parts of the ocean begin.  A stone formation that some call the Stone Claw due it its shape is where you may find what you seek.$B$BBe warned - threshers gather by the Stone Claw, and will attack those who trespass on their territory.',Text0_1_loc9='In the northern part of Darkshore runs the Cliffspring River, flowing down from the lands now known as Felwood.  As the river flows out and empties out into the Mist\'s Edge, travel north to where deepest parts of the ocean begin.  A stone formation that some call the Stone Claw due it its shape is where you may find what you seek.$B$BBe warned - threshers gather by the Stone Claw, and will attack those who trespass on their territory.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5375;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='In the northeastern Barrens lies a pool of water sickened by pollution.  The locals call it the Sludge Fen; the Venture Company has turned the once crystal-blue waters into a mire of industrial byproducts and waste.  In the heart of this fen lies what you seek, $N.$B$BBe warned - the Venture Company does not tolerate trespassers, and they consider anyone who does not work for them as such.  You\'ll especially be a target as a protector of nature, something they vehemently oppose.',Text0_1_loc9='In the northeastern Barrens lies a pool of water sickened by pollution.  The locals call it the Sludge Fen; the Venture Company has turned the once crystal-blue waters into a mire of industrial byproducts and waste.  In the heart of this fen lies what you seek, $N.$B$BBe warned - the Venture Company does not tolerate trespassers, and they consider anyone who does not work for them as such.  You\'ll especially be a target as a protector of nature, something they vehemently oppose.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5376;
Text0_0_loc9='The grass is soft and lush. The air is fresh, full of light and song. Everything I\'ve seen suggests that Teldrassil is a dream come true. Why, then, is my heart full of foreboding?'
Text0_0_loc9='You have advanced beyond my skill to teach you. Journey now to Aerie Peak in the Hinterlands and speak with the dwarf Drakk Stonehand. His work is magnificent, far better than my own.'
Text0_0_loc9='I regret to say that I cannot aid you, $Gnoble sir:gentle lady;, until you learn more of working with leather. Speak with Faldron or Darianna here instead. They can teach you the skill you require.'
Text0_0_loc9='Do not try to force your will upon the leather. Rather, let its natural tendencies dictate what form and function it will take. This is not a battle to be won. Work with the leather, not against it.'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The needle is small, but the thread is strong, and the stitches are fine. Our pact with Thrall and the others will hold. The Horde will not be driven from these lands.',Text0_1_loc9='The needle is small, but the thread is strong, and the stitches are fine. Our pact with Thrall and the others will hold. The Horde will not be driven from these lands.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5398;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Even my talents have a limit, and you have reached it. Congratulations, $N. Your next stop should be Camp Mojache in Feralas. The tauren Hahrana Ironhide lives there; she is renowned for her skill.',Text0_1_loc9='Even my talents have a limit, and you have reached it. Congratulations, $N. Your next stop should be Camp Mojache in Feralas. The tauren Hahrana Ironhide lives there; she is renowned for her skill.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5399;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='It\'s been so long since I was a novice myself that I don\'t think I\'d be the best teacher for you. Try talking to Tarn or Mak, right over there. One of them should be able to answer your questions.',Text0_1_loc9='It\'s been so long since I was a novice myself that I don\'t think I\'d be the best teacher for you. Try talking to Tarn or Mak, right over there. One of them should be able to answer your questions.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5401;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Cairne has brought us to a land rich with possibilities for the future. We have been fortunate, and so in turn we pass on our good fortune to others. That is why I began teaching, $N.',Text0_1_loc9='Cairne has brought us to a land rich with possibilities for the future. We have been fortunate, and so in turn we pass on our good fortune to others. That is why I began teaching, $N.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5402;
Text0_0_loc9='I can make amazing things with the materials I find out here. By Muradin\'s beard, there are fantastic creatures in these hills! Go have a whack at them, $N, and bring me back some tall tales.'
Text0_0_loc9='I love a good challenge; don\'t you? Aye, of course ye do. An\' that\'s why you\'re about to do exactly what I say.'
Text0_0_loc9='I\'m not here to teach babes fresh out of the cradle. Ye\'ve nowhere near the amount of skill I require in my students. In fact, ye\'re a sad figure of a $Glad:lass;, an\' I\'ll thank ye not to stand there jibber-jabberin\' at me.'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='All requests for my work must be made in person by the buyer. Orwin often asks me to reconsider, but my priorities lie here. Look around you: many of these fighters rely upon me for their armor.',Text0_1_loc9='All requests for my work must be made in person by the buyer. Orwin often asks me to reconsider, but my priorities lie here. Look around you: many of these fighters rely upon me for their armor.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5407;
Text0_0_loc9='I only wish I had more students like you. Not many will venture so far into enemy territory. I salute your courage.',Text0_1_loc9='I only wish I had more students like you. Not many will venture so far into enemy territory. I salute your courage.'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='We cannot afford to give an inch in this war. Day and night, I create new armor, and I patch whatever can be salvaged from the old. I have no time for other tasks. Would you take care of something for me?',Text0_1_loc9='We cannot afford to give an inch in this war. Day and night, I create new armor, and I patch whatever can be salvaged from the old. I have no time for other tasks. Would you take care of something for me?',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5409;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You have wasted your time and mine by coming to me for training, $N. I have no time to teach basic skills. We\'re fighting a war here, and this is one of the front lines. Don\'t return to me until you are more prepared.',Text0_1_loc9='You have wasted your time and mine by coming to me for training, $N. I have no time to teach basic skills. We\'re fighting a war here, and this is one of the front lines. Don\'t return to me until you are more prepared.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5410;
Text0_0_loc9='I can tell that your wardrobe is in dire need of care.'
Text0_0_loc9='I\'m a simple man who knows a few things about tailoring, but you need more assistance than I can provide. I have heard of a Night Elf who is quite an accomplished tailor. He resides in Stormwind, in the Magic District.'
Text0_0_loc9='So you would like to learn a few things? I would be happy to get you started!'
Text0_0_loc9='Life is like a carefully woven tapestry.'
Text0_0_loc9='Hmm... the things you need to learn are a little above my head. Have a talk with Sellandus over at Larson\'s Clothiers just up the path to the right. He taught me everything I know!'
Text0_0_loc9='Very well, let your journey of tailoring begin.'
Text0_0_loc9='Needlework requires a steady hand. And patience... above all, patience.'
Text0_0_loc9='It is time for you to journey to Darnassus and speak to Me\'lynn. She will guide you from now on.'
Text0_0_loc9='I would be happy to take you under my wing. Let us begin.'
Text0_0_loc9='Welcome to me shop. What can I do for ye\'?'
Text0_0_loc9='Hold on there, I\'m just an assistant. If ye want to start learnin\' the fancy stuff, talk to old Stonebrew over there.'
Text0_0_loc9='Excellent! I\'ve been hopin\' for a new student. Well, let\'s get started right away then!'
Text0_0_loc9='We use many animal pelts and skins in our creations.'
Text0_0_loc9='I know a few things, but I\'m no expert. Lucky for you, Magar is. He\'s standing near the back of the shop. See if he can help you, but be careful not to rile him. He can be irritable.'
Text0_0_loc9='I will teach you what I can.'
Text0_0_loc9='No part of the animals we hunt is wasted.'
Text0_0_loc9='You seek a higher knowledge. Tepa is blessed with such knowledge. She should be standing somewhere nearby...'
Text0_0_loc9='With the Earth Mother\'s blessing, we shall begin.'
Text0_0_loc9='Pleased to make you acquaintance. May I help you?'
Text0_0_loc9='I am knowledgable, but I am not an expert. You know who you should talk to? Rhiannon! She\'s not far. Ask around for her in Undercity'
Text0_0_loc9='So... you want to be a tailor? Very well, we\'ll see if you have what it takes.'
Text0_0_loc9='We don\'t get many visitors out here. May I interest you in something?'
Text0_0_loc9='I\'m just a student myself, really. Rhiannon\'s the expert. She\'s standing by the crates over there. You can learn a lot from her.'
Text0_0_loc9='Yes, I think you have potential. Maybe I can show you a thing or two.'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='There is no greater way to clear the mind than to weave.',Text0_1_loc9='There is no greater way to clear the mind than to weave.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5437;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='My education is ongoing, and your knowledge surpasses mine. If you wish to learn more you must speak to Me\'lynn. She will guide you.',Text0_1_loc9='My education is ongoing, and your knowledge surpasses mine. If you wish to learn more you must speak to Me\'lynn. She will guide you.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5438;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You will not be disappointed, traveler. Tailoring is a joyous endeavor.',Text0_1_loc9='You will not be disappointed, traveler. Tailoring is a joyous endeavor.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5439;
Text0_0_loc9='Hey mon, what can I be doin\' for you?'
Text0_0_loc9='At dis point you know as much as I do, mon. Maybe you go see Magar in Orgrimmar. He not be da happiest tailor around, but he help you anyway.'
Text0_0_loc9='Dat\'s da attitude! Grab a needle and thread and let\'s get jammin\'!'
Text0_0_loc9='I am afraid that I am no longer gentle or humble. Age and countless battles have hardened my skin and soul. Perhaps that is why Cairne assigned me to Sun Rock Retreat... the gentle winds and warm sun does ease the pain.'
Text0_0_loc9='Greetings.  Our bats are well trained and fed.  You\'ll not find faster.'
Text0_0_loc9='How may I be of service?'
Text0_0_loc9='Greetings, and welcome.  I am not very good at smiling, but trust me; I am happy to serve you.'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The Hippogryph is a noble beast, proud and swift.  They are an honor to train, and can quickly take their rider a great distance.',Text0_1_loc9='The Hippogryph is a noble beast, proud and swift.  They are an honor to train, and can quickly take their rider a great distance.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5473;
Text0_0_loc9='To maintain our link to the mainland, we have hippogryphs constantly flying between Rut\'theran Village and Darkshore.'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The fish off the coast of Teldrassil are quite large and robust.  Rumors say it is the speedy growth of our new world tree that is the cause.',Text0_1_loc9='The fish off the coast of Teldrassil are quite large and robust.  Rumors say it is the speedy growth of our new world tree that is the cause.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5475;
Text0_0_loc9='Although the coast of Darkshore is more dangerous than that of Teldrassil, many fishers find profit here.'
Text0_0_loc9='It is my honor to provide for adventurers, for they are heroes in the making.'
Text0_0_loc9='Fastest gryphons this side of Aerie Peak. Want to take a ride?'
Text0_0_loc9='On the northern dock, you can board a ship that will carry you to Rut\'theran Village and Darnassus.  From the southern dock, you can find passage across the Great Sea to Menethil Harbor on Khaz Modan.  Safe journeys to you!'
Text0_0_loc9='This dock here?  Well you can catch the ship that goes to that Night Elf place.  What\'s it\'s name?  Uhh Auberdine I think.  I don\'t really know for sure, I just load and unload stuff.'
Text0_0_loc9='Delivering these barrels to the excavation site is hard work, but there are so many depending on us to get the blast powder there.$B$BWe must do what we can against the Dark Irons!'
Text0_0_loc9='My wind riders are trained to fly quickly through the hot Barrens air.'
Text0_0_loc9='The Barrens, with its hot sun and hostile denizens, is the perfect place to test your strength and fortitude.'
Text0_0_loc9='Greetings.  If you are here for leather goods, then you will find my wares well crafted.'
Text0_0_loc9='Are you here to help with the delivery? Miran\'s just about ready.'
Text0_0_loc9='When mounted on the back of a wind rider, one sees that its reputation for strength and speed is well earned.'
Text0_0_loc9='This is a dangerous line of business!$B$BMiran just left with a delivery. He should be back in a few minutes.'
Text0_0_loc9='You\'re better at this gig than I am! You want someone with even more experience than I\'ve got. That\'d be Doctor Herbert Halsey, an undead who works in the Apothecarium of the Undercity.'
Text0_0_loc9='Have a look at my meats, friend.  You won\'t want to go out into the Barrens without a good stock of provisions.'
Text0_0_loc9='You haven\'t lived until you\'ve looked down on the world from the back of a wind rider.'
Text0_0_loc9='You can find passage to Theramore from this dock.  Heed my words, those lands are rarely safe to travel for people of the Alliance.  Watch your step and your back.'
Text0_0_loc9='Good day to you.'
Text0_0_loc9='You are beyond my level of expertise. Georgio Bolero, the master of Duncan\'s Textiles around the corner could help you advance your skills.'
Text0_0_loc9='Speak with Lawrence Shneider at Duncan\'s Textiles around the corner to the left. He is adept at dealing with beginners.'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='' WHERE entry=5523;
Text0_0_loc9='Ah, this Darnassian fabric is the finest!'
Text0_0_loc9='Well, aren\'t you the smarty-pants? Ye know more than I do, I can tell ye that! Don\'t go getting\' a big head, but if ye want to keep learnin\', have a chat with Georgio Bolero in Stormwind. They say he knows his tailorin\'!'
Text0_0_loc9='I don\'t have time to babysit! Go talk to me assistant, Uthrar!'
Text0_0_loc9='Hmm... you show a little promise, I\'ll give you that. Okay then, where were we?'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Do you hear the call of the hunt, $C?  You must listen closely, but the call comes from deep within you.  It comes from deep within all of us.',Text0_1_loc9='Do you hear the call of the hunt, $C?  You must listen closely, but the call comes from deep within you.  It comes from deep within all of us.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5529;
Text0_0_loc9='I made a lot of the things you see in the store. What do you think? Answer carefully, your life may depend on it.'
Text0_0_loc9='You need to learn from someone who knows more than I do. Go talk to Josef Gregorian in Undercity. Well, what are you still doing here?'
Text0_0_loc9='What? Why are you bothering me? Why, I bet you can\'t even create a high quality robe! Go talk to Snang and come back when you\'re worthy of my talents!'
Text0_0_loc9='About time you showed me some results! Now I\'ll show you results!'
Text0_0_loc9='They say a stitch in time saves... what, eleven? Ah, I can\'t remember. Stupid saying anyway.'
Text0_0_loc9='Not bad... for an amateur! Still, you know about as much as I do. If you wanna\' learn more you\'re gonna\' have to talk to Josef Gregorian in Undercity.'
Text0_0_loc9='Well well, not too bad. Maybe I CAN show you a few things...'
