Text0_0_loc9='Yes, I\'ve been running this shop for some time now. Business has been pretty good lately. A lot of new adventurers coming through...'
Text0_0_loc9='There\'s only one person I know of who is more learned in the art of tailoring than myself. Last I heard he could be found in Theramore Isle. He is the person you should seek.'
Text0_0_loc9='You\'ll need more training before I can share my knowledge with you, I\'m afraid.'
Text0_0_loc9='Good! I can tell that my efforts will not be wasted!'
Text0_0_loc9='Cloth is okay. Personally I prefer to work with human skin.'
Text0_0_loc9='You require the instruction of a true master! Go to Daryl Stack in Tarren Mill and embrace your destiny!'
Text0_0_loc9='I will instruct you when the time is right... that time is not now. You have much more to learn first!'
Text0_0_loc9='Good! I can tell that my efforts will not be wasted!'
Text0_0_loc9='I have outfitted kings. With the proper training, you can too.'
Text0_0_loc9='You have come a long way, traveler. There is one more task for you to perform...'
Text0_0_loc9='I cannot help you until you have learned more of the essentials. Come back to me when you are ready.'
Text0_0_loc9='The place is a bit drafty... but what do I care? I\'m dead.'
Text0_0_loc9='You\'re doing very well in the art of tailoring, I must admit. Now, let\'s see how good you REALLY are...'
Text0_0_loc9='Who sent you here? You\'re not ready for my instruction yet! You\'ll be told when you\'re ready.'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I do so enjoy sitting out here, listening to the sounds of the Great Sea.  Oh, what?  Yes, there is a ship that will take you to Menethil Harbor.  It docks here from time to time.',Text0_1_loc9='I do so enjoy sitting out here, listening to the sounds of the Great Sea.  Oh, what?  Yes, there is a ship that will take you to Menethil Harbor.  It docks here from time to time.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5579;
Text0_0_loc9='Mark my words!  You won\'t find faster gryphons anywhere in the Eastern Kingdoms than the ones right here in Thelsamar!'
Text0_0_loc9='If you ask me, there\'s no greater profession than a miner.  And if you ask me, there\'s no greater miner than a dwarf!'
Text0_0_loc9='The Wildhammer dwarves might have fast steeds, but can those Aerie Peak gryphons stand the heat of The Great Forge?  I think not!'
Text0_0_loc9='The best miner has a firm grip on $Ghis:her; pick, a stout heart in $Ghis:her; chest, and thick, black dust in $Ghis:her; hair.'
Text0_0_loc9='The sturdy crate sits in the middle of the lumber mill surrounded by debris and very zealous followers of the Scarlet Crusade.'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='This bear wanders a path close to where the Talondeep Path lies, due west of Mystral Lake and the Alliance outpost of Silverwind Refuge.  While he is the easiest of the three creatures you will face on the Ashenvale Hunt, he should not be trifled with.  His presence is a constant threat to travelers who sojourn between Ashenvale and the Stonetalon Mountains.',Text0_1_loc9='This bear wanders a path close to where the Talondeep Path lies, due west of Mystral Lake and the Alliance outpost of Silverwind Refuge.  While he is the easiest of the three creatures you will face on the Ashenvale Hunt, he should not be trifled with.  His presence is a constant threat to travelers who sojourn between Ashenvale and the Stonetalon Mountains.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5593;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The mightiest of all the beasts that make up the Ashenvale Hunt, Sharptalon is let to wander freely by the self-proclaimed guardians of this land, the night elves.  Sharptalon patrols for prey to the south of here, taking delight in rending the unsuspecting and unaware traveler limb from limb.$B$BTo bring down such a beast would be the mightiest of hauls, $N.  I wish you luck in the hunt for this creature!',Text0_1_loc9='The mightiest of all the beasts that make up the Ashenvale Hunt, Sharptalon is let to wander freely by the self-proclaimed guardians of this land, the night elves.  Sharptalon patrols for prey to the south of here, taking delight in rending the unsuspecting and unaware traveler limb from limb.$B$BTo bring down such a beast would be the mightiest of hauls, $N.  I wish you luck in the hunt for this creature!',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5594;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='This nightsaber is rumored to be docile in the presence of night elves and their allies, which makes her an even more worthy opponent.  Shadumbra\'s hunting path takes her from the Raynewood Retreat to our west, ultimately to lands due west of there.  Her fur is the color of pitch, and her speed is not to be underestimated.',Text0_1_loc9='This nightsaber is rumored to be docile in the presence of night elves and their allies, which makes her an even more worthy opponent.  Shadumbra\'s hunting path takes her from the Raynewood Retreat to our west, ultimately to lands due west of there.  Her fur is the color of pitch, and her speed is not to be underestimated.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5595;
Text0_0_loc9='Greetings $C - welcome to the front lines in our conquest of Ashenvale!  If you are looking for something to do, then you\'ve come to the right place.  I\'m always looking for able-bodied individuals to help bring glory to the Horde!'
Text0_0_loc9='The dragon hides behind a royal facade. The tablets will reveal her for what she is... If what I have seen holds true, I will not survive this battle, friend. It is you that must finish what I have started. Are your forces ready? Are you ready? We will begin on your command.'
Text0_0_loc9='If you want to know about the comings and goings of caravans and merchants here in Splintertree Post, then I am fortunately the orc you are looking for.  Unfortunately for you though, I don\'t like people.$B$BIf you want something, make it quick.'
Text0_0_loc9='The elements speak to us, $C.  They share knowledge that we must learn, and they share secrets that must be kept.'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Through rigorous retraining I have had to break many students of all they had previously learned so that I might teach them anew.  The service I offer becomes increasingly difficult to perform each time it is done.  It is for that reason that it becomes increasingly expensive with each retraining.  Do you desire that I break you of the talents you have learned?',Text0_1_loc9='Through rigorous retraining I have had to break many students of all they had previously learned so that I might teach them anew.  The service I offer becomes increasingly difficult to perform each time it is done.  It is for that reason that it becomes increasingly expensive with each retraining.  Do you desire that I break you of the talents you have learned?',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5673;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='If you desire, in addition to training, I have it within my power to erase the knowledge of your talents from your mind.  Be warned that every time you undergo this procedure the more difficult it is to perform, and therefore the more expensive it becomes.',Text0_1_loc9='If you desire, in addition to training, I have it within my power to erase the knowledge of your talents from your mind.  Be warned that every time you undergo this procedure the more difficult it is to perform, and therefore the more expensive it becomes.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=5674;
