Text0_0_loc9='Yes, $C? Are you reporting in?'
Text0_0_loc9='The Coldtooth Mine lies in Horde territory, in the mountains north of the Frostwolf Graveyard.$B$BIt is controlled by the Kobolds.'
Text0_0_loc9='The Irondeep Mine is in Alliance territory, north of the Stormpike Graveyard.$B$BIt is controlled by the Troggs.'
Text0_0_loc9='This monument is dedicated to all those who have fallen in the protection of Stormwind.$B$BOur people have weathered unbelievable hardships to retain their freedoms and to control their own destinies. It is here we remember every sacrifice our citizens have made during the first war that riddled our people.'
Text0_0_loc9='In Alterac Valley, battles rage and equipment is in short supply.'
Text0_0_loc9='Our units are not upgraded, and I don\'t have enough supplies to upgrade them.'
