Text0_0_loc9='I am Hydraxis, Duke of the Waterlords.  You are not an elemental and so cannot understand our struggle, but perhaps we can strike a deal that will benefit us both...'
Text0_0_loc9='$N, it is good to see you.  Our war with the other elemental lords yet rages, but your efforts help ensure our victory.'
