Text0_0_loc9='If you\'re looking for information that the Cenarion Circle might have archived somewhere, then I\'m the one to talk to.  Then again, you need to know what information you\'re looking for first before I can really help you.$B$BSee how that works?  Brilliant!'
Text0_0_loc9='Don\'t listen to the hearts of the world - the answer lies within.  You know the truth.'
Text0_0_loc9='The past lives in these wastes, $C.  We must be careful to not awaken it.'
Text0_0_loc9='Hey there, friend. My name\'s Remy. I\'m from Redridge to the east, and came here looking for business, looking for business. You got any...got any??',Text0_1_loc9='Hey there, friend. My name\'s Remy. I\'m from Redridge to the east, and came here looking for business, looking for business. You got any...got any??'
Text0_0_loc9='$N, you are ready for the ultimate task.  The fiery runes etched on the floor of the molten core are conduits to the realm of fire, and their presence is both an affront to us and a source of power for the Firelords.  They must be extinguished!$B$BTo extinguish a rune, take a vial of aqual quintessence.  Pour it on the rune and its flame will go out, rendering it useless and weakening our enemy!'
Text0_0_loc9='Welcome to the Undercity Guild Registry. What do you want?'
Text0_0_loc9='Welcome to the Cenarion Circle, $C.  How may I assist you?'
Text0_0_loc9='Speak with Hydraxis.',Text1_0_loc9='You have no business with me, little one.'
Text2_0_loc9='Speak not your vulgar language to me!  Only Hydraxis can stand it.'
Text0_0_loc9='Greetings, little one.  You have business with the Waterlords?',Text1_0_loc9='Tales of your exploits spread.  Your name is not unknown to us, $N.'
Text2_0_loc9='You have made our enemies your own.  I will gladly share waters with you.'
Text0_0_loc9='Perhaps you will tell me of your deeds, $N.  I would be honored to know them.',Text1_0_loc9='Our lord Hydraxis speaks highly of you.  My water is your water, friend.'
Text2_0_loc9='When you next go to the Molten Core, kill a Firelord for me, will you?'
