Text0_0_loc9='Tell me what weapon you want to learn or go away.'
Text0_0_loc9='A wondrous Winter Veil to you... uh... little $G boy : girl;.  Good children get special, um, discounts at any local Smokywood Pastures vendor.  Yum.',Text1_0_loc9='I have a pretty good idea what ol\' Greatfather Winter\'s gonna be doing when this shift is over.  I got a bottle of Winter Veil cheer right here in my bag, and I intend to get to the bottom of it.'
