Text0_0_loc9='They say an army travels on its stomach, and that\'s the truth.  For any offensive to succeed, your troops have to be well-fed and well supplied.'
Text0_0_loc9='Some say that strength and bravery are most needed for an army\'s success.  And it\'s true!  But an army also needs supplies to keep itself in good shape, and it\'s my job to make sure they have what they need.'
