Text0_0_loc9='Ah, $N!  You\'re just the person I was hoping to see!  We have enough supplies to send a ground assault against the Horde!  Field Marshal Teravaine is waiting in the Field of Strife for orders...$B$BYou\'re a brave veteran who\'s proven himself time and again.  Do you want to deliver Teravaine the orders?'
Text0_0_loc9='What you want to learn, mon?'
Text0_0_loc9='I would be honored to train you in the use of the weapons that I have mastered should you have the ability to learn within you.'
Text0_0_loc9='If you require more training, I would be happy to tell you who can aid you. What weapon has caught your eye?'
Text0_0_loc9='Death to Stormpike!'
Text0_0_loc9='$N!  Our supplies are dwindling and until we get more we can\'t launch large ground assaults into the Field of Strife!$B$BSpeak with the Stormpike Quartermaster.  He\'ll tell you what you can do to resupply our assault forces.'
Text0_0_loc9='I suppose you are here to be trained in the use of a new weapon?  Make it fast, I\'m very busy!'
Text0_0_loc9='I\'ll tell you where to go, provided you tell me what interests you.'
Text0_0_loc9='$N, it\'s good to see veterans like you in the field!  I\'m sorry to report that our supplies are currently too low to launch any large ground assaults against the Horde.$B$BSpeak with our quartermaster; he has supply missions available.'
Text0_0_loc9='Have you come seeking training in the ways of armed combat?'
Text0_0_loc9='What weapon in particular interests you?'
