Text0_0_loc9='For 10,000 years I have ruled this kingdom. In that time, I have heard many fascinating tales from those that would walk the hallowed grounds of the House of Shen\'dralar.$B$BAs I am bound to this place, I often exchange stories with visitors. Do you have a story for me or perhaps you would like to hear a story?',Text0_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text0:'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='We mustn\'t anger the Master. His is a wrath that is cruel beyond measure.',Text0_1_loc9='We mustn\'t anger the Master. His is a wrath that is cruel beyond measure.',Text1_0_loc9='Keep your voice down, stranger. You do not want to disrupt the Master\'s meditations.',Text1_1_loc9='Keep your voice down, stranger. You do not want to disrupt the Master\'s meditations.' WHERE entry=6911;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc9='Many have come to this sanctuary, few have left.',Text2_1_loc9='Many have come to this sanctuary, few have left.',Text3_0_loc9='The Lorekeeper is an ancient. He has served under our glorious Queen!',Text3_1_loc9='The Lorekeeper is an ancient. He has served under our glorious Queen!' WHERE entry=6911;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text4_0_loc9='Books have been disappearing as of late. The Lorekeeper and his assistants are in a frenzy. They suspect foul play within Eldre\'Thalas.',Text4_1_loc9='Books have been disappearing as of late. The Lorekeeper and his assistants are in a frenzy. They suspect foul play within Eldre\'Thalas.',Text5_0_loc9='Has the Prince recanted the tale of the Ashbringer? It is our most favorite of his stories. His favorite is the followup to the Ashbringer. Of course, nobody has ever been able to get that story out of him.',Text5_1_loc9='Has the Prince recanted the tale of the Ashbringer? It is our most favorite of his stories. His favorite is the followup to the Ashbringer. Of course, nobody has ever been able to get that story out of him.' WHERE entry=6911;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text6_0_loc9='I suspect that the imps are stealing knowledge.',Text6_1_loc9='I suspect that the imps are stealing knowledge.',Text7_0_loc9='The Master holds great interest in the lair of Nefarian. If only someone would defeat the dragon and his minions and retell the tale to the Prince. I bet that would loosen the Prince\'s lips. The Ashbringer could be found!',Text7_1_loc9='The Master holds great interest in the lair of Nefarian. If only someone would defeat the dragon and his minions and retell the tale to the Prince. I bet that would loosen the Prince\'s lips. The Ashbringer could be found!' WHERE entry=6911;
Text0_0_loc9='What you doin\' wanderin\' around here?  Why them small fries not in da shackles?!'
Text0_0_loc9='You da strong one now!  All hail to da new king of da Gordok!',Text0_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text0:'
Text0_0_loc9='Do I see them with weapons still?  Why you let them keep their weapons?!'
Text0_0_loc9='All henchmen of da boss - Stomper Kreeg, all three of da Guards, Captain Kromcrush, and da Observer - give tribute to da new boss.  If you kill a henchman, then that henchman can\'t give tribute!  Each one you keep alive will give you more tribute.  Keep all of them alive and you get da BIG tribute!$B$BYeah!'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Oh the horror! The tragedy! We are on the verge of a breakthrough, yet all could be lost.',Text0_1_loc9='Oh the horror! The tragedy! We are on the verge of a breakthrough, yet all could be lost.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=6917;
