Text0_0_loc9='So, you have found me. I suppose that you have come to learn of suppression and control.$B$BI will teach you much more than that... you will also learn of sacrifice.$B$B<Daio grins.>'
Text0_0_loc9='That will be the choice of the demon you wish to conjure and enslave. We wield dark powers and we pay grossly for the use of said powers.'
Text0_0_loc9='We must first craft a prison to confine the beast, if you wish to progress further.'
Text0_0_loc9='Bow in my presence, insect! Surely you can feel the power I hold over you.'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='So you have come to Niby to learn the secrets of calling down an infernal servant from the Nether.$B$BSilence! Niby knows all!$B$BNiby is not so quick to part with such knowledge. First, you must assist Niby with a very important task.',Text0_1_loc9='So you have come to Niby to learn the secrets of calling down an infernal servant from the Nether.$B$BSilence! Niby knows all!$B$BNiby is not so quick to part with such knowledge. First, you must assist Niby with a very important task.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=7002;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='There is a powerful infernal named Kroshius northeast of this camp. It is why Niby is here. Kroshius is a greater infernal - an infernal that has lasted longer than expected. You see, nub, an infernal crashes down into the earth with great intensity to serve its master but this intensity fades fast. Once the blazing flames have died down, the infernal crumbles.',Text0_1_loc9='There is a powerful infernal named Kroshius northeast of this camp. It is why Niby is here. Kroshius is a greater infernal - an infernal that has lasted longer than expected. You see, nub, an infernal crashes down into the earth with great intensity to serve its master but this intensity fades fast. Once the blazing flames have died down, the infernal crumbles.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=7003;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Do not interrupt Niby, fool! I shall rend the flesh from your bones and use your skeletal remains as a coat rack. Now where was I? Oh yes, so, Kroshius lasted nearly ten times longer than any ordinary infernal. I am not sure why but I am confident that with enough study, I could find out.$B$BI need you to recover Kroshius\' Infernal Core.',Text0_1_loc9='Do not interrupt Niby, fool! I shall rend the flesh from your bones and use your skeletal remains as a coat rack. Now where was I? Oh yes, so, Kroshius lasted nearly ten times longer than any ordinary infernal. I am not sure why but I am confident that with enough study, I could find out.$B$BI need you to recover Kroshius\' Infernal Core.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=7004;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='If I am to teach you the secrets of summoning an infernal servant, you must destroy Kroshius and bring me the infernal core from his burning remains. This, however, is not as easy as it sounds. Kroshius has all but burned out completely. You must reignite his corpse and raise him from the rubble. To do this, however, you must gather some components from other demonic entities.$B$BMy imp, Impsy, shall set you on your way.',Text0_1_loc9='If I am to teach you the secrets of summoning an infernal servant, you must destroy Kroshius and bring me the infernal core from his burning remains. This, however, is not as easy as it sounds. Kroshius has all but burned out completely. You must reignite his corpse and raise him from the rubble. To do this, however, you must gather some components from other demonic entities.$B$BMy imp, Impsy, shall set you on your way.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=7005;
