Text0_0_loc9='The spirit of the Dreadsteed pulses with rage.'
Text0_0_loc9='The ways of Jaedenar are dark and treacherous.  Watch your moves in this place, $C, or you will find your soul entralled by your rivals...'
Text0_0_loc9='Be gone!  I hold counsel with Dreadlords, and the matters we discuss are not your concern!'
Text0_0_loc9='... A message from Banehollow?  What message is that?  Does he have need of his great advisor and servant, Ulathek?  Does he require my presence?'
Text0_0_loc9='What?  But how?  No!  This is not possible!  I have been so careful... he could not know!$B$BYou lie!  You lie, and now you\'ll die for your deceit!'
