Text0_0_loc9='Lava? Pay no mind to all of that, friend. Look around you. Take in the joys that nature has to offer.'
Text0_0_loc9='I come to Silithus every year around this time. The weather is phenomenal for my bunions.$B$BYou should take a stroll with me, friend. Enjoy the sights and what not.'
Text0_0_loc9='How wonderful to see another person in this remote region of the world. Come, walk with me. Let our bodies keep each other warm.'
