UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='All of a sudden you\'re a \'Defender of the Alliance\' are you?! Well, I suppose you\'ll be wanting to head to the Champions\' Hall now. It\'s over in Old Town.',Text0_1_loc9='All of a sudden you\'re a \'Defender of the Alliance\' are you?! Well, I suppose you\'ll be wanting to head to the Champions\' Hall now. It\'s over in Old Town.',Text1_0_loc9='Well, well, moving up in the world are we? You\'re looking for the Champions\' Hall, and you\'ll find it on the southeast end of Old Town. Good luck!',Text1_1_loc9='Well, well, moving up in the world are we? You\'re looking for the Champions\' Hall, and you\'ll find it on the southeast end of Old Town. Good luck!' WHERE entry=7047;
Text0_0_loc9='If you\'ve come looking for the finest craftsmanship on this or any other continent in the world, then you\'ve come to the right place!$B$BGrimand Elmore, at your service!'
Text0_0_loc9='To summon a Dreadsteed, you must first create a Circle of Greater Summoning.  A portal to Xoroth may only be created from within such a circle.$B$BThe Circle of Greater Summoning requires three powerful implements: a Bell of Dethmoora, a Wheel of the Black March and a Doomsday Candle.'
Text0_0_loc9='Arr!   There be nothin I like to see better than folks fightin to the death in the arena.   If you be here at the right time maybe you can be one of them!'
Text0_0_loc9='Yesh, it\'sh true, I\'m blind as a bat! An\' drunk as a ... err, drunk as shomething that getsh drunk.$B$BI\'ll tell you what, $R. It\'sh the drink that keeps me shenses sharp. It\'sh common knowledge that when you lose a shense, yer other shenses become more alert. My drunk shense is incredible these days.'
