Text0_0_loc9='Maybe this wasn\'t the best place for a shop after all...'
Text0_0_loc9='Burninate\'s the name, smithin\'s my game... and, erm... I sell a little food and water on the side. Care for some meat?'
Text0_0_loc9='Well hello again, $N!  I don\'t know how much longer I\'m going to keep on trying to set up a shop out in the middle of nowhere.  Still, since you\'ve helped me out in the past, I\'ll show you some stuff you may find interesting!'
Text0_0_loc9='When Lolo doesn\'t wanna spill any o\' his precious ale or get his lil\' dress dirty, I\'m called in. Yep. Ol\' Hansel is the dwarf they use to mete out a lil\' bit o\' justice an\' a whole lotta pain.'
Text0_0_loc9='As acting Taskmaster of this here compound, it is my duty to make sure that there is a certain level of tedium involved with all forms of business, work, rest, and relaxation that may take place here.$B$BIf you find anything that you are asked to do to be too easy and hassle free, report to me immediately.'
Text0_0_loc9='You\'ve done all that I\'ve asked you to do, $N. There\'s really nothing more here for you. If you are interested in continuing your career as an agent of the Thorium Brotherhood, speak with Lokhtos Darkbargainer at the Grim Guzzler in Blackrock Depths.$B$BFarewell!'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Thorium Brotherhood or not, if one of them Dark Iron gets near to me they\'ll taste my mattock up the side of their head!  Now, where can I send ya $G lad : lass;?',Text0_1_loc9='Thorium Brotherhood or not, if one of them Dark Iron gets near to me they\'ll taste my mattock up the side of their head!  Now, where can I send ya $G lad : lass;?',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=7122;
