Text2_0_loc9='You\'ve got money and we\'ve got food.  What are you waiting for?!',Text3_0_loc9='For a limited time only, Crunchy Frog available exclusively here at the Darkmoon Faire.'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Every item that I have for sale I acquired myself.  You have my personal guarantee of authenticity.',Text0_1_loc9='Every item that I have for sale I acquired myself.  You have my personal guarantee of authenticity.',Text1_0_loc9='Darkmoon Faire Cards?  See the Professor here for those.  Come see me if you are a dealer in hard to come by antiquities and artifacts.',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=7389;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc9='Come and take a look at my wares while you still can.  We\'re here all week, and then we\'re off to some far off land.',Text2_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text2:',Text3_0_loc9='Have you any idea what I go through to bring these incomparable valuables to sell?  Come see them all for yourself!',Text3_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text3:' WHERE entry=7389;
