Text0_0_loc9='If you have come to save the world then you have come to the right place. The faceless one - the Blood God, Hakkar - has been brought back into our world!'
Text0_0_loc9='The strength of your resolve shines, $N. You continue to prove that you are an asset to our people. Someday the world will realize the extent of your great deeds.'
Text0_0_loc9='The burgeoning hero returns! It is good to see you again, $N. You are always welcome at our village.'
