UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I know just the one that you speak of $C.  You must seek out Brogun Stoneshield on the Warrior\'s Terrace.',Text0_1_loc9='I know just the one that you speak of $C.  You must seek out Brogun Stoneshield on the Warrior\'s Terrace.',Text1_0_loc9='The Stormpike Guard is in need of your assistance in the fight against the Frostwolf Clan, $N.  Speak to Brogun Stoneshield on the Warrior\'s Terrace and he will help you find your way to Alterac Valley.',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=7496;
Text0_0_loc9='Aye, and which battleground be ye looking for?'
Text0_0_loc9='Warsong Gulch you say? Well then, you\'ll be wanting to speak with fair Lylandris over in the Hall of Arms.',Text0_1_loc9='Any chance to fight against the Horde, especially orcs, is a good time if you ask me. You\'ll find plenty of battle in Warsong Gulch, that you will. Head on over to the Hall of Arms and speak with Lylandris. She\'ll set you on your way.',Text1_0_loc9='Any chance to fight against the Horde, especially orcs, is a good time if you ask me. You\'ll find plenty of battle in Warsong Gulch, that you will. Head on over to the Hall of Arms and speak with Lylandris. She\'ll set you on your way.'
Text0_0_loc9='Which battleground are you interested in?'
Text0_0_loc9='Then it is Thelman Slatefist that you wish to speak to.  You can find him in the presence of the King at Stormwind Keep.',Text1_0_loc9='And I wish I could join you $N.  Head over to Stormwind Keep.  You\'ll find Thelman Slatefist in the King\'s audience chamber.  He will aid you in getting to Alterac Valley.'
Text0_0_loc9='Indeed, Silverwing Hold is in need of your assistance.  Speak with Elfarran in the audience chamber at Stormwind Keep.',Text1_0_loc9='The Silverwing Sentinels can use all the help they can get in their fight against the Warsong Outriders.  $N, go to Stormwind Keep and speak with Elfarran if you wish to assist them.'
Text0_0_loc9='We must eliminate the elves and their cowardly Alliance from Warsong Gulch. Go to the Hall of the Brave in the Valley of Honor and speak with Brakgul Deathbringer if you have what it takes to aid the Horde.',Text1_0_loc9='The Silverwing Sentinels are hardly what I would call honorable opponents.  But if you are intent upon their slaughter $C, then seek out Brakgul Deathbringer in the Hall of the Brave.'
Text0_0_loc9='Which battleground do you seek your glory in?'
Text0_0_loc9='And to which battleground do you wish to journey?'
Text0_0_loc9='Then it is to Taim Ragetotem that you must speak.  Seek him out on the Hunter Rise.',Text1_0_loc9='There is one that I know of here in Thunder Bluff that can aid you in your journey to Alterac Valley.  On the Hunter Rise look for Taim Ragetotem.  May you find what you are looking for $N.'
Text0_0_loc9='Kergul Bloodaxe on the Hunter Rise stands ready to help you get to Warsong Gulch.',Text1_0_loc9='Such needless strife, but if the elves of Silverwing Hold will not speak to us in peace, then what alternative do they leave us?  Seek out the aid of Kergul Bloodaxe on the Hunter Rise to get to Warsong Gulch.'
Text0_0_loc9='What battleground you want?'
Text0_0_loc9='It cold there!  You go in Royal Quarter, talk to Grizzle Halfmane.',Text1_0_loc9='Him name is Grizzle Halfmane.  He in Royal Quarter with Banshee Queen and Dread Lord.'
Text0_0_loc9='Think him in Royal Quarter.  Kurden Bloodclaw is little orc.',Text1_0_loc9='Elves in Warsong Gulch make crunchy sound.  You crunch them good.  Talk to Kurden Bloodclaw in Royal Quarter.'
Text0_0_loc9='I am Jin\'rokh the Breaker, envoy of Mugamba: Fist of Rastakhan!$B$BMy dealings are with warriors and heathens.'
Text0_0_loc9='I am Al\'tabim the All-Seeing - an envoy of King Rastakhan.$B$BMy dealings are with priests, mages, and warlocks.'
Text0_0_loc9='The League of Arathor has sworn to retake Arathi for humans of Stromgarde and the Alliance.  It is a battle hard fought, but a battle worth fighting.'
