UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='In the King\'s audience chamber you will find the Lady Hoteshem.  She can assist you in getting to Arathi Basin where The League of Arathor is in need of assistance against The Defilers.',Text0_1_loc9='In the King\'s audience chamber you will find the Lady Hoteshem.  She can assist you in getting to Arathi Basin where The League of Arathor is in need of assistance against The Defilers.',Text1_0_loc9='It\'s admirable what The League of Arathor is attempting to do in Arathi Basin.  Too bad those undead abominations and their Horde friends are standing in the way.  Head over to Stormwind Keep.  Lady Hoteshem awaits you in the King\'s audience chamber.  She can help you to get to Arathi Basin.',Text1_1_loc9='It\'s admirable what The League of Arathor is attempting to do in Arathi Basin.  Too bad those undead abominations and their Horde friends are standing in the way.  Head over to Stormwind Keep.  Lady Hoteshem awaits you in the King\'s audience chamber.  She can help you to get to Arathi Basin.' WHERE entry=7650;
