Text0_0_loc9='Well met master of Rod and Reel!   If you be willing to test your skills against the best fisher-folk in the lands then listen up!   On this very Sunday there be a contest in Stranglethorn where the master angler will be chosen!$B$B'
Text0_0_loc9='Paragons of Power are powerful mojo.  They are Gurubashi Empire mojo.  We Zandalar must get mojo.  The tribe will take mojo for our own.  The Blood God will not destroy us.$B$BThere are three kinds of Paragons in Zul\'Gurub.  Seek coins.  Seek bijous.  Seek primal items.  These are the Paragons.$B$BGo to Zul\'Gurub now.  Kill.  Take the Paragons of Power.  Bring them to the tribe.  Earn our respect.  Earn our battle gear.  Earn real power.'
Text0_0_loc9='We already have a winner for our contest, but Jang is willing to purchase any Tastyfish that you have fished up!$B$BThere is always next Sunday for you to show your Angling skill!'
Text0_0_loc9='Behind me is the Altar of Zanza, a sacred place for us Zandalar.  We pray here to bolster our resolve in preparation for war against the Blood God, Hakkar.$B$BProve yourself to the tribe by using the altar to destroy any of the Hakkari Bijous you might find inside Zul\'Gurub.  Also, I will trade you Honor Tokens our tribe uses for sets of coins you may find in Zul\'Gurub.  Bring me the coins that I seek, and you will be rewarded!'
