Text0_0_loc9='You\'re hunting Deathclasp, $N?  Color me impressed.  I lost two of my men to her this week alone.  Let\'s hope your luck is better than theirs.'
Text0_0_loc9='Hey!  Thanks for saving my hide!  I think I\'ll be lying down for a while until I recover my strength.'
Text0_0_loc9='Who are you?  Where am I?  I feel... so weak...'
