Text0_0_loc9='The Sunspire held a beautiful vantage of the Sunwell... once.  Our lives have been turned upside down, $N, but we nonetheless carry on.  It is our way; we are survivors.$B$BIf you are to survive this upheaval... to carry on in your own right, then you MUST learn how to survive.  All blood elves must do this.  You must master your insatiable hungering for magic before it masters you.'
Text0_0_loc9='Your continued service to the Blood Elves is paramount to our survival!  We must all pitch in and pull ourselves out of the mire we all find ourselves in.$B$BIf you\'re ready to work, then let\'s get started.'
Text0_0_loc9='Knowledge is power - TRUE power, my young friend.  You\'ll be wise to acquire as much of it as you can, and pay proper heed to those who have already done so.$B$BBefore the razing of the Sunwell, we fooled ourselves into thinking we had neared the apex of our civilization.  It took the Scourge to bring us to our knees... and in a way, back to reality.'
