Text0_0_loc9='Around this reindeer\'s neck is a tag with the Smokywood Pastures logo on it and a name - "Metzen".$B$BMetzen looks at you with sad, forlorn eyes.  It is almost as if the reindeer has been immobilized by some unseen force.'
Text0_0_loc9='Metzen\'s eyes light up with reindeer joy as you sprinkle the dust on him.  He shakes his antlers at you and breathes out a heavy sigh of what sounds like relief.$B$BAround you, magical energy begins to swell.  It would seem that something\'s about to happen!'
Text0_0_loc9='Even if you somehow managed to free us without defeating C\'Thun, we would focus all of our powers to see the beast banished back to the hell from whence it came - AT ANY COST.'
