Text0_0_loc9='To honor your elders is to honor your culture and your people, $C.  For this, the Coins of Ancestry serve as a tangible means to recognize those who choose to follow a venerable path of respect.$B$BDuring this Lunar Festival, you may have the opportunity to honor many elders.  As you do so, you will acquire the Coins of Ancestry.  Bring me these coins, and I will reward your diligence with a selection of unique items.$B'
