Text0_0_loc9='Hey, $Gmister:miss;.  You look like a $C with discerning tastes in wine.  I have a favor to ask, and I think I can make you an offer you can\'t refuse...forget about it!'
Text0_0_loc9='What are you looking at, $Glad : lass;?  Never seen a dwarf before, then?$B$BYou\'d best be on yer way if you don\'t want any trouble.'
Text0_0_loc9='Ah, you must be the $Glad : lass; assigned to show me around the Eversong Woods.  Took your sweet time getting here, didn\'t you?$B$BVery well, off we go.  Let us not waste one more minute.'
