Text0_0_loc9='<The blood elf quickly regains consciousness as you pour the draught into his mouth.>$B$BI owe you my life, $C.  Without your help I would\'ve succumbed to the Scourge\'s painful torture.'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='<The blood elf lies on the floor in some manner of induced torpor.>',Text0_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text0:',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8457;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='<The Forsaken female is curled up on the floor, her face in a grimace.  She does not appear capable of getting up on her own at the moment.>',Text0_1_loc9='<The Forsaken female is curled up on the floor, her face in a grimace.  She does not appear capable of getting up on her own at the moment.>',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8459;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Ahhhhggg... this pain in my head is killing me.$B$BThey must\'ve sent you to rescue me.  Took them long enough!  Do you have any idea of the things they do to prisoners here?',Text0_1_loc9='Ahhhhggg... this pain in my head is killing me.$B$BThey must\'ve sent you to rescue me.  Took them long enough!  Do you have any idea of the things they do to prisoners here?',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8460;
Text0_0_loc9='<The blood elf lies limp on the table.  While he\'s still breathing, he appears to have been the victim of potent sedative toxins.>'
Text0_0_loc9='Well met, $R. I am here as a resource of advice for the High Executor to make use of as he will. I am confident that together we can forge the Horde into something that is even stronger than before and turn back the Scourge menace once and for all!'
Text0_0_loc9='<Varnis coughs violently as the restorative draught takes effect.>$B$BThank you for rescuing me.  I must go back to Tranquillien at once!'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The drafts of fresh air that blow from Eversong from time to time really upset my stomach, if you know what I mean.',Text0_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text0:',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8464;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='If it is a matter of import that you wish to speak on, $C, it may be more appropriate to seek an audience with Dame Auriferous. I warn you though, she is very busy and you may be in for quite a wait.',Text0_1_loc9='If it is a matter of import that you wish to speak on, $C, it may be more appropriate to seek an audience with Dame Auriferous. I warn you though, she is very busy and you may be in for quite a wait.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8466;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Normally it would not be my place to speak with you directly; rather, you would seek an audience with milady. However, I did give you a task directly, so what is it that we need to discuss?',Text0_1_loc9='Normally it would not be my place to speak with you directly; rather, you would seek an audience with milady. However, I did give you a task directly, so what is it that we need to discuss?',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8467;
Text0_0_loc9='$C, Dame Auriferous has conveyed to me her great pleasure in the service that you have done us in the past. She wishes to extend to you her hope that you will continue to be a champion of sin\'dorei interests here in the Ghostlands.',Text0_1_loc9='$C, Dame Auriferous has conveyed to me her great pleasure in the service that you have done us in the past. She wishes to extend to you her hope that you will continue to be a champion of sin\'dorei interests here in the Ghostlands.'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='This sign contains various announcements and notices of rewards.',Text0_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text0:',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8469;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='We\'ve important work to do, $N.  Let us attack our enemies while their guard is down.  Let us show them that sin\'dorei vengeance never forgets nor forgives.',Text0_1_loc9='We\'ve important work to do, $N.  Let us attack our enemies while their guard is down.  Let us show them that sin\'dorei vengeance never forgets nor forgives.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8470;
Text0_0_loc9='The tides of war have come again. From the cold north, the Lich King\'s necropolises have laid siege to our lands.  He and his cursed general, Kel\'Thuzad, send flying necropolises to invade across the world.'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Well this is troublesome! How am I supposed to collect the ore samples for the magisters if the mines have been overrun with gnoll vermin?',Text0_1_loc9='Well this is troublesome! How am I supposed to collect the ore samples for the magisters if the mines have been overrun with gnoll vermin?',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8472;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Where could she possibly be? I sent my apprentice, Shatharia, to the Underlight Mines to the west quite some time ago. We need those ore samples back, and fast or our experiment is going to fail!',Text0_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text0:',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8474;
Text0_0_loc9='Without delivery of the Underlight ore in such a timely fashion, our research would have failed.$B$BJust wait until Shatharia shows her head here again. I\'ve got some interesting tasks for her, you can be sure of it!'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Sin\'dorei have lost far too much in the past years.  Our land, our homes, even our identities...$B$BIt\'s about time we started taking it all back.',Text0_1_loc9='Sin\'dorei have lost far too much in the past years.  Our land, our homes, even our identities...$B$BIt\'s about time we started taking it all back.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8476;
Text0_0_loc9='Before we can overcome external obstacles like the Scourge and the Amani trolls, we must overcome obstacles from within.  The Wretched have been a nuisance for long enough; it is time we vanquished them.'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Think you could help me to get out of here?',Text0_1_loc9='Think you could help me to get out of here?',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8478;
Text0_0_loc9='Amongst the various pieces of parchment containing checklists and other information from the Farstriders, one stands out. It is a drawing of a hideous troll, perhaps the most fearsome creature that you have ever seen!'
Text0_0_loc9='Indeed, the hills of Winterspring are currently attempting to withstand a renewed Scourge assault. Your assistance would help them greatly.$B$BNumber of Necropolises remaining: $2284W'
Text7_0_loc9='0'
Text0_0_loc9='For the time being, that area is free of Scourge influence. I fear it will only be a matter of time before they return.'
Text0_0_loc9='If additional support is not soon sent to the Burning Steppes, I fear the Scourge will establish a base of operations there. If you can, you should go there to aid the defenders.$B$BNumber of Necropolises remaining: $2281W'
Text7_0_loc9='0'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Many an advantage can be gained from getting to know your enemy.  Take that lesson to heart, $N.$B$BThe more we learn about the Scourge the better prepared we are to defeat them.',Text0_1_loc9='Many an advantage can be gained from getting to know your enemy.  Take that lesson to heart, $N.$B$BThe more we learn about the Scourge the better prepared we are to defeat them.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8485;
Text0_0_loc9='The Scourge are establishing small staging points in the places under attack, receiving communications and other assistance from the necropolises that fly overhead. From what we can tell, the only way to root them out is by killing the ground forces that surround the points.'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You\'re welcome to stay at the Farstrider Enclave for as long as you\'d like, $C.  We welcome any who would aid us in our endeavors in the Ghostlands.',Text0_1_loc9='You\'re welcome to stay at the Farstrider Enclave for as long as you\'d like, $C.  We welcome any who would aid us in our endeavors in the Ghostlands.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8487;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Stray arcane forces can do strange things to the land, the elements and even the spirits of the dead.',Text0_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text0:',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8488;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The High Executor is a very busy man, $C.  Maybe I can help you with whatever you need?',Text0_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text0:',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8489;
Text0_0_loc9='You\'ve done us exemplary service, $N. Between dealing with the gnolls at the Underlight Mines, and the mummified trolls in the Amani Catacombs, you\'ve dealt a mighty blow to our enemies!$B$B$G Good job! : We should get together for drinks sometime, what do you say?;'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Good to see you again, $G man! : gorgeous!; We work well together; $G see you around. : I hope we get to continue to do so.;',Text0_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text0:',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8491;
Text0_0_loc9='Word got back to me through channels concerning Lady Sylvanas\'s reaction to you and the recovery of her necklace. I still think you did the right thing; don\'t worry too much about how the lady reacted.$B$BNow, state your business.'
Text0_0_loc9='What can I say, $C? You\'re a true $G hero : heroine;! Not only have you personally saved many of my rangers, but you\'ve dealt a decisive blow against the Shadowpine trolls. Are you sure that you don\'t want to stay here and be one of my Farstriders?$B$BFare well, $N.'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Your help with the Shadowpine trolls is proving invaluable, $C. Keep this up and maybe we\'ll be able to turn our attention back to dealing with the Scourge.',Text0_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text0:',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8495;
Text0_0_loc9='You\'ve dealt the decisive blow against the Shadowpine trolls, $N. I only hope that we can muster our forces quickly enough to finish them off before they receive reinforcements from Zul\'Aman.$B$BIt would be nice if Tranquillien were to reinforce us.'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Certainly, $N. You only need to tell me what reputation you would like to know about.$B',Text0_1_loc9='Certainly, $N. You only need to tell me what reputation you would like to know about.$B',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8498;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Certainly, $N.$B$BAdventurers that the Dawn views as honored must submit a combined total of 40 insignias to access superior items. To access items of even greater power, they would be required to submit a total of 150 insignias.$B$BI must admit, the price is high even for those honored amongst the Dawn.$B',Text0_1_loc9='Certainly, $N.$B$BAdventurers that the Dawn views as honored must submit a combined total of 40 insignias to access superior items. To access items of even greater power, they would be required to submit a total of 150 insignias.$B$BI must admit, the price is high even for those honored amongst the Dawn.$B',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8499;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Certainly, $N.$B$BAdventurers that the Dawn views as revered must submit a combined total of 14 insignias to access superior items. To access items of even greater power, they would be required to submit a total of 90 insignias.$B$BThose that are revered by the Dawn will find the cost of superior items quite reasonable! The cost for the more powerful items is still high.$B',Text0_1_loc9='Certainly, $N.$B$BAdventurers that the Dawn views as revered must submit a combined total of 14 insignias to access superior items. To access items of even greater power, they would be required to submit a total of 90 insignias.$B$BThose that are revered by the Dawn will find the cost of superior items quite reasonable! The cost for the more powerful items is still high.$B',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8500;
Text0_0_loc9='The situation is more grim than many have been led to believe. The Forsaken are here as allies in the fight against our common enemy, the Scourge.$B$BTrust me when I say this, without them the Ghostlands would be lost and the Scourge would already have overrun all of Eversong Woods!$B$BBut more than anything else, we need your help in reclaiming our once proud lands!'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Certainly, $N.$B$BAdventurers that the Dawn views as exalted must submit a combined total of 12 insignias to access superior items. To access items of even greater power, they would be required to submit a total of 54 insignias.$B$BThose exalted in the eyes of the Dawn receive the greatest discounts.$B',Text0_1_loc9='Certainly, $N.$B$BAdventurers that the Dawn views as exalted must submit a combined total of 12 insignias to access superior items. To access items of even greater power, they would be required to submit a total of 54 insignias.$B$BThose exalted in the eyes of the Dawn receive the greatest discounts.$B',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8502;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Certainly, $N.$B$BAdventurers that the Dawn views as friendly must submit a combined total of 60 insignias to access superior items. To access items of even greater power, they would be required to submit a total of 220 insignias.$B$BI must admit, the price is quite high for adventurers not favored by the Dawn.$B',Text0_1_loc9='Certainly, $N.$B$BAdventurers that the Dawn views as friendly must submit a combined total of 60 insignias to access superior items. To access items of even greater power, they would be required to submit a total of 220 insignias.$B$BI must admit, the price is quite high for adventurers not favored by the Dawn.$B',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8503;
Text0_0_loc9='These Runestones protect the lands in Eversong from becoming tainted by the Scourge.  The Western Runestone failed long ago, forcing us to burn the ground around it.$B$BAs long as I live I won\'t allow the remaining Runestones to fail us.  That is my oath.'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Well, you didn\'t come all this way out here to jaw over a cup of tea. Let\'s see how you might be able to help get us out of this situation.',Text0_1_loc9='Well, you didn\'t come all this way out here to jaw over a cup of tea. Let\'s see how you might be able to help get us out of this situation.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8505;
Text0_0_loc9='There are those who would say that the Argent Crusade is a thing of the past.  I am one of them, but not because the Scourge have fallen.$B$BNo... it is because of their stubborn ways.  They\'ve become too much like the church that they seceded from: too rigid, too governed by honor and order.  This is what I\'m trying to tell Barthalomew, anyhow.$B$BSure, it may sound a bit jingoistic, but it makes for a good debate.'
Text0_0_loc9='Master craftsman Omarion just vanished one night. Like a toot in the wind... Poof! Gone! Bah, now I\'m the only one left to craft the goods for the boys on the front lines.'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='<Omarion grumbles something under his breath.>$B$BBut of course I can help you, dear $G boy:girl;. It is my dying wish... my final desire. Please, take this handbook. The information on its pages are a compilation of all that I know and have learned in the past 30 some-odd years of my miserable life. Give the handbook to that good for nothing apprentice of mine that\'s probably sitting on his fat duff at Light\'s Hope Chapel.',Text0_1_loc9='<Omarion grumbles something under his breath.>$B$BBut of course I can help you, dear $G boy:girl;. It is my dying wish... my final desire. Please, take this handbook. The information on its pages are a compilation of all that I know and have learned in the past 30 some-odd years of my miserable life. Give the handbook to that good for nothing apprentice of mine that\'s probably sitting on his fat duff at Light\'s Hope Chapel.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8516;
Text0_0_loc9='<Tarsis groans.>$B$BThere may still be time... Listen closely, mortal.$B$BThrough time and across the Nether I have searched. Deals made with a host of evil and villainy so wretched...$B$B<Tarsis coughs blood into his hands.>$B$BWould you... would you believe that even Elune has turned her back on me, $R? To die here, in this manner now...'
Text0_0_loc9='The things I have done... such horrible things...$B$B<Tarsis begins to sob.>'
Text0_0_loc9='I am Highborne, $R. It has no meaning now. There was a time, though, when this world was ruled by Highborne. Ten thousand years past...'
Text0_0_loc9='I would have it back, mortal. Atiesh... From it I would create the Highborne anew. I would have it all back. Even the Queen...'
Text0_0_loc9='<Tarsis grabs you weakly by the collar. Even in death you see power unimaginable in his eyes.>$B$BAm I? Then listen closely, for more nonsense is about to escape my lips. Within this citadel you will find my life\'s work: The exact location of every fragment of the splintered staff.'
Text0_0_loc9='Atiesh, Greatstaff of the Guardian. The staff handed down through the ages to each of the Guardians of Tirisfal. The staff corrupted by Sargeras. The staff of the last Guardian. The staff of Medivh.'
Text0_0_loc9='<Tarsis\'s eyes light up.>$B$BI held it once... I held it despite the warnings of the Kirin Tor. I held it, mortal... Power unending. Power to do what I desired, as I desired. And just as quickly, it was taken from me. But I had tasted... And that taste was all that it took.'
Text0_0_loc9='<Tarsis is badly injured.>'
Text0_0_loc9='The battle goes well. The Scourge forces seem weakened. I believe it will only be a matter of time before we drive them from our shores. I will turn my magics to you, to aid in this struggle.',Text0_1_loc9='The battle goes well. The Scourge forces seem weakened. I believe it will only be a matter of time before we drive them from our shores. I will turn my magics to you, to aid in this struggle.'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The first steps of our fight against the Scourge go well. We have had some successes, and hopefully my assistance can aid you in bringing future success to the battle.',Text0_1_loc9='The first steps of our fight against the Scourge go well. We have had some successes, and hopefully my assistance can aid you in bringing future success to the battle.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8527;
Text0_0_loc9='It was lost when the Violet Citadel fell... splintered into forty-two pieces.'
Text0_0_loc9='Kel\'Thuzad has put forth considerable effort in attempting to reform the staff. The pieces were once scattered across this world, from Kalimdor to the South Seas. I myself held twenty of the pieces at one point in time - until they were stolen from me by Kel\'Thuzad\'s minions. It is why I am here.'
Text0_0_loc9='Haven\'t you been listening? No, I very much doubt we would be having this conversation had Kel\'Thuzad formed the staff. Kel\'Thuzad holds the head. His underlings hold forty splinters of Atiesh. The last piece - the base - was uncovered by Brann Bronzebeard. He was last seen in the Silithus desert; undoubtedly doing his best to stay as far away as possible from the relentless seekers Kel\'Thuzad has dispatched into the world.'
Text0_0_loc9='Our Sanctums syphon arcane power from ley-line currents that traverse our lands invisible to the naked eye.$B$BWith the Sunwell gone, they provide us with a steady and reliable source of energy.'
Text0_0_loc9='It\'s a testament to our race\'s tenacity that Fairbreeze Village still stands.  We shall never concede defeat to the Scourge ever again.'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Gangway, ye scurvy dog!  Revilgaz has spared me from the gallows but my punishment might be nearly as bad.',Text0_1_loc9='Gangway, ye scurvy dog!  Revilgaz has spared me from the gallows but my punishment might be nearly as bad.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8536;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You\'d better not be causing trouble, $N!',Text0_1_loc9='You\'d better not be causing trouble, $N!',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8537;
Text0_0_loc9='What can I do for you, $N?  Make it quick, I don\'t have all day!'
Text0_0_loc9='What can I do for you?  No, wait!  What can you do for me?'
Text0_0_loc9='You\'ve served our cause with great loyalty, $N.  Allow me to present you with an unending source of our elemental quintessence.'
Text0_0_loc9='Welcome back, $N.  You\'ve proven a worthy ally against Ragnaros and your presence is always welcome among us.'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Dar\'Khan thinks we\'ll roll over for the Scourge without putting up a fight.  We shall prove him wrong, $N.',Text0_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text0:',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8548;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Can\'t you see that I\'m trying to have a conversation with the lady?  Oh, very well, she seems preoccupied anyway.$B$BI deal in only the finest drinks, both local and exotic in vintage.  Care to have a look?',Text0_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text0:',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8549;
Text0_0_loc9='Is that a list from Saltheril\'s Haven?  No doubt, his lordship will require a bottle of my finest.  And, of course, any friend of Lord Saltheril deserves a special price on such a fine vintage.'
Text0_0_loc9='We have won $2219W battles against the Scourge.  Gird yourself, $N, for this war is far from over.'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='If you have the coin, I have the food and drink to keep that appetite of yours satisfied.  Every copper goes to keeping the Retreat in tip-top shape.',Text0_1_loc9='If you have the coin, I have the food and drink to keep that appetite of yours satisfied.  Every copper goes to keeping the Retreat in tip-top shape.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8552;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Is that a list from Lord Saltheril that you have there? Yes, I can sell you a batch of appetizers, fresh off the fire.',Text0_1_loc9='Is that a list from Lord Saltheril that you have there? Yes, I can sell you a batch of appetizers, fresh off the fire.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8553;
Text0_0_loc9='I have all manner of goods for sale, $C.  Browse at your leisure.'
Text0_0_loc9='A list... how intriguing.  Ah yes, the shipment of fireworks for Lord Saltheril.  He hasn\'t paid for them; are you here to purchase them on his behalf, $C?'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Is there no end to these undead?  It seems that for every ghoul or skeleton we kill, two take its place.',Text0_1_loc9='Is there no end to these undead?  It seems that for every ghoul or skeleton we kill, two take its place.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8558;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='$C, you didn\'t happen to see a courier on your way here? We are awaiting word from Silvermoon City and their messenger is late!',Text0_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text0:',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8561;
Text0_0_loc9='Sometimes I stand here, looking into the forest beyond the lake, and I see the land as it once was... green and full of life.'
Text0_0_loc9='We really must perfect a way to deal with those smelly Shadowpine trolls!'
Text0_0_loc9='I must say, you delivered my poison and dealt with those trolls most ruthlessly, $C. You\'ve got the makings of quite a talented young $G man : lady;!'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='We must maintain a state of vigilance, $C! Between Dar\'Khan the Betrayer and his Scourge, and the Shadowpine trolls backed by the might of Zul\'Aman, we\'re barely keeping our heads above water here. We really shouldn\'t have to be dividing our attentions!$B$BI hope you\'re here to help.',Text0_1_loc9='We must maintain a state of vigilance, $C! Between Dar\'Khan the Betrayer and his Scourge, and the Shadowpine trolls backed by the might of Zul\'Aman, we\'re barely keeping our heads above water here. We really shouldn\'t have to be dividing our attentions!$B$BI hope you\'re here to help.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8569;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I\'m glad that you\'re here to help, $C. The faster we can deal with these trolls, the faster we\'ll get to send the scourge back to where they came from.',Text0_1_loc9='I\'m glad that you\'re here to help, $C. The faster we can deal with these trolls, the faster we\'ll get to send the scourge back to where they came from.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8570;
Text0_0_loc9='One set of trolls dealt with, one yet to go. You have no idea how much I appreciate what you\'re doing, $N! Before you came along I didn\'t think we\'d ever get the Shadowpine problem under control.',Text0_1_loc9='One set of trolls dealt with, one yet to go. You have no idea how much I appreciate what you\'re doing, $N! Before you came along I didn\'t think we\'d ever get the Shadowpine problem under control.'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You wouldn\'t believe some of the rabble that we\'ve had come through here lately. Most are more trouble than the supposed help that they provide. Nothing at all like you.$B$BYou sure you don\'t want to sign up with the Farstriders?',Text0_1_loc9='You wouldn\'t believe some of the rabble that we\'ve had come through here lately. Most are more trouble than the supposed help that they provide. Nothing at all like you.$B$BYou sure you don\'t want to sign up with the Farstriders?',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8572;
Text0_0_loc9='The Scourge brought only small forces to bear against each of Azeroth\'s capital cities, while their main forces periodically attack the following lands:$B$BAzshara, the Blasted Lands, the Burning Steppes, the Tanaris Desert, the Eastern Plaguelands and Winterspring.'
