UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I am most grateful for your help, $C!',Text0_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text0:',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8650;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Ah, you\'re the one who found the letter. Thank you for the... news, I suppose, about my family. You\'re welcome to what food and drink I can offer.',Text0_1_loc9='Ah, you\'re the one who found the letter. Thank you for the... news, I suppose, about my family. You\'re welcome to what food and drink I can offer.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8653;
Text0_0_loc9='Sid\'s the name. It\'s nice to see some new faces around here. What can I do you for?'
Text0_0_loc9='Though we\'ve arrived at the promised land, $N, much work remains to be done.  Our people won\'t reach Kael\'thas if we lunge desperately across Outland.$B$BSafe routes must be found, resources must be secured and our enemies must be avoided or destroyed.'
Text0_0_loc9='What I wouldn\'t give for a healing crystal right about now!'
Text0_0_loc9='Thank you for delivering that list!  My leg is almost recovered enough that I\'ll be able to walk back to the crash site.'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='How are we ever going to get out of here?',Text0_1_loc9='How are we ever going to get out of here?',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8664;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Thank you for taking care of the lake, the lashers and the owlkin, $C.',Text0_1_loc9='Thank you for taking care of the lake, the lashers and the owlkin, $C.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8665;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='None will question your actions, $C.  You did what had to be done.',Text0_1_loc9='None will question your actions, $C.  You did what had to be done.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8666;
Text0_0_loc9='It is good to see you alive and well, $N!'
Text0_0_loc9='Thank you again for replenishing our healing crystals. I hear that you\'re helping out all over the place. Keep up the good work!'
Text0_0_loc9='I hope yer not here for our ale. We\'re not sharing and that\'s final!$B$BIt\'s not our fault no one had the good sense to bring beer to Outland but us.'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Here\'s to hoping not all of Outland is as barren as this region.  This is quite a change from the green grasslands and forests of Eversong.',Text0_1_loc9='Here\'s to hoping not all of Outland is as barren as this region.  This is quite a change from the green grasslands and forests of Eversong.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8674;
Text0_0_loc9='There exist in Outland demonic presences much more powerful than anything we\'d ever seen in the old world.$B$BGreat power shall come to those who do not shy away from it, but learn to harness and master its strength.'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='' WHERE entry=8676;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='How may I serve?',Text0_1_loc9='How may I serve?',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8678;
Text0_0_loc9='Outland just oozes with magical energy, it\'s in the very air.  Can you feel it, $N?  I can\'t think of a place better suited to our race.  Soon the sin\'dorei shall have a new land to call our own!'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='My husband\'s been missing for days.  We went on this pilgrimage together; we were supposed to finish it together.$B$BAll this worry has gotten me tapping into mana crystals more often than I really should.',Text0_1_loc9='My husband\'s been missing for days.  We went on this pilgrimage together; we were supposed to finish it together.$B$BAll this worry has gotten me tapping into mana crystals more often than I really should.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8681;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Dragonhawks, if raised properly, are really quite tame.  Don\'t you think that is fascinating?  To be so friendly and companionable if raised right and so vicious and deadly in the wild...I just love them so much.',Text0_1_loc9='Dragonhawks, if raised properly, are really quite tame.  Don\'t you think that is fascinating?  To be so friendly and companionable if raised right and so vicious and deadly in the wild...I just love them so much.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8682;
Text0_0_loc9='Don\'t... worry... about me...'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I really don\'t think our situation is so bad.  I am certain it will all be rectified soon and the Sunwell\'s power will be restored.  It just can\'t possibly be as bad as everyone is making it out to be.',Text0_1_loc9='I really don\'t think our situation is so bad.  I am certain it will all be rectified soon and the Sunwell\'s power will be restored.  It just can\'t possibly be as bad as everyone is making it out to be.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8684;
Text0_0_loc9='Befriending the Sunstriders has paid off; I get to conduct research with subjects I can only find in Outland and they get... my charming personality and rugged good looks.'
Text0_0_loc9='I was only an infant when my father was deployed to this wasteland. All that I have ever known of him is what others have told me.$B$BDo your dreams change, $N? Mine do not. I have one dream: A crimson skyline envelops me as Legion, numbering beyond comprehension, battle in the distance. I kneel before the body of a man, presumably my father, and weep. As he is gasping for air, his body wholly crushed, he whispers something. Despite every effort, I am unable to hear what he is trying to tell me.'
Text0_0_loc9='You think I\'m being cruel to this worm?$B$BThey\'ve killed two of my men this month!  We\'re too kind to this Wretched scum.'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Welcome to Fairbreeze Village.  Silvermoon\'s all but given up on us, but we refuse to leave.  This is our home.',Text0_1_loc9='Welcome to Fairbreeze Village.  Silvermoon\'s all but given up on us, but we refuse to leave.  This is our home.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8699;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='My job consists of one task and one task only: ensuring that the West Sanctum runs smoothly.$B$BYou\'ll have to excuse my temper but, as you can see, the situation here is a bit out of hand.',Text0_1_loc9='Could night elf saboteurs be behind this?  I doubt it.  With the load we\'ve been putting on the West Sanctum it was only a matter of time until something went wrong.',Text1_0_loc9='Could night elf saboteurs be behind this?  I doubt it.  With the load we\'ve been putting on the West Sanctum it was only a matter of time until something went wrong.',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8700;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='With the Emperors slain, the magical protection blocking teleportation within the temple has been greatly weakened. If you desire, I am able to translocate you to the Emperors\' lair.',Text0_1_loc9='With the Emperors slain, the magical protection blocking teleportation within the temple has been greatly weakened. If you desire, I am able to translocate you to the Emperors\' lair.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8701;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='With Ouro slain the way is clear to the final chamber. I am able to transport you there, if you desire.',Text0_1_loc9='With Ouro slain the way is clear to the final chamber. I am able to transport you there, if you desire.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8702;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Enjoying the festival, $C?$B$BWhile the Flame Wardens tend to the fires of the present, I am more of a historian, keeping close the festivals past. I\'m also, of course, documenting this year\'s festivities. Things are going well thus far, don\'t you think?$B$BYou know, $N, there is power inherent in all festival fires burning throughout the holiday. We\'re taking care of ours, but I\'m certain there are sacred flames burning deep within our enemy\'s cities...',Text0_1_loc9='Enjoying the festival, $C?$B$BWhile the Flame Wardens tend to the fires of the present, I am more of a historian, keeping close the festivals past. I\'m also, of course, documenting this year\'s festivities. Things are going well thus far, don\'t you think?$B$BYou know, $N, there is power inherent in all festival fires burning throughout the holiday. We\'re taking care of ours, but I\'m certain there are sacred flames burning deep within our enemy\'s cities...',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8703;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='If you\'re looking for work, $C, grab yourself a pick and get to digging. There\'re ruins out there as far as the eye can see!',Text0_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text0:',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8712;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Greetings, $N. My fellow Sons of Lothar and I have been stuck on this miserable world for close to twenty years now. We held on as best we could, but it still amazes me that the threats we face today are just the shadows of our past failures.$B$BPerhaps you will help us atone for them?  $B',Text0_1_loc9='Greetings, $N. My fellow Sons of Lothar and I have been stuck on this miserable world for close to twenty years now. We held on as best we could, but it still amazes me that the threats we face today are just the shadows of our past failures.$B$BPerhaps you will help us atone for them?  $B',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8713;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The extent of the corruption in Outland is truly astonishing, $C. The Cenarion Circle hopes to understand how these creatures have managed to survive. Studying this broken, tortured land and its inhabitants may yet teach us how to heal ailing parts of our own world.',Text0_1_loc9='The extent of the corruption in Outland is truly astonishing, $C. The Cenarion Circle hopes to understand how these creatures have managed to survive. Studying this broken, tortured land and its inhabitants may yet teach us how to heal ailing parts of our own world.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8715;
Text0_0_loc9='It is sad to see what has happened to this land.  The Cenarion Expedition will do what it can to understand and heal the damage that has been done.'
Text0_0_loc9='You look lost, $C. Don\'t make me put you to work on the walls with the other peons.'
Text0_0_loc9='Well met, $C. Your arrival in Thrallmar could not have occurred at a better time. The warchief is depending on us, since he cannot be here himself.',Text0_1_loc9='Well met, $C. Your arrival in Thrallmar could not have occurred at a better time. The warchief is depending on us, since he cannot be here himself.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:'
Text0_0_loc9='Thrallmar needs you, $C. The warchief needs you. Stand ready to do your duty.',Text0_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text0:',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:'
Text0_0_loc9='Few bouts are won by sheer strength.  It is cunning, reflexes and knowledge of your weapon that wins the day in the end.',Text0_1_loc9='Few bouts are won by sheer strength.  It is cunning, reflexes and knowledge of your weapon that wins the day in the end.'
Text0_0_loc9='Another hero? The fates smile upon us on this day, $N.',Text0_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text0:',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:'
Text0_0_loc9='I\'ve heard something of your exploits, $N.  I know that while you\'re here in Forsaken lands that you\'ll comport yourself with dignity and as a true hero of the sin\'dorei!'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I bid you welcome, $C.',Text0_1_loc9='I bid you welcome, $C.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8750;
Text0_0_loc9='I haven\'t time for idle chatter, $C. I must see to the pilgrims and ensure they are prepared for the long journey ahead.'
Text0_0_loc9='Welcome to Falcon Watch, $C. I see to the needs of the pilgrims and help them in continuing their long journey. If you haven\'t yet undertaken the pilgrimage, I can provide you with the information you will need.'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Walk always in the Light, $N.',Text0_1_loc9='Walk always in the Light, $N.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8754;
