UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I am a night elf, stranger. While you may know nothing of my kind, we know much of you and your progenitors. You may not call yourself eredar but, in appearance, you share many similarities.$B$BYou have helped my allies, and for that I am thankful; but for the time being, you walk a tenuous path. Perhaps in time, you will be able to dissolve the doubts and fears that I hold in my heart.',Text0_1_loc9='I am a night elf, stranger. While you may know nothing of my kind, we know much of you and your progenitors. You may not call yourself eredar but, in appearance, you share many similarities.$B$BYou have helped my allies, and for that I am thankful; but for the time being, you walk a tenuous path. Perhaps in time, you will be able to dissolve the doubts and fears that I hold in my heart.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8862;
Text0_0_loc9='Watch your step around here, stranger.'
Text0_0_loc9='You\'ve been a great help thus far, $N. You would do well to help out the others at the encampment.$B$BAnd don\'t worry about those goblins, I\'m taking care of everything.'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='It is good to see you again, $N. Perhaps once things have settled down, I can talk to you about the priceless treasure that we have lost...',Text0_1_loc9='It is good to see you again, $N. Perhaps once things have settled down, I can talk to you about the priceless treasure that we have lost...',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8866;
Text0_0_loc9='What are you looking at?'
Text0_0_loc9='I am Adamant Ironheart of the great city of Ironforge. As you could probably guess by looking at my uniform, I was once part of the Ironforge elite guard. Yep, I was Magni\'s right hand man! At least until I retired. Now I dabble in archaeology. It\'s a hobby really; plus I figured it would be a great way to see the world!'
Text0_0_loc9='<Cowlen sobs.>'
Text0_0_loc9='What could I have done to give the gods cause to lash out at me with such ferocity? All that I cherished is gone - dead or destroyed. My family taken from me by the brutes of the forest. My home razed. My ship sunk.$B$BI am a broken man, stranded on a broken island.$B$BPerhaps you are you here to finish the job? Make it quick, I will not resist. Take my life, stranger; I am too cowardly to do it myself. My hand shivers... the blade will not strike true.$B'
Text0_0_loc9='If not the gods, who? How? What could cause such strife?'
Text0_0_loc9='Legion? Demons? They hunt you? My people have also been hunted by Legion: Targeted by their dark masters for damnation.$B$B<Cowlen wipes the tears away.>$B$BIt is the reason that I moved my family here oh-so-many years ago.'
Text0_0_loc9='Greetings, $C. Before the night elves invited the draenei to join them here, this glade was all but forgotten.$B$BThe kaldorei are deeply tied to these lands, and we draenei are honored that they have asked us to share in the task of revitalizing Forest Song.'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='It\'s good to see a new face out here. Our outpost is small and our enemies plentiful. We are surrounded by those who seek to destroy us: the satyr to the west, the orcs of the Warsong Lumber camp to the south, and the demons of Felfire Hill.$B$BWe\'re grateful that the draenei have accepted our invitation to join us in fortifying Forest Song against these myriad threats.',Text0_1_loc9='It\'s good to see a new face out here. Our outpost is small and our enemies plentiful. We are surrounded by those who seek to destroy us: the satyr to the west, the orcs of the Warsong Lumber camp to the south, and the demons of Felfire Hill.$B$BWe\'re grateful that the draenei have accepted our invitation to join us in fortifying Forest Song against these myriad threats.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8874;
Text0_0_loc9='It\'s good to hear the voices of others here in Forest Song again. I\'d begun to feel as though I might be the last of the kaldorei ever to set eyes on these lands before their descent into corruption.'
Text0_0_loc9='Can you feel the evil to the south?  By the Hand, it must be cleansed!'
Text0_0_loc9='With you and your people as allies, we have decided to stay on this island and rebuild. Elune bless you, hero.$B$BWhile the sadness still comes and goes, I think we will survive.$B'
Text0_0_loc9='You\'re a $R, right?  I am heartened to see you here!  We can use all of the help that we can get.'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='There are demons to kill, $C.  Do you have the backbone to do what needs to be done?',Text0_1_loc9='There are demons to kill, $C.  Do you have the backbone to do what needs to be done?',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8883;
