Text0_0_loc9='All hail the exalted hero!',Text0_1_loc9='All hail the exalted hero!',Text1_0_loc9='The story of your journey will be told for years to come!'
Text2_0_loc9='I finally have a story to tell my grandchildren about... A traitor to the kingdom was living among us!$B',Text3_0_loc9='Truth be told, I never liked that gnome...'
Text4_0_loc9='We are lucky to have survived this ordeal. If it wasn\'t for you, everyone on this island could have been killed!',Text5_0_loc9='I wonder how many more of them live among us. I knew Spark for years - never could I have imagined that he was a traitor.'
