Text0_0_loc9='Welcome to my shop!'
Text0_0_loc9='Ah, the Promised One has arrived. Welcome to Stillpine Hold.'
Text0_0_loc9='Good tidings, $C. I am Stillpine the Younger, heir to the throne of Stillpine.'
Text0_0_loc9='It is you who will defend my people and usher in a new era of prosperity for Stillpine!'
Text0_0_loc9='I\'m afraid I\'m rather busy fixing horseshoes at the moment.  Would you mind coming back at another time?'
Text0_0_loc9='I once served Medivh... or pretended to.  I helped the Violet Eye keep a close eye on the Master.$B$BBut now all I can think of is... making horseshoes.  Over and over.'
Text0_0_loc9='You know about the Violet Eye then?  Maybe I\'ll have time for you later.$B$BI have to get back to my work.'
