Text0_0_loc9='Need me to take care of your animal companions?'
Text0_0_loc9='On Argus, Mac\'Aree was the most sacred of our cities.$B$BWould you believe me if I told you that the walkways were lined with precious minerals? That the rivers glittered even in complete darkness?$B$BI long for those days... How long has it been? A thousand years? Ten-thousand?'
Text0_0_loc9='If you only learn one thing during your time in Bloodmyst, $C, I hope that it is vigilance. This island claims the unwary first, then begins to wear down even the most guarded of warriors.$B$BEverywhere you turn, a foe stands ready to take your life.'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Everything that has happened since the crash is little more than a blur. It seems like a lifetime ago that I was aboard the Exodar.$B$BNow, my reality is restricted to this island with its mutant creatures and endless sea of blood elf agents. Soon, it will be as if I\'ve never known anything different...',Text0_1_loc9='Everything that has happened since the crash is little more than a blur. It seems like a lifetime ago that I was aboard the Exodar.$B$BNow, my reality is restricted to this island with its mutant creatures and endless sea of blood elf agents. Soon, it will be as if I\'ve never known anything different...',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=9034;
Text0_0_loc9='The others look at this landscape and see only death, corruption, and adversity. None of those things are in short supply, true, but that view ignores the opportunities presented by our environment.$B$BI will not stand by and watch these opportunities go ignored, $C. With your help, we can demonstrate to the others here at Blood Watch just how to make use of the environment and its creatures.'
Text0_0_loc9='Hello, $C.$B$BOld man Kessel over there, he\'s a clever one. I\'d be real careful in my dealings with him if I were you.$B$BHe offered me work \'caring for the elekk\' and being the fool I was, I took it to mean feeding, training, and the like. Things became real clear when he handed me the shovel...'
Text0_0_loc9='Thanks for the warning, $N! We shall prepare!'
Text0_0_loc9='Promised One, we thank you for the warning. The Stillpine tribe will be prepared.'
Text0_0_loc9='Thank you for the warning, $N. We will prepare our defenses.'
Text0_0_loc9='I am Kessel, lord of the elekk, disciple of the Hand of Argus. Are you the new recruit?'
Text0_0_loc9='What it means to be a Hand of Argus... We are agents of the Light. We serve without question. We die without question.'
Text0_0_loc9='Did they send you to find me? Well I\'m not going back without my men.'
Text0_0_loc9='Yes, I am one of the \'Broken\'.  I trust that this does not bother you?  Broken or draenei, we must endure the ridicule that some in our society may throw at us.  A better understanding and communication with the elements of this world is all that matters.'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Please, sit and make yourself comfortable.',Text0_1_loc9='Please, sit and make yourself comfortable.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=9051;
Text0_0_loc9='Good day, $C. Are you in need of a reliable hippogryph?'
Text0_0_loc9='Shh! Be very quiet; I\'m observing murlocs.$B$BLiving in an oversized turtle shell is a sacrifice I\'m willing to make for science. After all, if the murlocs see me here, they\'ll react to my presence and contaminate my data!$B$BAs the first gnomish member of the Explorers\' League, I\'m boldly going places no dwarf has gone before!'
Text0_0_loc9='Are you mad? Look around you, mortal. Do you not see that you stand upon sundered earth? Leave this place lest you suffer as my people and I have...'
Text0_0_loc9='Are you blind as well as insane?$B$BI am a ghost - a cruel reminder of a civilization that has long since ceased to exist - anchored to a land that I failed to protect.$B$BLong ago - ten-thousand years past - I was flesh and bone, just like you. I was prince of this land and a dragon rider, blessed by Ysera of the Dream.'
Text0_0_loc9='Have you not heard of Ysera? Guardian of nature? Aspect of the Dream? She is the matron of all green dragons! Aye, it was Ysera herself that gifted my kingdom with her brood. We stood shoulder to shoulder with the noble creatures and they allowed us to ride them into battle against our enemies. All was well for many centuries... until...'
Text0_0_loc9='Deathwing\'s brood... Ysera\'s benevolence raised the ire of Deathwing - patron of the black dragonflight. They attacked us in our sleep! Many died on the initial surge but the greens rose to protect us.$B$B<Prince Toreth points around the island.>$B$BThe bones are all that remain of the once great dragons. None were spared.'
Text0_0_loc9='I was the last to die. As I felt my spirit leaving my mortal shell, I swore a blood oath.$B$B<Prince Toreth shakes his head.>$B$BA pact was made between this land and I: My blood for this world. I became the sole keeper of the history of my people.$B$BI cannot rest until I am secure in knowing that the story of the dragon riders of Loreth\'Aran is not lost in the passages of time.'
Text0_0_loc9='Students are a bit like sheep.  They\'re useful and even likeable when you guide and pay close attention to them.$B$BYou leave them alone for a minute and they end up falling down a cliff or drowning in a shallow river.'
Text0_0_loc9='This sign contains various announcements and notices of rewards for performing dangerous sounding tasks.  Nothing particularly catches your eye; perhaps you should check again at a later time.'
Text0_0_loc9='Greetings, citizen. I ask that you move along if you have nothing to ask of me.'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Marshal Windsor has been expecting you, $N. Unfortunately, he is currently indisposed. He should be returning shortly.',Text0_1_loc9='Marshal Windsor has been expecting you, $N. Unfortunately, he is currently indisposed. He should be returning shortly.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=9064;
Text0_0_loc9='You made it! Outstanding! Marshal Windsor has been expecting you. Would you like me to signal him now?'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Hail, champion. The tale of your deeds will be told throughout the ages. Perhaps one day, a statue of you will stand amongst the heroes of Stormwind.',Text0_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text0:',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=9066;
Text0_0_loc9='Stay away from me, $R! There\'s no telling when the sickness will take me again.$B$BJust leave me alone before it happens again.'
Text0_0_loc9='Examining the corpse, you conclude that this must be Blood Knight Dawnstar, the leader of the failed assault on Deatholme.'
Text0_0_loc9='I can help you establish a guild.'
Text0_0_loc9='A search of the corpse\'s clothing and equipment reveals the insignia you need, undamaged by the battle and foul environment.'
