Text0_0_loc9='[In broken Common] Stillpine be ready! Many thanks!'
Text0_0_loc9='Welcome to the headquarters of the Blood Knights, the defenders of Quel\'Thalas, the faithful servants of Prince Kael\'thas, and the true masters of the Light.'
Text0_0_loc9='Nature favors those willing to learn its secrets, $N.'
Text0_0_loc9='Nature is a powerful force, $R.  Those who seek to subdue never succeed in doing so permanently.'
