Text0_0_loc9='Welcome to the Allerian Stronghold, $C.'
Text0_0_loc9='Be wary, $C. The forest is full of hidden dangers and potential enemies.'
Text0_0_loc9='This is just horrible.$B$BI care not for our own discomforts here, but we must do something to ease the pain of the dead in the Bone Wastes!'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You are here to assist the Aldor?',Text0_1_loc9='You are here to assist the Aldor?',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=9478;
Text0_0_loc9='If you\'re expecting some kind of official welcome, you\'re going to be disappointed, $C. We don\'t stand on tradition, here. What works is what goes.'
Text0_0_loc9='One note stands out from the other various pieces of parchment that are tacked onto this wanted poster.  It\'s a call to slay the bonelashers of the Bone Wastes.'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='No, don\'t feel bad.  I get that a lot.$B$B<Taela looks both amused and annoyed.>$B$BI\'m a HIGH elf, not a blood elf.  Don\'t worry, I\'m not going to suck all of the magic out of you.',Text0_1_loc9='No, don\'t feel bad.  I get that a lot.$B$B<Taela looks both amused and annoyed.>$B$BI\'m a HIGH elf, not a blood elf.  Don\'t worry, I\'m not going to suck all of the magic out of you.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=9484;
Text0_0_loc9='Bonelashers, I hate them all!$B$BIf it weren\'t for the loss of my eye, and the fainting spells that I get sometimes, I\'d be out there shooting them down all the time!'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='There\'s a whole vast forest out there, $C. Let the shaman play with the spirits and the warriors toy with their swords. Terokkar is where I\'ll make my fortune.',Text0_1_loc9='There\'s a whole vast forest out there, $C. Let the shaman play with the spirits and the warriors toy with their swords. Terokkar is where I\'ll make my fortune.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=9487;
Text0_0_loc9='Malukaz chatters incessantly about the historical importance of this forest, but I don\'t have the luxury of indulging in history until our present problems are settled.$B$BI\'m not saying his work here isn\'t important, but someone has to see to the defenses and logistics of running the hold.'
Text0_0_loc9='Until I traveled through Nagrand and came to the forest, I feared that too much of our original culture was lost. I\'m thankful to see that I was wrong.$B$BThere is so much to be done here!'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The opening of the Dark Portal brought news of my people\'s fate. In a way, my exile shielded me from sharing in their downfall, but to see the Farstriders throw their lot in with Kael\'thas...$B$BI never imagined my one-time brethren capable of such a thing.$B$BThe homecoming I once dreamt of will never happen. This forest is the only home I have left.',Text0_1_loc9='The opening of the Dark Portal brought news of my people\'s fate. In a way, my exile shielded me from sharing in their downfall, but to see the Farstriders throw their lot in with Kael\'thas...$B$BI never imagined my one-time brethren capable of such a thing.$B$BThe homecoming I once dreamt of will never happen. This forest is the only home I have left.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=9490;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='When I first arrived, I\'d hoped to meet the town\'s namesake.$B$B<Ros\'eleth glances around.>$B$BMost young high elves outgrow the \'I wanna be a Farstrider\' phase by the time they\'re taken as apprentices. Then, it\'s onto the \'I\'m going to be a magister\' stage.$B$BI don\'t think I ever quite outgrew the Farstrider phase, to be honest. No one dreams of growing up to be a seamstress, but we can\'t have the Farstriders running around naked, as my mother used to say.',Text0_1_loc9='When I first arrived, I\'d hoped to meet the town\'s namesake.$B$B<Ros\'eleth glances around.>$B$BMost young high elves outgrow the \'I wanna be a Farstrider\' phase by the time they\'re taken as apprentices. Then, it\'s onto the \'I\'m going to be a magister\' stage.$B$BI don\'t think I ever quite outgrew the Farstrider phase, to be honest. No one dreams of growing up to be a seamstress, but we can\'t have the Farstriders running around naked, as my mother used to say.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=9492;
Text0_0_loc9='Have you seen the way Ros\'eleth winks at me whenever I go to pick up a garment or hat? When things SETtle down around here, I\'m going to take her for a nice walk in the woods.$B$BFor once, I miss all those fancy taverns in Stormwind.'
Text0_0_loc9='<Kaide hisses at you.>$B$BBe quiet, or you\'ll bring the orcs and the Alliance down on us, you clumsy oaf!$B$BThat\'s right, nod your head, and when we\'re done speaking, you\'ll walk away and forget you found me here.'
Text0_0_loc9='We may be working together, but that only increases the need for discretion. Once again, be mindful of your words and actions.$B$BI can guarantee we\'re far from the only ones out here.'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Yeah, what do you want?  Can\'t you see I\'m busy here?  The Shadow Council isn\'t paying me by the hour!',Text0_1_loc9='Yeah, what do you want?  Can\'t you see I\'m busy here?  The Shadow Council isn\'t paying me by the hour!',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=9497;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='What\'s it look like I\'m doing?  I\'m fixing the place up - all on my own I might add - so that we can move in!$B$BWith a base of operations out here in the forest, it\'ll be easier to keep track of what Shattrath, Allerian, Stonebreaker and the Cenarion druids are all up to.  Our base in Auchindoun is just too inconvenient for that.$B$BWait a minute, do I know you?',Text0_1_loc9='What\'s it look like I\'m doing?  I\'m fixing the place up - all on my own I might add - so that we can move in!$B$BWith a base of operations out here in the forest, it\'ll be easier to keep track of what Shattrath, Allerian, Stonebreaker and the Cenarion druids are all up to.  Our base in Auchindoun is just too inconvenient for that.$B$BWait a minute, do I know you?',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=9498;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Yes?  Darn it all, now I\'ll have to start over from scratch!',Text0_1_loc9='Yes?  Darn it all, now I\'ll have to start over from scratch!',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=9502;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Practicing!  Soon I\'ll be good enough to join the other summoners and take my turn inside the Shadow Labyrinth at Auchindoun.$B$BI hope that I\'ll get the chance to summon something big!  Maybe something as big as Murmur, though I wouldn\'t lose control of him!',Text0_1_loc9='Practicing!  Soon I\'ll be good enough to join the other summoners and take my turn inside the Shadow Labyrinth at Auchindoun.$B$BI hope that I\'ll get the chance to summon something big!  Maybe something as big as Murmur, though I wouldn\'t lose control of him!',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=9503;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='And what is it exactly that you think I can do for you?  Can\'t you see that I\'m very busy here discussing matters of import with our illustrious leader?$B$BBe quick about your business or I\'ll have you beaten, dog!',Text0_1_loc9='And what is it exactly that you think I can do for you?  Can\'t you see that I\'m very busy here discussing matters of import with our illustrious leader?$B$BBe quick about your business or I\'ll have you beaten, dog!',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=9505;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Well, I was just giving our leader here a progress report on how everything is proceeding according to plan.  It should only be a few more weeks and we\'ll have this place back in shape.$B$BWe may want the Shadow Council to only staff the village with orcs, however.  That way we can make an ancestral claim and work undercover.$B$BWait a minute.  Do I know you?  What\'s your name?',Text0_1_loc9='Well, I was just giving our leader here a progress report on how everything is proceeding according to plan.  It should only be a few more weeks and we\'ll have this place back in shape.$B$BWe may want the Shadow Council to only staff the village with orcs, however.  That way we can make an ancestral claim and work undercover.$B$BWait a minute.  Do I know you?  What\'s your name?',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=9506;
