Text0_0_loc9='Who do you think you are that you can walk in here and address me?  I\'m the leader of the Shadow Council in this village.  Get out of my sight!$B$BIf I see you again, I\'ll be the last person that you ever see.  Understand?$B$BPerhaps you\'d like to be buried in the labyrinth of Auchindoun, or sacrificed to Murmur?'
