Text0_0_loc9='Fleshling, I am Captain Saeed of the Protectorate and these soldiers that stand by me are my avengers. We await orders from the fleshling who destroyed the void conduit. On that fleshling\'s word, we will make our way up to Dimensius\'s lair and wait for the word to make a final strike!$B$BToo long it has been... The void lord will soon face our combined might!'
