Text0_0_loc9='Expedition Point is a tough place to be stationed, but it\'s critical to the defense of Honor Hold.  The information gathered here, and the engagements our soldiers make against the Legion and the orcs of Zeth\'Gor, are invaluable to the Alliance\'s Hellfire campaign.'
Text0_0_loc9='I hear that you\'ve already begun to pull your weight around here.$B$BGood.  I was worried that we were going to have to \'convince\' you to help out.'
Text0_0_loc9='The skin stretched taut between the bones is a call to arms against the main defender of the Alliance\'s Sylvanaar and the Living Grove to the west.'
