Text0_0_loc9='$N, I am pleased to see you. Our dwarven allies require our assistance in Alterac Valley. Will you help them?'
Text0_0_loc9='The Sons of Lothar have been fighting a war without end.  I\'m amazed we\'ve kept our equipment in as good a shape as it is!'
