Text0_0_loc9='It is good to see you again, friend.'
Text0_0_loc9='It feels good to walk about and stretch all four limbs. Is there something I can help you with, $C?'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Greetings, $C.  If I might be so bold, may I remind you that -- while I attune myself to the magics of Hellfire Citadel -- there will undoubtedly be Hellfire wardens biting at my proverbial heels!$B$BSo, do be an upstanding member of your Horde and play the part of the hero... and protect me!',Text0_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text0:',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=10659;
Text0_0_loc9='The search for my people.  Our struggle against the Alliance.  The war with the ogres and their gronn masters.$B$BAll of these things weigh heavy upon my shoulders, $C.$B$BEven I can use some help from time to time.'
Text0_0_loc9='The Deathforge is run by the Shadow Council, under the watchful eye of the Legion.'
Text0_0_loc9='Below is the aptly named Deathforge. If left to their own devices, the Shadow Council would supply the Legion with an endless stream of infernals.'
Text0_0_loc9='We know that the wyrmcultists are massing on the other side of the tunnel.  We\'ll make our stand here.'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Welcome, $N. My expertise is in the art of working with primal mooncloth. Tailors interested in becoming mooncloth specialists often ask me to teach them our ways.',Text0_1_loc9='Welcome, $N. My expertise is in the art of working with primal mooncloth. Tailors interested in becoming mooncloth specialists often ask me to teach them our ways.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=10669;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I\'m afraid there is little I can teach you, $C. You\'re free to browse my wares, of course, but you will not find them of use to you.',Text0_1_loc9='I\'m afraid there is little I can teach you, $C. You\'re free to browse my wares, of course, but you will not find them of use to you.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=10670;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Pleased to meet you! I\'m Gidge, the resident spellfire tailoring expert here in Shattrath. Not that there\'s any competition, but if you\'re interested in learning to be a spellfire tailor and haven\'t settled on a specialization, I can help.',Text0_1_loc9='Pleased to meet you! I\'m Gidge, the resident spellfire tailoring expert here in Shattrath. Not that there\'s any competition, but if you\'re interested in learning to be a spellfire tailor and haven\'t settled on a specialization, I can help.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=10671;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='If you\'re not a tailor, I don\'t think any of my patterns will interest you, but you\'re welcome to browse!',Text0_1_loc9='If you\'re not a tailor, I don\'t think any of my patterns will interest you, but you\'re welcome to browse!',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=10672;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='If you\'re seeking patterns or knowledge about shadoweave tailoring, I\'d be happy to help you.',Text0_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text0:',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=10673;
Text0_0_loc9='I\'m sorry, $C, but my wares are best suited to those who know which end of the needle the thread goes through.$B$BI can assure you, tailoring is about far more than monogramming handkerchiefs.'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='These Tears of the Goddess have been blessed by Elune, and their power will help you combat Archimonde\'s vile magics. Use their power well.',Text0_1_loc9='These Tears of the Goddess have been blessed by Elune, and their power will help you combat Archimonde\'s vile magics. Use their power well.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=10675;
Text0_0_loc9='They fear my words. They make an example out of me. A mockery of the one true god, Neptulon.$B$B<Skar\'this spits.>$B$BRetribution comesss, mortal. The glorious hand of the Tidehunter will one day sweep through the non-believers like a scythe against a new harvest.',Text0_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text0:',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:'
Text0_0_loc9='These wastes are scarred by terrible magic.  We must do what we can to heal this great wound.'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Death\'s Door is a portal that opens upon the world that the Burning Legion uses to breed their fel hounds and other canine-like terrors.  Any time that you see one of those creatures, that is where it came from, and it passes through here, first.$B$BLately, we became aware that the Burning Legion have ramped up their summoning of these creatures through the portal.$B$BYou must shut down Death\'s Door before it becomes an inexorable tide, and all is lost!',Text0_1_loc9='Death\'s Door is a portal that opens upon the world that the Burning Legion uses to breed their fel hounds and other canine-like terrors.  Any time that you see one of those creatures, that is where it came from, and it passes through here, first.$B$BLately, we became aware that the Burning Legion have ramped up their summoning of these creatures through the portal.$B$BYou must shut down Death\'s Door before it becomes an inexorable tide, and all is lost!',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=10679;
Text0_0_loc9='I came to this land to cleanse troubled spirits, but after the attack I fear that my mission has failed.  So many have been taken by the wastes.  Please, you must help them.'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='May the Light guide you, $N.',Text0_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text0:',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=10682;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='It is with solemn pride that I perform my services in Honor Hold.',Text0_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text0:',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=10683;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='When I first set up my rogue academy in Shattrath, it wasn\'t nearly this crowded. Then, the refugees started flooding in and the naaru needed every available building to house them.$B$BI\'ve closed the doors to my academy for now, but it\'s not permanent. I\'ll find a new place to set up.$B$BThen, a new generation of rogues will learn such staples as the gouge\'n grin, combat looting, and blaming someone else for breaking polymorph. And who can forget the central rule of roguery --- real rogues don\'t feint.',Text0_1_loc9='When I first set up my rogue academy in Shattrath, it wasn\'t nearly this crowded. Then, the refugees started flooding in and the naaru needed every available building to house them.$B$BI\'ve closed the doors to my academy for now, but it\'s not permanent. I\'ll find a new place to set up.$B$BThen, a new generation of rogues will learn such staples as the gouge\'n grin, combat looting, and blaming someone else for breaking polymorph. And who can forget the central rule of roguery --- real rogues don\'t feint.',Text1_0_loc9='The trick to using evasion is realizing that the best fifteen seconds of your life are often the last.',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=10686;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc9='Swords, claws, daggers, of course -- I\'ve trained rogues in the use of them all. Now maces, I won\'t touch maces and I won\'t instruct any rogue who gets it in his head to wield one.$B$BThere\'s nothing stealthy about a mace. You\'re in for a noisy kill and a long cleanup if you go that route.',Text2_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text2:',Text3_0_loc9='My early classes are always filled with bright-eyed young lads. Few make it past the first test, though.$B$BI\'ve given up on shouting, \'when I yell vanish, you need to vanish.\' They never listen. Now, the test simply kills the inept.',Text3_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text3:' WHERE entry=10686;
Text4_0_loc9='Never leave home without ample supplies of flash powder, especially when working with others. I guarantee someone will run out every time.$B$BWhen the choice comes down to handing out materials or letting the poor sap die, I help... most of the time.',Text4_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text4:'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I am Zarevhi of the Consortium.  My skills as a transmuter are known in a thousand worlds.',Text0_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text0:',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=10687;
Text0_0_loc9='Oh, no!  My Fei Fei would never take someone else\'s things!  He\'s a good dog... he just needs attention sometimes.  If you give him a treat, then you see!',Text0_1_loc9='Oh, no!  My Fei Fei would never take someone else\'s things!  He\'s a good dog... he just needs attention sometimes.  If you give him a treat, then you see!'
Text0_0_loc9='I used to amuse myself by accepting challenges from anyone who would offer them, but I\'ve long since grown tired of such easy victories.$B$BFor now, I\'m taking some time to get my reagent business off the ground and write a book about my experiences in Twilight\'s Hammer.',Text0_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text0:',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Our resident alchemist Lorokeem brought his equipment with him, in fact. It may be slightly different from what you\'re used to - he is an arakkoa, after all - but it should serve your needs. He roosts in the northwest portion of the lower city.',Text0_1_loc9='Our resident alchemist Lorokeem brought his equipment with him, in fact. It may be slightly different from what you\'re used to - he is an arakkoa, after all - but it should serve your needs. He roosts in the northwest portion of the lower city.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=10696;
