Text0_0_loc9='Gahk new at Ogri\'la like little $R.  It like heaven da other ogres below always talk about.  But, Gahk\'s heads hurt from crystal making Gahk smarter.$B$B<Both of Gahk\'s heads nod to each other.>$B$BUs learning ta make da crystalforged darkrune.  When us learn dat, we smash da demon\'s warp-gate!'
