Text0_0_loc9='$N smash warp-gate good, but da demons make it strong again.$B$B$N bring Gahk another darkrune and Gahk make special crystalforged darkrune for $N!'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Welcome to Ogri\'la, $C.$B$BThe ogres here have managed to gain a great mental acuity through the magical emanations of the surrounding crystals.  Though we do not fully understand how they work, we have come to appreciate our new home and only want to live in peace.$B$BUnfortunate then that the demons and ethereals, and especially the Black Dragonflight, will not leave us to that peace.',Text0_1_loc9='Welcome to Ogri\'la, $C.$B$BThe ogres here have managed to gain a great mental acuity through the magical emanations of the surrounding crystals.  Though we do not fully understand how they work, we have come to appreciate our new home and only want to live in peace.$B$BUnfortunate then that the demons and ethereals, and especially the Black Dragonflight, will not leave us to that peace.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=10926;
