Text0_0_loc9='The egg appears resilient as an egg of the Black Dragonflight rightfully should.  Perhaps if you were to place a great many apexis shards next to it, their vibrations would cause it to crack open?$B$BToo bad that you don\'t appear to have the thirty-five apexis shards necessary to do the job.'
