Text0_0_loc9='You\'ll find plenty to do here, $N.'
Text0_0_loc9='Ack, ye\'ve been busy now haven\'t ye?!  I canna thank ye enough for bombing them demons and resupplying us with mounts.$B$BYer making our job all the more easier.  Keep up the good work, $G laddy : lassie;!'
