UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I spend all day retrieving parts for the zeppelin and Frezza doesn\'t even have the decency to pay me an hourly wage. But you\'re not here about that, are you? I bet you want to know where the zeppelin is located. Well, you\'re in luck - I have my zeppelin tracking device right here!',Text0_1_loc9='I spend all day retrieving parts for the zeppelin and Frezza doesn\'t even have the decency to pay me an hourly wage. But you\'re not here about that, are you? I bet you want to know where the zeppelin is located. Well, you\'re in luck - I have my zeppelin tracking device right here!',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=11189;
Text0_0_loc9='The merchant known as Griftah has been exiled from this city for his fraudulent activities. We plan to go over these little knick-knacks he sells extremely carefully. Please, leave his stall undisturbed and let us do our work.'
Text0_0_loc9='You won\'t find a better brew in Azeroth.'
Text0_0_loc9='We Thunderbrews take pride knowing that we are the best brewhouse in all the realms.'
Text0_0_loc9='Whoah! You really want buy from us?'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Can\'t you see that I\'ve got places to go and people to see! Step aside, peasant!',Text0_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text0:',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=11215;
Text0_0_loc9='I can only assume that you know who I am. And yet you insist on disturbing me?$B$BWhat could you possibly want that requires my attention?'
Text0_0_loc9='Oh come now, don\'t be ridiculous! I\'m the one and only Budd Nedreck!$B$BI\'ve been all over this land, from the top of Mount Hyjal to the depths of the Sunken Temple. In fact, I was the first to call it the Sunken Temple!$B$BYes, that was me. Don\'t give it a second thought.
'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I highly recommend that you visit Sayge to get your fortune told. I know, I know... he\'s a gnoll.  But he\'s a very special gnoll with the power to divine your future!$B$BAnd we are constantly expanding the faire with all manner of new attractions!',Text0_1_loc9='I highly recommend that you visit Sayge to get your fortune told. I know, I know... he\'s a gnoll.  But he\'s a very special gnoll with the power to divine your future!$B$BAnd we are constantly expanding the faire with all manner of new attractions!',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=11220;
Text0_0_loc9='Yes, well, listen here, $C. I\'m older than I look and wise beyond my years. You\'d do well not to question me so much.$B$BLook, you don\'t need to take my word for it. Read the postings on any local bulletin board for yourself. I\'m everywhere!$B$BJust do yourself a favor and ignore the ones with \'WANTED\' in the title. Simple misunderstandings, I assure you.'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Well met, $C. I\'m learning the art of gryphon handling from Baldruc over there. One day, I hope to run my own stable of gryphons.',Text0_1_loc9='Well met, $C. I\'m learning the art of gryphon handling from Baldruc over there. One day, I hope to run my own stable of gryphons.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=11224;
