UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Oh, me a cook?  I suppose that\'s true.  A barmaid\'s got to work in the kitchens from time to time, and I\'ve learned a few recipes over the years.  Nothing too special, but they\'re hearty enough to fill Grok\'s substantial belly.',Text0_1_loc9='Oh, me a cook?  I suppose that\'s true.  A barmaid\'s got to work in the kitchens from time to time, and I\'ve learned a few recipes over the years.  Nothing too special, but they\'re hearty enough to fill Grok\'s substantial belly.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=11231;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I\'m sorry $N, but you\'ve already learned all I know about cooking.  Of course, you never know when our cooks will whip up something new, so don\'t be shy and be sure to visit again some time.',Text0_1_loc9='I\'m sorry $N, but you\'ve already learned all I know about cooking.  Of course, you never know when our cooks will whip up something new, so don\'t be shy and be sure to visit again some time.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=11233;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='My brother Krixx thinks he has it bad working in Orgrimmar. Nothing compares to the stench of this place. At least the boss had the decency to give me hazard pay!$B$BWhat? Do you want to see where the zeppelin is? Good thing I\'ve got my zeppelin tracker right here!',Text0_1_loc9='My brother Krixx thinks he has it bad working in Orgrimmar. Nothing compares to the stench of this place. At least the boss had the decency to give me hazard pay!$B$BWhat? Do you want to see where the zeppelin is? Good thing I\'ve got my zeppelin tracker right here!',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=11234;
Text0_0_loc9='Be on your guard. We are Theramore\'s first line of defense against its many enemies in the marsh.'
Text0_0_loc9='Now that the deserters have taken over Lost Point, North Point Tower is the most distant of Theramore\'s outposts.'
Text0_0_loc9='What can a guy like me be doin\' for a $R like you at a time like this?$B',Text1_0_loc9='Sumthin\' I can do fer ya, $C?$B'
Text2_0_loc9='If yer here to partake in the big spoils, ya best be gettin\' in line!$B$BMy share be long overdue....$B'
Text0_0_loc9='Beats me, kid. I\'m new to the crew.$B$BI\'ve had my fill of troll-killin\' and grog drinkin, I can tell ya that. Only thing left to see is the treasure Budd keeps promisin\'....$B'
Text0_0_loc9='Budd\'s crew, ye mean? Aye, he be no respecter of persons. He\'ll take on anyone who can work a shovel.$B$B\'cept them undead. Budd hates \'em. Scared of \'em, likely as not.$B',Text1_0_loc9='Aye, ya never know who\'s gunna join next, or who be dyin\' next for that matter.$B$BMy advice? Don\'t be gettin\' too attached to anyone.'
Text2_0_loc9='Agreed. Budd\'s scraped together rif-raf from all over creation.$B$BSeems when there\'s free booze to be had, there be plenty of folk willin\' to set aside their differences.'
Text0_0_loc9='<sniff\'s himself, and winces>$B$BThat there be the smell of adventure, $C!',Text1_0_loc9='<hic>Lissen here, $R. Spend a day or two wrestlin\' with wild trolls and then tell me how you smell!'
Text2_0_loc9='Ohh, that. See, there\'s been nuthin\' but orc grog around camp lately.$B$BOrc grog doesn\'t seem to agree with me, if ya know what I mean....'
Text0_0_loc9='Welcome to Sentry Point, $C.'
Text0_0_loc9='Listen, mon!$B$BI tell ya all I be knowin\', but first ya gotta be savin\' me from these savages and their killer bears.$B$BDeal?'
Text0_0_loc9='Hooray! Tanzar be free, mon!$B$BWhat luck! All that an\' not even a chipped tusk.$B$BCharmed, mon. That\'s what I be. No sense denyin\' it.'
Text0_0_loc9='I\'ve never experienced cold like this, $R. Even in the absence of ice and snow, the frozen wastes of Northrend are extremely taxing.',Text0_1_loc9='I\'ve never experienced cold like this, $R. Even in the absence of ice and snow, the frozen wastes of Northrend are extremely taxing.'
Text0_0_loc9='Say, you look familiar. Have we met?',Text1_0_loc9='Do I know you?'
Text2_0_loc9='Lemme give you some advice: Never trust a gnome.'
Text0_0_loc9='Ok mon, a deal be a deal....$B$BIt was night when we all snuck in to Zul\'Aman fer a look around.$B$BAll was quiet, til we be hearin\' a rustlin\' sound, like the wind through the trees. Before we know it, we be surrounded by these savages and their pets! Next day, I be wakin\' up here, stuck in a cage.$B$BDay an\' night, one by one, prisoners be gettin\' killed. Every time one be dyin\', that bear-troll be lookin\' stronger.$B$BThat be all I know \'bout this place, mon. And I don\'t wanna be knowin\' any more!'
Text0_0_loc9='That man be nuthin\' but a fool!$B$BFame, fortune? Phooey! This place be nuthin\' but a deathtrap, mon!$B$BI seen all kinds a\' trolls in my day, but these, they be different - sneaky, strong, tricky.$B$BSeemed to me like they knew we was comin\'....'
Text0_0_loc9='<Budd rolls his eyes as he sees you draw near>$B$BAhh, yes, the soon-to-be-famous $N!$B$BTo what do I owe the pleasure of your company?'
Text0_0_loc9='Now, now, $N, just relax and take a deep breath. You really need to learn to trust me.$B$BYour lack of experience in these situations is causing you to panic, and panic always exaggerates the truth. So you see, there really is no crisis.$B$BNow that we\'ve settled that, I must ask that you stop being so negative. It\'s not good for the crew\'s morale....'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='' WHERE entry=11304;
Text0_0_loc9='If you need to speak with Apprentice Garion, you\'ll find him inside the cottage with Tabetha. At least there, he can\'t steal all the reagents.'
Text0_0_loc9='I wish we had a priest or a druid out here. I can\'t continue my studies until I\'ve recovered from my injuries.'
Text0_0_loc9='Wait, don\'t tell me... $N, right?$B$BWhat can I do for you?$B'
Text0_0_loc9='Oh, well, that all depends on which partners you mean. Many have come and gone over the years - always someone eager to ride the coat-tails of the legend that is Budd Nedreck!$B$BYou can rest assured that most of them have become wealthy and retired. That\'s simply not the path I\'ve chosen. You see, I\'ve always felt that I\'ve been called to reveal the world\'s great mysteries. Alas, if I don\'t do it, who could?$B'
Text0_0_loc9='Listen, $N, you should know by now that when fortune comes knocking, you open the door and ask questions later. Chances like this don\'t come along every day!$B$BNow, are you in or not, $C?$B$B<Budd doesn\'t wait for a reply>$B$BOf course you are! Now, there\'s work to be done, and so far I\'ve seen a lot of talking and no action. I suggest you show me something before I find a replacement.$B$BThere are thousands who would kill for an opportunity like this, I assure you!'
Text0_0_loc9='Ahh, them - a sad tale, that one.$B$BThey have disappeared behind the walls of Zul\'Aman. I haven\'t heard from them in days.$B$BI\'ve seen it a hundred times; that overeager itch for fame and fortune. I tried to hold them back, told them they weren\'t prepared, but in the end they chose to face their peril....'
Text0_0_loc9='Hi there! We\'re being blockaded by those good-for-nothing pirates out in the bay! Do you think you can help us out by dropping a few bombs on them?!$B$BOur stolen zeppelin\'s here; hop on board before she sets sail!'
Text0_0_loc9='Hi there! We\'re being blockaded by those good-for-nothing pirates out in the bay! Do you think you can help us out by dropping a few bombs on them?!$B$BOur stolen zeppelin\'s less than $3078w minutes away.  Make sure you\'re onboard when she leaves!'
Text0_0_loc9='Hi there! We\'re being blockaded by those good-for-nothing pirates out in the bay! Do you think you can help us out by dropping a few bombs on them?!$B$BOur stolen zeppelin\'s almost here... I think I hear her now.  Make sure you\'re onboard when she leaves!'
Text0_0_loc9='I\'m a prisoner!$B$BThey shot me and my beautiful zeppelin out of the sky. And what for? Because I was ferrying men and materiel for the Horde? That\'s nothing new!$B$BNow they have me running her in circles around the bay so that they can bomb the pirates. I just don\'t have the parts to keep her going like this! I\'m barely keeping her together on spit and bailing wire!$B$BI won\'t be held responsible for what happens to you, but you might as well get on board before she leaves.$B$BIt\'s a crime I tell you!'
Text0_0_loc9='I\'m a prisoner!$B$BThey shot me and my beautiful zeppelin out of the sky. And what for? Because I was ferrying men and materiel for the Horde? That\'s nothing new!$B$BNow they have me running her in circles around the bay so that they can bomb the pirates. I just don\'t have the parts to keep her going like this! I\'m barely keeping her together on spit and bailing wire!$B$BIf you\'re determined to help them out, she\'s due to arrive back in port in less than a minute.$B$BIt\'s a crime I tell you!'
Text0_0_loc9='Patience, $N. I didn\'t become the renowned Budd Nedreck by being hasty.$B$BFinal preparations are being made and soon the treasures and secrets of Zul\'Aman shall be mine! $B$B<Budd pauses and looks at you for a moment, then chuckles.>$B$B...ours I mean, of course.'
Text0_0_loc9='Day and night all I do is sit here and make ammo and restring crossbows.$B$BI suppose you want me to do something for you too?'
