Text0_0_loc9='I advise the captain on matters that he chooses to share with me, but I have a feeling that he\'d rather hear from you.'
Text0_0_loc9='All of these mouths to feed, and who has to do it? Me!$B$BAll the cooking, and the cleaning, and everything else!',Text0_1_loc9='All of these mouths to feed, and who has to do it? Me!$B$BAll the cooking, and the cleaning, and everything else!'
Text0_0_loc9='In all of my days I never thought to see such a magnificent new frontier.$B$BIf only it weren\'t tainted by evil and knowledge which is best left hidden.'
Text0_0_loc9='You have reached the limits of my knowledge, but there is more yet to learn. Across the sea, in the Mage Quarter of Stormwind City, a great tailor dwells. His name is Georgio Bolero, and he will train you now, I think. Go and speak with him.'
Text0_0_loc9='The ground... is frozen.  We\'re sitting ducks here; these meatwagons aren\'t going anywhere.'
Text0_0_loc9='What does it look like?  The ground is frozen like a rock!$B$BThe wheels on these meatwagons were built to go over mud at best.  We\'re going to need an abomination and some chains to salvage them.'
Text0_0_loc9='I will never call Brackenwall Village my home. To do so is to give up hope of reclaiming our rightful lands.'
Text0_0_loc9='Well then, I spose I be owin\' ya my thanks, $R.$B$BTruth is, I thought I\'d swallowed me last tankard \'til ye showed up.'
Text0_0_loc9='A sad tale, that one - a wee bit embarrassin\' too.$B$BMy people be know fer havin\' a taste fer the ale, ya know. And I be no exception. Seems I been given more than me share of the thirst.$B$BSo I run inta ol\' Budd ya see, an\' he offers me all the grog I can swallow fer joinin\' his crew - a move I\'ve come to regret.$B$BOne night, after drinkin\' enough grog to drop a Kodo, I was lured into followin\' Budd\'s band o\' misfits into Zul\'Aman.$B$BThat be the last I recall before findin\' meself in that cage.'
Text0_0_loc9='Ohh, thank you soo much for getting me out of that cage because I was in there for soo long and it smelled like minced mutton that had been sitting out in the sun for a week and I don\'t like mutton to begin with because when I was little, well littler, I was actually turned into a sheep for a minute and so I know what it feels like to be a sheep and I don\'t want someone eating me, especially an overgrown troll dressed up like a kitty....$B$B<Ashli takes a deep breath.>$B$BHow\'s my hair?$B',Text0_1_loc9='Ohh, thank you soo much for getting me out of that cage because I was in there for soo long and it smelled like minced mutton that had been sitting out in the sun for a week and I don\'t like mutton to begin with because when I was little, well littler, I was actually turned into a sheep for a minute and so I know what it feels like to be a sheep and I don\'t want someone eating me, especially an overgrown troll dressed up like a kitty....$B$B<Ashli takes a deep breath.>$B$BHow\'s my hair?$B'
Text0_0_loc9='The stranded Alliance sailors know they\'re going to die, yet they fight us tooth and nail.$B$BImpressive and pathetic at the same time.',Text0_1_loc9='The stranded Alliance sailors know they\'re going to die, yet they fight us tooth and nail.$B$BImpressive and pathetic at the same time.',Text1_0_loc9='It will be a matter of hours before the Alliance in the Derelict Strand are crushed.  They are surrounded and outnumbered.'
Text2_0_loc9='By the will of Sylvanas, our enemies will fall.'
Text0_0_loc9='It is those two cannons along the wall that are slowing us down.  Without their protection our forces would be able to rush their fortification without taking any losses.$B$BIt\'s either take out those cannons or wait until they run out of ammunition.  Anselm\'s choice, I suppose.',Text0_1_loc9='It is those two cannons along the wall that are slowing us down.  Without their protection our forces would be able to rush their fortification without taking any losses.$B$BIt\'s either take out those cannons or wait until they run out of ammunition.  Anselm\'s choice, I suppose.'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The Headless Horseman, once a knight of the Silver Hand and a hero among his fellow paladins, is cursed.  Driven insane within the Scarlet Monastery, he believes that he is alive and we are dead.$B$BNow, his fervor no longer serves the Light.  With the coming of Hallow\'s End, he spreads gloom and fire across the villages of Azeroth.',Text0_1_loc9='The Headless Horseman, once a knight of the Silver Hand and a hero among his fellow paladins, is cursed.  Driven insane within the Scarlet Monastery, he believes that he is alive and we are dead.$B$BNow, his fervor no longer serves the Light.  With the coming of Hallow\'s End, he spreads gloom and fire across the villages of Azeroth.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=11590;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='' WHERE entry=11596;
Text0_0_loc9='Freedom! Kraz life was over.$B$BI thank you, $C.'
Text0_0_loc9='Kraz should never have come to this cursed place... should have known not to trust the human. A blind fool I was, $C, as are you if you follow his counsel.$B$BMy son, lost for two moons, was last seen with the human, Budd. He told me I could find him behind the walls of Zul\'Aman....$B$BI followed his people here, and was captured with the rest. Without your help, I was doomed to die.$B$BThank you, stranger.'
Text0_0_loc9='Come in out of the cold and rest your weary bones a while. Our hospitality is yours.',Text0_1_loc9='Come in out of the cold and rest your weary bones a while. Our hospitality is yours.'
Text0_0_loc9='Walk in the Light, my child.'
Text0_0_loc9='$G Sir : Ma\'am;! I\'m here to assist and defend you.$B$BYour orders?'
Text0_0_loc9='For ages, I was lost.  Now, finally, I see how dark my soul had become...'
Text0_0_loc9='The pumpkin head smolders forebodingly...'
Text0_0_loc9='Make haste, $C!$B$BThis crisis is nowhere near being under control.',Text0_1_loc9='Make haste, $C!$B$BThis crisis is nowhere near being under control.'
Text0_0_loc9='You seek passage somewhere, $N?  My bats will get you there in no time.'
Text0_0_loc9='Tread carefully, $R.$B$BThese corpses here are all that remain of my best men.'
Text0_0_loc9='These Alliance pondsuckers sure are gutsy!  Boarding fully-manned Forsaken destroyers... now that\'s suicidal behavior if I ever heard of it.',Text0_1_loc9='These Alliance pondsuckers sure are gutsy!  Boarding fully-manned Forsaken destroyers... now that\'s suicidal behavior if I ever heard of it.'
Text0_0_loc9='My sisters and I welcome you, $R.',Text0_1_loc9='My sisters and I welcome you, $R.'
Text0_0_loc9='Stay sharp, $N.$B$BWe\'re not out of the woods yet....'
Text0_0_loc9='I am here to assist and defend you.$B$BHow next shall we strike at the enemy?'
Text0_0_loc9='Come closer, young one; my ears aren\'t what they once were, and I care not for raising my voice.',Text0_1_loc9='Come closer, young one; my ears aren\'t what they once were, and I care not for raising my voice.'
