Text0_0_loc9='So many uses for the plague, so little time!'
Text0_0_loc9='Aren\'t you a sight for sore eyes!$B$BThere\'s work to be done and not much time.',Text0_1_loc9='Aren\'t you a sight for sore eyes!$B$BThere\'s work to be done and not much time.'
Text0_0_loc9='Gorth not afraid of getting killed.  Them Forsaken just put me back together again.',Text1_0_loc9='Gorth is confused sometimes.  Gorth is good at killing people so Gorth is made sergeant.  But now Gorth never gets to kill nothing!'
Text2_0_loc9='Vrykuls is bigger and stronger than us.  But we is better looking!'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The Blastenheimer 5000 Ultra Cannon is a state-of-the-art single person projectile device. Delivering its payload at near the speed of a dragon, the cannon is the pride and joy of the Blastenheimer family, world renown for their aeronautical and combustible feats!$B$BIf you\'d like to be launched through the skies to fly free as a bird, seek out Maxima Blastenheimer in the Terrace of Light in Shattrath City. She\'ll aim you at a target in a small pond outside the city walls!',Text0_1_loc9='The Blastenheimer 5000 Ultra Cannon is a state-of-the-art single person projectile device. Delivering its payload at near the speed of a dragon, the cannon is the pride and joy of the Blastenheimer family, world renown for their aeronautical and combustible feats!$B$BIf you\'d like to be launched through the skies to fly free as a bird, seek out Maxima Blastenheimer in the Terrace of Light in Shattrath City. She\'ll aim you at a target in a small pond outside the city walls!',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=11743;
Text0_0_loc9='Keep your voice down, $C. We wouldn\'t want them to hear us.'
Text0_0_loc9='I\'ve been in the military my whole life.  I\'ve fought in many wars, under many banners - but they\'ve always been other people\'s battles.$B$BNot this time.  Every Forsaken soldier you see here has come for one reason alone.  Arthas must be killed.'
Text0_0_loc9='Hungry? Can sleep here, too.'
Text0_0_loc9='Keep your wits about you, $R, we\'re surrounded by the walking dead here.'
Text0_0_loc9='We plaguebringers tend to be slightly more practical than the average apothecary.  After all, we deal with the logistics of deploying the plague.$B$BThat doesn\'t mean our theoretical background isn\'t rock solid.  We just prefer... hands on tasks.'
Text0_0_loc9='Ya be havin\' me gratitude, $C.$B$BIf there be anythin\' I can be doin\' fer yeh, just say so.'
Text0_0_loc9='It was kind of the Explorers\' League to allow me to tag along. However, with the dangers in the Rivenwood and surrounding area, it looks like it may have been foolish of me to come without help.',Text0_1_loc9='It was kind of the Explorers\' League to allow me to tag along. However, with the dangers in the Rivenwood and surrounding area, it looks like it may have been foolish of me to come without help.'
Text0_0_loc9='I\'m going to miss Camp Winterhoof, but I understand why Chieftain Ashtotem made his decision. Home is a comfort we cannot always afford.',Text0_1_loc9='I\'m going to miss Camp Winterhoof, but I understand why Chieftain Ashtotem made his decision. Home is a comfort we cannot always afford.'
Text0_0_loc9='Hey, can\'t you shee I\'m trying to drink here?',Text0_1_loc9='Hey, can\'t you shee I\'m trying to drink here?'
Text0_0_loc9='Bones... flesh... muscles... tendons... cartilage... it all comes together here under my hacksaw.',Text0_1_loc9='Bones... flesh... muscles... tendons... cartilage... it all comes together here under my hacksaw.'
Text0_0_loc9='Here you go, $G lad : lass;. Make \'em count!'
Text0_0_loc9='Of course. I found it on the corpse of a dwarf nearby.'
Text0_0_loc9='Of course.'
Text0_0_loc9='Let me guess, another group of Budd\'s riff-raff?$B$BAway with you, $R, before you get hurt - or worse.'
Text0_0_loc9='Hey there!  Just because I can race rams better than anyone else, doesn\'t mean I won\'t pitch in and help out the brewers.  You can help out if you like.$B$BBut wait, there\'s more!$B$BHelping out with Brewfest means you get a chance to ride some of the fastest rams in the realms!'
Text0_0_loc9='Ahaha, ya see this? Griftah\'s BACK! Back in my stall, back with my old wares, and ready to pass on the deals to ya!$B$BWant to be better, stronger, faster? Each one of these amulets be guaranteed to do just what I say they be doin\'. Step up and buy one of these miraculous baubles! Cheap at twice the price!'
