Text0_0_loc9='All this free candy is just bad business, I tell you. Or... maybe it\'s just a loss leader... they get you in the inn, and then gouge you on the meat. It\'s brilliant!',Text0_1_loc9='All this free candy is just bad business, I tell you. Or... maybe it\'s just a loss leader... they get you in the inn, and then gouge you on the meat. It\'s brilliant!'
Text0_0_loc9='When Hallow\'s End is over we\'ll smash all these pumpkins. That\'ll be the greatest day I\'ve ever known!',Text0_1_loc9='When Hallow\'s End is over we\'ll smash all these pumpkins. That\'ll be the greatest day I\'ve ever known!'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='To celebrate the birth of yet another deadly enemy is an odd thing, to say the least. Still, we will join our allies in their festivities.',Text0_1_loc9='To celebrate the birth of yet another deadly enemy is an odd thing, to say the least. Still, we will join our allies in their festivities.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=11962;
