UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='No other holiday matches the feasting and drinking of Brewfest!',Text0_1_loc9='No other holiday matches the feasting and drinking of Brewfest!',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=12134;
Text0_0_loc9='A word to the wise, stranger, go back to wherever you\'re from.$B$BThis is no place for lighthearted adventurers. It\'ll chew up the likes of you and spit out your bones.'
Text0_0_loc9='This large jack-o\'-lantern rests in the middle of the village.'
Text0_0_loc9='The pumpkin has been smashed, and offers no more treasure.'
Text0_0_loc9='Smashing the pumpkin reveals a hidden treasure!  This is the greatest day you\'ve ever known!'
Text0_0_loc9='Welcome, friend, to the Brewfest Grounds! There\'s much to enjoy here while we celebrate the spirit of friendly competition between rival breweries. If you have any questions, let me know!'
Text0_0_loc9='Brewfest is all about enjoying the very best food and drink in the lands, and that\'s no exaggeration! Just take a gander at the many invigorating hand-crafted beers and holiday sausages, pretzels, and cheeses available. You\'ll find nothing better, and for so little coin!'
Text0_0_loc9='Next to the beer and sausage, the most popular part of Brewfest is the souvenirs! From traditional holiday garb to mini-kegs of tasty brew, all sorts of Brewfest-themed items are available from Belbi Quikswitch. Just be sure to have plenty of Brewfest Prize Tokens on hand, as it\'s the only way to buy them! You can earn prize tokens by helping out around the Brewfest Grounds.'
Text0_0_loc9='Ram racing is one of the great traditions of Brewfest. Speak to Pol Amberstill down by the ram stable if you want to learn more. It\'s a right hoot AND can be a great way to earn Brewfest Prize Tokens!'
Text0_0_loc9='Hey there, welcome to Brewfest! There\'s a mess of ways to keep yourself entertained in there, so you got any questions, you let me know. Otherwise, go buy some beer and a pretzel!'
Text0_0_loc9='Brewfest is all about the beer and the eats, and it don\'t get any better than what we\'re serving up. Think I\'m lying? Just check out all the tasty brews, sausages, pretzels, and cheeses we got. You\'ll see: Best chow around, and it don\'t get any cheaper!'
Text0_0_loc9='Everyone loves those crazy Brewfest racing rams. Want to know more? Talk to Driz Tumblequick down by the ram stable. Have a blast and earn some Brewfest Prize Tokens while you\'re at it!'
Text0_0_loc9='Hey hey, don\'t forget to grab yourself some Brewfest souvenirs! We got everything from traditional holiday garb to mini-kegs of tasty brew. Just talk to Blix Fixwidget, but make sure you got plenty of Brewfest Prize Tokens on hand... it\'s the only way to buy them! You can earn prize tokens by helping out around the Brewfest Grounds.'
