Text0_0_loc9='Twice a day, at six fifteen in the morning and six fifteen in the evening, Shadow Hunter Vol\'jin himself comes out to the Brewfest grounds for the Tapping of the Keg ceremony. You\'d be a fool to miss it!'
Text0_0_loc9='This barrel of ale is guarded by Jarven Thunderbrew.  As long as he\'s in the basement, no barrels may be disturbed.'
