Text2_0_loc9='The Lady Mehley is the best ship EVER!',Text3_0_loc9='Swabbin\' decks cured my rickets!'
Text0_0_loc9='Times are changing, $N.  War has arrived.$B$BWill our people rise to the occasion and aid our allies... or will we linger in the sidelines?'
Text0_0_loc9='I\'ve little time for talk, sorry.'
