Text0_0_loc9='Not right now, $Gpal:sugar;... I got things to do. See ya around.'
Text0_0_loc9='I run the tightest airship in Azeroth. She used to be fitted with twin light cannons and enough bombs to flatten a city, you know... her mere shadow was enough rout armies.$B$BWhat? Of course it\'s true!'
Text0_0_loc9='We\'ve almost consolidated our control over Sun\'s Reach.  If we manage to keep the harbor from getting any reinforcements we will certainly succeed.$B$BWe are $3238w percent done with our goal.'
Text0_0_loc9='We\'ve done it, $N.  With Sun\'s Reach under our control we are but mere moments away from absolute victory.'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I\'m gathering funds to build a monument in honor of those who\'ve died in the war.  It is important to not forget the sacrifices we\'ve made to achieve victory.$B$BWe are $3275w percent done with this goal.',Text0_1_loc9='I\'m gathering funds to build a monument in honor of those who\'ve died in the war.  It is important to not forget the sacrifices we\'ve made to achieve victory.$B$BWe are $3275w percent done with this goal.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=12322;
