Text0_0_loc9='Relaxation is the key to being an efficient crew.  Let the crew relax, and they\'ll perform better.'
Text0_0_loc9='Please allow me a few seconds of rest.'
Text0_0_loc9='Let me sleep just five more minutes, mon...'
