Text0_0_loc9='No time to talk -- I have work to do!',Text1_0_loc9='You can understand me? I can understand you!'
Text2_0_loc9='$R, why would I want to talk to you? Your people probably caused this mess in the first place!',Text3_0_loc9='There are clams to be collected and orcas to be killed. Help or stay out of the way!'
Text4_0_loc9='Blurglgr murbrgl... just kidding, I can understand you.',Text5_0_loc9='You figure out yet why our brothers and sisters over in the village have gone insane?'
Text6_0_loc9='I knew that we never should have gone into those caves. It\'s not natural!',Text7_0_loc9='There\'s something fishy about new King Mrgl-Mrgl, but I can\'t quite put my finger on it.'
Text0_0_loc9='Kael\'thas and his felbloods be damned! All we\'ve worked for is gone, but they\'re fools to think we won\'t fight back. Already, Lady Liadrin seeks a new source of power for our order. We will not be destroyed so easily.'
