Text0_0_loc9='You\'ve reached an Alliance bonfire! Desecrate this bonfire and stamp it out!'
Text0_0_loc9='We need to get this outpost ready for the push into Sholazar Basin.$B$BDon\'t just stand there, $C. Go out and represent the Horde with honor and spilled blood!'
Text0_0_loc9='I have to clean up this mess, but I\'ll do it without complaint.$B$BYou\'ll help if you have any Horde pride at all!',Text0_1_loc9='I have to clean up this mess, but I\'ll do it without complaint.$B$BYou\'ll help if you have any Horde pride at all!'
Text0_0_loc9='The spirits speak all around us. Are you listening, $R?',Text0_1_loc9='The spirits speak all around us. Are you listening, $R?'
