Text0_0_loc9='While Nesingwary\'s advances upon the wildlife of Northrend has been halted, it is only a matter of time before he attempts another incursion. You must remain vigilant, $N!$B$BAbove all else, do not give in to whatever temptations may be set before you... The demon will attempt to charm you. When it happens, you must resist!'
Text0_0_loc9='I\'ll be damned if these blasted Scourge are going to drive us away!  Us settlers gave everything up to start new lives in Northrend.$B$BYou\'d better believe we\'re going to fight tooth and nail.',Text0_1_loc9='I\'ll be damned if these blasted Scourge are going to drive us away!  Us settlers gave everything up to start new lives in Northrend.$B$BYou\'d better believe we\'re going to fight tooth and nail.'
