Text0_0_loc9='Oh....$B$BWhere am I?',Text0_1_loc9='Oh....$B$BWhere am I?'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Welcome, $C. Have you come to honor this flame?$B$BRemember: Our festival fires burn in every land with a Horde settlement. Make time to honor each of them, if you can.$B$BThe Alliance, too, burns fires of their own. You would do well to desecrate such unworthy efforts when you see them.',Text0_1_loc9='Welcome, $C. Have you come to honor this flame?$B$BRemember: Our festival fires burn in every land with a Horde settlement. Make time to honor each of them, if you can.$B$BThe Alliance, too, burns fires of their own. You would do well to desecrate such unworthy efforts when you see them.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=12582;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Then I am glad you came. Now that you know of our fires, and of honoring them... and of the fires of our enemies, and of extinguishing them... you may return to him and be rewarded.',Text0_1_loc9='Then I am glad you came. Now that you know of our fires, and of honoring them... and of the fires of our enemies, and of extinguishing them... you may return to him and be rewarded.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=12587;
Text0_0_loc9='In a word, magic.$B$BIrresponsible mortals with their brief lifespans think nothing of the lasting effects of their actions.$B$BArcane energies have been tapped too liberally, disrupting the world\'s balance. If this is allowed to continue, Azeroth will soon be annihilated.$B$BOn this, both sides agree. But before a council could even be appointed, Malygos put his own plan into action.$B$BWe had no choice but to confront him.'
Text0_0_loc9='We\'re making progress, $R, but far too slowly.'
Text0_0_loc9='We must succceed! Azeroth\'s fate lies in the balance....'
Text0_0_loc9='Malygos the Spellweaver, the Lord of Magic, Master of the Blue Dragonflight. He is the blue dragon aspect, one of the most ancient creatures on Azeroth.$B$BHe is said to be recovering from a madness which has lasted for millennia, but his recent actions lead me to believe that he is still far from sane.$B$BHis solution to our dilemma is to search out and destroy every magic-wielding mortal on Azeroth.$B$BAs the guardians of life, this has forced the red dragonflight to take action.$B$BDragon now fights against dragon, and the fate of our frail world lies in the balance.'
Text0_0_loc9='I\'m glad you are here, $C. The military situation in the Sunwell Plateau is rather grim.',Text0_1_loc9='I\'m glad you are here, $C. The military situation in the Sunwell Plateau is rather grim.'
Text0_0_loc9='Captain Selana has instructed me to assist you with your efforts here on the Sunwell Plateau.'
Text0_0_loc9='The Shattered Sun Offensive has made great progress in the outer areas of the Isle of Quel\'Danas. Kil\'jaeden\'s forces are being pushed back, and in the chaos I was able to lead a small scouting force here inside the Sunwell Plateau. My troops proceeded through Parhelion Plaza, spotted a group of Sunblade blood elves, and we then engaged the enemy. That fight quickly turned into a disaster.',Text0_1_loc9='The Shattered Sun Offensive has made great progress in the outer areas of the Isle of Quel\'Danas. Kil\'jaeden\'s forces are being pushed back, and in the chaos I was able to lead a small scouting force here inside the Sunwell Plateau. My troops proceeded through Parhelion Plaza, spotted a group of Sunblade blood elves, and we then engaged the enemy. That fight quickly turned into a disaster.'
Text0_0_loc9='Kil\'jaeden\'s defenders here on the Sunwell Plateau are much stronger than anything we faced outside on the Island. The Legion have even twisted our Arcane Guardian technology with fel energy to create something much more sinister. Just one of those Sunblade Protectors decimated my troops, and I ordered a swift retreat. I expected my squad to be pushed completely off the plateau, but the enemy surprised me by calling off the pursuit.',Text0_1_loc9='Kil\'jaeden\'s defenders here on the Sunwell Plateau are much stronger than anything we faced outside on the Island. The Legion have even twisted our Arcane Guardian technology with fel energy to create something much more sinister. Just one of those Sunblade Protectors decimated my troops, and I ordered a swift retreat. I expected my squad to be pushed completely off the plateau, but the enemy surprised me by calling off the pursuit.'
Text0_0_loc9='A friend and I have come to rescue a young human woman from the clutches of the Legionlord, Kil\'jaeden and his vile minions.$B$BWe\'ve discovered that Kael\'thas is trying to summon Kil\'jaeden from the depths of the Sunwell itself.$B$BFor the sake of this world - this cannot come to pass! I am committed to seeing that it does not.$B'
Text0_0_loc9='Madrigosa accompanied me on this journey, but we have become separated in the Sunwell.$B$BMay fate keep her safe.$B'
Text0_0_loc9='Anveena is no mere mortal, $R. Those who recognize her true nature stop at nothing to possess her.$B$BShe once rescued me, and now I intend to return the favor.'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Enjoying the festival, $C?$B$BWhile the Flame Keepers tend to the fires of the present, I am more of a historian, keeping close the festivals past. I\'m also, of course, documenting this year\'s festivities. Things are going well thus far, don\'t you think?$B$BYou know, $N, there is power inherent in all festival fires burning throughout the holiday. We\'re taking care of ours, but I\'m certain there are sacred flames burning deep within our enemy\'s cities...',Text0_1_loc9='Enjoying the festival, $C?$B$BWhile the Flame Keepers tend to the fires of the present, I am more of a historian, keeping close the festivals past. I\'m also, of course, documenting this year\'s festivities. Things are going well thus far, don\'t you think?$B$BYou know, $N, there is power inherent in all festival fires burning throughout the holiday. We\'re taking care of ours, but I\'m certain there are sacred flames burning deep within our enemy\'s cities...',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=12609;
Text0_0_loc9='Welcome to our camp, $C. You\'re free to rest here if you\'d like.',Text0_1_loc9='Welcome to our camp, $C. You\'re free to rest here if you\'d like.'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='There is nothing left for us here.',Text0_1_loc9='There is nothing left for us here.',Text1_0_loc9='My family was slaughtered without mercy. Even the young.',Text1_1_loc9='My family was slaughtered without mercy. Even the young.' WHERE entry=12611;
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc9='May the Lich King burn in hellfire for what he has called down upon this land.',Text2_1_loc9='May the Lich King burn in hellfire for what he has called down upon this land.',Text3_0_loc9='We are a people without a home to call our own now.',Text3_1_loc9='We are a people without a home to call our own now.' WHERE entry=12611;
Text4_0_loc9='The Scourge are a fearless machine set to bring about the end of all life on this world.',Text4_1_loc9='The Scourge are a fearless machine set to bring about the end of all life on this world.',Text5_0_loc9='The one that they call Hellscream might be our only hope.'
Text6_0_loc9='Only the Horde can save us now.',Text6_1_loc9='Only the Horde can save us now.'
Text0_0_loc9='<Budd holds very still, pretending not to hear you. Looking closely you see a bit of drool drip from under his mask.>',Text1_0_loc9='<Budd rocks back and forth on his haunches, muttering something that sounds like troll speech.>'
Text2_0_loc9='Go away, mon.',Text3_0_loc9='No time to be talkin\', mon. I be needin\' to rest now....'
Text4_0_loc9='Troll powah, mon!',Text5_0_loc9='What be wrong wit you, mon? Ain\'t ya never seen a troll before?'
Text0_0_loc9='Will the Horde grant me the chance to battle the Scourge?',Text0_1_loc9='Will the Horde grant me the chance to battle the Scourge?'
Text0_0_loc9='To avenge my people, to drive out the blight that has engulfed our land - I will take your oath. I will pledge all that I have and all that I am to the Horde.',Text0_1_loc9='To avenge my people, to drive out the blight that has engulfed our land - I will take your oath. I will pledge all that I have and all that I am to the Horde.'
Text0_0_loc9='Lok\'tar ogar! Victory or death - it is these words that bind me to the Horde. For they are the most sacred and fundamental of truths to any warrior of the Horde.$B$BI give my flesh and blood freely to the Warchief. I am the instrument of my Warchief\'s desire. I am a weapon of my Warchief\'s command.$B$BFrom this moment until the end of days I live and die - FOR THE HORDE!',Text0_1_loc9='Lok\'tar ogar! Victory or death - it is these words that bind me to the Horde. For they are the most sacred and fundamental of truths to any warrior of the Horde.$B$BI give my flesh and blood freely to the Warchief. I am the instrument of my Warchief\'s desire. I am a weapon of my Warchief\'s command.$B$BFrom this moment until the end of days I live and die - FOR THE HORDE!'
Text0_0_loc9='Ey, mon! Take me to mah troll bruddas!',Text1_0_loc9='Time to play some troll tag, mon!'
Text2_0_loc9='My troll bruddas be in for some real fun today, mon!',Text3_0_loc9='Hee hee hee! Dis gunna be some fun, mon!'
Text4_0_loc9='You sure we be goin\' da right way, mon?',Text5_0_loc9='<sniff, sniff> I can smell \'em, mon.'
Text6_0_loc9='Nuttin\' says luvin\' like a little tap on da noggin.',Text7_0_loc9='Nuttin\' says luvin\' like a little tap on da noggin.'
Text0_0_loc9='All three of the gates at the Sunwell Plateau have been brought down, $N.$B$BYou must marshal your forces and stop Kil\'jaeden from entering Azeroth before all is lost!'
Text0_0_loc9='Riplash will never return to its former glory, but these boat-riding scum will pay for their deeds - I swear it!',Text0_1_loc9='Riplash will never return to its former glory, but these boat-riding scum will pay for their deeds - I swear it!'
Text0_0_loc9='It is our duty to protect these taunka and provide them with what little comfort we can offer.',Text0_1_loc9='It is our duty to protect these taunka and provide them with what little comfort we can offer.'
Text0_0_loc9='I never understood why some pirates bury their treasure.  Me... I like to keep it within arm\'s reach.'
Text0_0_loc9='Moa\'ki Harbor is blessed with two great sea turtles: Walker of Waves and Green Island. They swim between Unu\'pe and Kamagua.'
Text0_0_loc9='Eager to get to Northrend, are you? The steam-powered Kraken sails from here to Valiance Keep in Borean Tundra.',Text0_1_loc9='Eager to get to Northrend, are you? The steam-powered Kraken sails from here to Valiance Keep in Borean Tundra.'
Text0_0_loc9='Hey there! Miss the Eastern Kingdoms, huh? Well, the Kraken sails back to Stormwind if you\'re really itching to return. I know I\'d enjoy the warmer weather!'
Text0_0_loc9='Our blessed great sea turtle, Green Island, travels from here to Moa\'ki Harbor in Dragonblight.'
Text0_0_loc9='Yo. Lookin\' to get back to the Old World? Fly to Tirisfal Glades in style on the Cloudkisser.'
Text0_0_loc9='Northrend awaits, $R. The majestic Cloudkisser will take you straight across to the sea to Vengeance Landing in Howling Fjord.',Text0_1_loc9='Northrend awaits, $R. The majestic Cloudkisser will take you straight across to the sea to Vengeance Landing in Howling Fjord.'
Text0_0_loc9='Heading home, $C? The Mighty Wind will get you there, if home\'s in Kalimdor. She flies straight from here to Durotar.'
Text0_0_loc9='Wanted DEAD for treason and other treacherous acts against the Horde!$B$BAll bounties paid by Captain Gort.'
Text0_0_loc9='G\'day mate! Sit an\' have yerself a sip, won\'t yeh?'
Text0_0_loc9='All I ever wished for was to serve my king once again.  For humanity, against a common enemy.$B$BInstead, I find that our numbers have been infiltrated by cultist scum.... and all signs point to Naxxanar as the origin of this rot.'
Text0_0_loc9='This is where the cultists\' orders are coming from.  Their leader is bound to show up soon.$B$BLet\'s not miss this opportunity.'
Text0_0_loc9='Huh?  What?!  Go away.'
Text0_0_loc9='If I can make a new war machine, I know I can get a pretty penny for it over at the Wrath Gate.  $B$BSome of our previous iterations haven\'t been entirely... stable, but my flying machine should do the trick if I can just develop an effective bomb system for it.',Text0_1_loc9='If I can make a new war machine, I know I can get a pretty penny for it over at the Wrath Gate.  $B$BSome of our previous iterations haven\'t been entirely... stable, but my flying machine should do the trick if I can just develop an effective bomb system for it.'
Text0_0_loc9='You feel a strange presence as you stand before this ancient idol.'
Text0_0_loc9='Where the Eye of the Prophets rested for millenia, only an empty niche remains.'
Text0_0_loc9='Welcome!  If you need a place to rest, I can solve that problem.',Text0_1_loc9='Welcome!  If you need a place to rest, I can solve that problem.'
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Looking for an Arena Battlemaster? You can find them on the road between towns, or in the capitals.$B$BYou can bind here, at me. I can also teleport you to one of the capitals.',Text0_1_loc9='Looking for an Arena Battlemaster? You can find them on the road between towns, or in the capitals.$B$BYou can bind here, at me. I can also teleport you to one of the capitals.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=12684;
Text0_0_loc9='Welcome, $C!  I hope you aren\'t afraid of heights!$B$BI\'ve got a practice parachute for you.  These chutes are for quick landings.  If you want to gently soar to the ground, use a mount.  If you want action and an adrenaline rush, you fall.  At the last possible moment you use your chute.  That\'s how these were made.  Quick action!  Are you ready for some quick action?$B$BThe chute only lasts a few seconds.  So you\'ll need to time it just right.  I\'m not sure you can handle it, $C.  I\'d like to see you prove me wrong.',Text0_1_loc9='Welcome, $C!  I hope you aren\'t afraid of heights!$B$BI\'ve got a practice parachute for you.  These chutes are for quick landings.  If you want to gently soar to the ground, use a mount.  If you want action and an adrenaline rush, you fall.  At the last possible moment you use your chute.  That\'s how these were made.  Quick action!  Are you ready for some quick action?$B$BThe chute only lasts a few seconds.  So you\'ll need to time it just right.  I\'m not sure you can handle it, $C.  I\'d like to see you prove me wrong.'
Text0_0_loc9='You\'d better get outta here unless you want to find yourself in one of these cages....'
Text0_0_loc9='Thank you, $C, for seeing to it that I received the letter from my brother.$B$BRest assured, his death will not have been in vain. The blue dragonflight will pay for this.$B$BI\'ll see to it personally!',Text0_1_loc9='Thank you, $C, for seeing to it that I received the letter from my brother.$B$BRest assured, his death will not have been in vain. The blue dragonflight will pay for this.$B$BI\'ll see to it personally!'
Text0_0_loc9='Do your part in keeping the Scourge at bay, soldier! Report all suspicious activity and kill first, ask questions later!'
Text0_0_loc9='Mark my words, these forsaken fools will be the death of us all!',Text1_0_loc9='If you ask me, and you DID, I think we should kill all of the apothecaries before it\'s too late!'
Text2_0_loc9='The Horde is about honor and war. I am certain that there is nothing honorable about what these apothecaries are doing.',Text3_0_loc9='I\'m keeping an eye on the forsaken idiots down there. You can never be too cautious around them!'
Text4_0_loc9='If you have dealings with the doctor over there, be cautious. Whatever they\'re up to, it\'s unnatural.'
Text0_0_loc9='Mon, da west wastes of dis place be full o\' baddies. Stay away from dis here area if ya want to live!'
Text0_0_loc9='My charge at Agmar\'s Hammer extends far beyond the care of the animals at the stables.'
Text0_0_loc9='Expire? Me? Heh, not hardly, kid. That was just a scratch.'
Text0_0_loc9='With enough money, I could take over the world...'
