Text0_0_loc9='Leave me be, fool!'
Text0_0_loc9='What? You want to train under me, $C? You better be ready to work.'
Text0_0_loc9='You can sleep in the barracks, if you\'d like. Just don\'t wake my men, or I\'ll throw you out in the snow myself.'
Text0_0_loc9='Thank you for rescuing me, $N. I will never forget your courage and determination.'
Text0_0_loc9='It would be an honor to battle alongside of you as a brother of the Horde, $N. I accept your offer.'
Text0_0_loc9='You not a real mon til you killed a dragon... mon.'
Text0_0_loc9='Hello, $R.  I\'m sorry that you had to see our sacred land for the first time in such a state.',Text0_1_loc9='Hello, $R.  I\'m sorry that you had to see our sacred land for the first time in such a state.'
Text0_0_loc9='Hey dere. You need anythin\', you let me know.'
Text0_0_loc9='I have food, if you are hungry, and you may make use of my tent, should you require rest.',Text0_1_loc9='I have food, if you are hungry, and you may make use of my tent, should you require rest.'
Text0_0_loc9='Might not be snowy out there, but the nights here can freeze your nose right off. The bunks are in the back - just don\'t make a nuisance of yourself.'
Text0_0_loc9='Heh. Nothing against you, pup, but you might want to find somewhere else to bed down for the night. Wouldn\'t want that tender skin of yours to get bruised.'
Text0_0_loc9='Come in by the fire and rest, $R. I hope you don\'t mind the smell of fish.',Text0_1_loc9='Come in by the fire and rest, $R. I hope you don\'t mind the smell of fish.'
Text0_0_loc9='Through the valleys and peaks of Mount Hyjal, across the shifting sands of Silithus, against the Legion\'s dread armies - we have fought. We are the nameless, faceless, sons and daughters of the Alliance. By the Light and by the might of the Alliance, the first strike belongs to us and the last strike is all that our enemies see.$B$BWe are 7th Legion.$B'
Text0_0_loc9='Greetings!  Do you need something?'
Text0_0_loc9='My S.T.O.U.T. is more than just a target for throwing steins, it\'s a valuable training asset.  If you can hit S.T.O.U.T. you can probably hit anything!$B$BJust try not to hit me.'
Text0_0_loc9='All rewards to be paid by High Executor Wroth upon verification.$B$BSerious-minded individuals inquire within.$B$BNO SOLICITORS!'
Text0_0_loc9='We will ravage the living... I mean the Scourge, of course.$B$B'
Text0_0_loc9='<The Tuskarr eyes you suspiciously.>$B$BDo not stay long. You do not understand our people, and I don\'t want trouble.',Text0_1_loc9='<The Tuskarr eyes you suspiciously.>$B$BDo not stay long. You do not understand our people, and I don\'t want trouble.'
Text0_0_loc9='The sky is not safe, friend. Be alert!'
