Text0_0_loc9='The Infinite Dragonflight is attempting to alter the destiny of Prince Arthas Menethil. You know him now as the Lich King, but here and now he was still a Prince of Lordaeron trying to do what was best for his kingdom. Arthas makes a very fateful choice today, leading to something we Keepers of Time call an inflection point in the timeline.',Text0_1_loc9='The Infinite Dragonflight is attempting to alter the destiny of Prince Arthas Menethil. You know him now as the Lich King, but here and now he was still a Prince of Lordaeron trying to do what was best for his kingdom. Arthas makes a very fateful choice today, leading to something we Keepers of Time call an inflection point in the timeline.'
