Text0_0_loc9='How may I serve you?'
Text0_0_loc9='What do you want?'
Text0_0_loc9='I do not trust you enough to speak of such things.$B$BYou must respect the trials our people have endured, the burdens we have borne...$B$BPerhaps, if you were to bring great honor to Dun Niffelem, I would be inclined to share with you the knowledge of our people.'
