Text0_0_loc9='Sorry, friend. Only certified officers of the Horde can authorize the purchase of a vehicle.',Text0_1_loc9='Sorry, friend. Only certified officers of the Horde can authorize the purchase of a vehicle.'
Text0_0_loc9='Good to see ya again!$B$BKing Stormheart has informed me that he will be taking his leave for a time... a grim memory brought back to him has left him with a score to settle it seems. He was very insistent that we not join him, so we have respected his wishes as we always do.$B$BI have taken responsibility for our clan in the meantime. You are still welcome with us, of course.'
Text0_0_loc9='You are no taunka. Why have you come to the sacred burial grounds of our warriors?'
Text0_0_loc9='Look at them... all they care about is outdoing each other.',Text0_1_loc9='Look at them... all they care about is outdoing each other.'
Text0_0_loc9='You see, Thorim is not like these harpies.  He\'s a worthy being of near godlike stature.$B$BHe served the titans as guardian of Ulduar and the Terrace of the Makers.$B$BThat is until his wife, Sif, was cowardly slain by his brother.',Text0_1_loc9='You see, Thorim is not like these harpies.  He\'s a worthy being of near godlike stature.$B$BHe served the titans as guardian of Ulduar and the Terrace of the Makers.$B$BThat is until his wife, Sif, was cowardly slain by his brother.'
Text0_0_loc9='Thorim lost it.  He lashed out against his most beloved allies, the frost giants.$B$BThat\'s one reason why to this day, this land is torn apart by the war between the Hyldnir and the Sons of Hodir... and why Thorim has exiled himself to the Temple of Storms.',Text0_1_loc9='Thorim lost it.  He lashed out against his most beloved allies, the frost giants.$B$BThat\'s one reason why to this day, this land is torn apart by the war between the Hyldnir and the Sons of Hodir... and why Thorim has exiled himself to the Temple of Storms.'
Text0_0_loc9='What do I care if these she-wolves and the frost giants kill each other every day?$B$BNo, no... I want Thorim to break out of his stupor and rally all his allies to retake Ulduar.$B$BThe world will be torn asunder if he fails to accomplish this!$B$BAnd of course, I\'ll reward you appropriately.',Text0_1_loc9='What do I care if these she-wolves and the frost giants kill each other every day?$B$BNo, no... I want Thorim to break out of his stupor and rally all his allies to retake Ulduar.$B$BThe world will be torn asunder if he fails to accomplish this!$B$BAnd of course, I\'ll reward you appropriately.'
