Text0_0_loc9='Surely you\'ve been a student once in your life, $C. You learned from an instructor, and you gained respect for them in some way, yes? Maybe not as a person, but at the least, as one who knew more than you and was willing to teach you. If not, use your imagination...$B$BWhat would you do if you came to realize your instructor may not know as much as you thought, and that you may have found a better path?'
