Text0_0_loc9='I have heard tale of my boy being here. That he\'s now a powerful death knight in service of the Lich King. If this is true, then it must be me that ends the bloodline.$B$BMy charge now is to command Orgrim\'s Hammer to the top of Icecrown Citadel and destroy all Scourge that get in our way. We leave when you and your allies are ready.'
